Umubare w'abanduye indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19) mu Burayi/mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Umubare w'abarwaye coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibintu bimeze kimwe mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, byemeza ko nubwo biri mu bihe bitandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dushingiye ku byaranze Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro na UTIs bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kuzongera kwiyongera kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazakenera kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu buvuzi bw'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari umubare munini w'abantu barwaye indwara y'ibihaha z'impamvu zitazwi bavuzwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyo ndwara ari coronavirus nshya, ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yitwa indwara ya koronavirusi (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko 80% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 bagira uburwayi bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero bufite cyangwa budafite ibicurane by'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 ihita iba indwara ikomeye cyane, igasaba ko bajya mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi bantu 6% bahita baba indwara ikomeye, igasaba ko bavurwa mu buryo bw'ubutabazi.
Imfu z'abarwayi barwariye mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bufata abantu benshi mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza, tugereranya n'uko byagenze mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone twagereranyije umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'u Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bice bitandukanye by'isi, kandi uko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gihagaze mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi muri iki gihe ni na ko bimeze muri icyo gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ikinyamakuru Eurosurveillance cyo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, nk'uko byemezwa n'ishami rya OMS.
Muri EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye i Wuhan mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kandi kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ku itariki yavuzwe haruguru, hari abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, mu Butaliyani honyine hakaba hari abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Kubona imibare yose hamwe n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, ituruka gusa ku makuru yemewe, urugero nk'abakozi b'inzego z'ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere na OMS, buri munsi saa munani.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 imeze muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, no kuyigereranya n'iyo muri Italiya.
Mu buryo bwo kugereranya ubwandu bw'abanduye COVID-19, twabaze umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu minsi 14 yose, dufata urugero rw'imiterere isanzwe ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone, tugaragariza umubare w'abanduye muri buri gihugu kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani, tugereranyije n'abari mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imyiteguro ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imyiteguro y'ibyumweru 14 by'ubwandu bw'indwara ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikije iy'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri rusange, ku bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'izamuka ryihuse ry'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza na byo byerekanye ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Avuga ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutanga imibare y'abanduye ingana n'iyo mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bari mu kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imiterere igaragara mu mubare w'abandura COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo gutera imbere ku muvuduko nk'uwo mu bihugu byose.
Ibi bibaye nubwo ibihugu biri mu bihe bitandukanye, ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, ndetse wenda n'uburyo ibihugu bitandukanye byasobanuye abanduye n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye niba baranduye COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa kugira ngo bamenyekane.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twatewe n'icyorezo bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari bakeneye kuvurwa mu byumba byahariwe abarwayi cyane, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe byo muri utwo turere byari byamaze gukora ku buryo bwuzuye.
Amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bavurirwa mu bitaro na/cyangwa muri ICU ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru aterekanywe).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhoraho kugira ngo bisongere ku makuru y'ubugenzuzi bugezweho yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abishwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hagati ya 2010 na 2011 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kubona ibitanda bya ICU na Semi-intensive units mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29,2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4,2 muri Portugal ku bantu 100,000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira ubushobozi bwinshi cyangwa buke ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (ibitanda 12,5 bya ICU na serivisi z'ubuvuzi bw'indembe ku baturage ibihumbi 100 hagati ya 2010 na 2011).
Ibipimo by'imiterere bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushobozi bw'ubuvuzi, bigaragaza imibare ya buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza y'ubwiyongere bw'abarwariye mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 bafite ibyago birenze 90% by'ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU, bitangwa mu ivugurura rya gatandatu ry'igeragezwa ryihuse ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 rya ECDC.
Kubera ko kugeza ubu abarwayi baguye mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bikunze kwita ku baturage bagizwe n'abantu benshi, amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe by'indembe by'abarwayi bababaye cyane, akwiye gushyirwa ku rutonde rw'ibigo by'ibarwaye ku mpamvu z'ibarura 2 (NUTS-2).
Urugero rw'u Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro na UTIs rero bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera SIDA (SARS-CoV-2) mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu buvuzi bw'indembe, nk'uko bimeze mu turere two mu Butaliyani twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwitondewe kandi burambuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2, aho guhindukira ukava ku buryo bwo kugabanya ukagera ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera vuba kw'umubare w'abarwayi bishobora kutaha igihe gihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugira ngo basobanukirwe, bemere kandi bahindure ibikorwa byabo neza, niba bitashyizwe mu bikorwa hakiri kare.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rirerekana ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari umwanya muto ibihugu bishobora kongera ingamba zo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Iyo izo ngamba zananiranye, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'u Burayi na EAC zizagira umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya koronavirusi yo mu 2019 (COVID-19), yatewe n'indwara ya koronavirusi ya 2 (SARS-CoV-2) y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS), kimaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi 3 no kwandura abarenga ibihumbi 80 mu Bushinwa no ku isi hose, bituma abantu bagerwaho n'amakuba.
Kimwe na virusi ihuriyeho na yo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bantu babarirwa mu bihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwandura ikoresheje udusimba kandi igateza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo ikoresheje uburyo nk'ubwo.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane, kandi yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara nshya wiyongereye cyane, iki kiganiro kigamije gutanga isesengura rihoraho kandi ryuzuye ry'icyo kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi, kigenda kivuka vuba.
Tuzaganira ku mahame y'ibanze y'icyorezo, etiology, virology, gusuzuma, kuvura, kubara no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzafasha mu gusobanukirwa no kurandura iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'Igisibo wabaye ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umwibutso udasanzwe kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose bari basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'uwo munsi mukuru no mu byumweru byinshi bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya y'agakoko.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na koronavirusi (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) mu 2003; ku bw'ibyo, yiswe SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, indwara yayo yitwa indwara ya CoV-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yari imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80.000 banduye COVID-19, abarenga 40.000 bakize naho abarenga 3.000 barapfa.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere ku isi", kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zisaga 200 zanditswe ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, zirimo ibijyanye n'ubwandu, icyorezo, indwara, gusuzuma no kugifata, kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yatangajwe, igaragaza uko virusi yabonetse mu barwayi benshi.
Iki kiganiro kigamije gusubiramo iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi muri iki gice gishya cyihuta.
Aho bikenewe, tuzajya tugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyo mu 2012).
Tuzaganira kandi ku byo twize kugeza ubu ku kwirinda no kugenzura indwara, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo byihutirwa.
CoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zidakora ku bantu, ahanini zitera 15% by'ibicurane.
Ariko muri iki kinyejana, twabonye inshuro ebyiri abantu bafite virusi zanduza cyane, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zateye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi zifite uburwayi n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1,1, umubare munini w'abarwaye indwara y'ibicurane z'ibicurane z'inkomoko zitazwi wabanje kubwirwa Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rwa CoV rwarasohotse.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wapfuye muri Wuhan yaramenyekanye.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyahise gikwira mu mijyi, intara n'ibihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abashinzwe ubuzima batangajwe ko banduye, byerekana ko abantu bashobora guhura.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe, imodoka zose zitwara abagenzi zihagarara.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iyi ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho iyi ndwara, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibinyampeke rya Wuhan, ryitwa ko ryatangiriye ku nyama zitamenyekanye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku buzima ku isi hose.
Kugeza ubu iyi ndwara imaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi (Igishushanyo 2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda birushaho kuzamba, urugero n'uburemere bw'icyorezo biracyari kugenzurwa.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakorewe mu bigo bitandukanye ku barwayi 8,866, barimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19, bwagaragaje urugero rushya rw'icyorezo nk'uko bikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abantu b'imyaka yose, cyane cyane mu kigero cy'imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bamwe bari bafite imyaka iri munsi ya 20, kandi abanduye 14 gusa bari bafite imyaka iri munsi ya 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi (0,31/100.000) kurusha abagore (0,27/100.000).
COVID-19 yageze mu matsinda, cyane cyane muri Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
COVID-19 yahawe iminsi 5 (2 kugeza kuri 9) yo kuyisobanukirwa hashingiwe ku kugaragaza ibimenyetso.
Igihe cyo kubamo cyari iminsi 4,8 (3,0 - 7,2).
Igihe cy'urupfu ku bantu bose bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ni iminsi 9.5 (4.8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'abanduye (R0) wari 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51 kugeza 4.05), naho R0 ihindagurika yari 2.23 kugeza 4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bihuye n'igihe cy'ingendo z'abantu benshi mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Imfu z'abarwayi banduye ni 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10% - 1.86%), naho iz'abarwayi bose zashyizwe ku gipimo cya 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02% - 4.59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi bishobora gutera COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (barengeje imyaka 60), n'ibicurane bikomeye.
CoV ni umuryango muto wa virusi nini kandi ziganjemo virusi zirimo urukurikirane rumwe rw' RNA mu buryo runaka.
Zishobora kugabanywamo amoko ane ari yo: alpha, beta, gamma na delta, muri yo alfacoronavirus na betacoronavirus bizwiho kwanduza abantu.
Glycoprotein (S) yo mu mufuniko ifata ku byuma by'umubiri byakira angiotensin converting enzyme 2 (ECA2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hanyuma membrane fusion ikorwa.
Genome ya RNA ya virusi irasohoka mu cytoplasma; nyuma yo gusubiramo genome ya virusi, RNA ya genomic ijyanirana na glycoproteins zashyizwe mu mwanya wayo na poroteyine za nucleocapsid zigize uduhimba tugize virions, twunga uruhu rwa plasma maze dusohora virusi.
Urukurikirane rwa mbere rwa genom ya SARS-CoV-2 rwatangajwe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
Byagaragaye ko SARS-CoV-2 ari ubwoko bushya bwa betacoronavirus bufite ibimenyetso birenga 99,98% by'uko ari yo mu bwoko bwazo mu bipimo 10 byavanywe aho iki cyorezo cyaturutse, mu isoko ry'imbuto z'inyanja rya Huanan, mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite imiterere isa cyane na SARS-CoV kurusha MERS-CoV.
Binyuze muri mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike, udukoko twa SARS-CoV-2 twabonetse mu bice by'inyuma cyane by'urusobe rw'umwuka w'umuntu.
ECA2 y'umuntu yagaragaye ko ari receptor ya SARS-CoV-2, kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Icyakora, poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifatanye na poroteyine ECA2 y'umuntu mu buryo budafite imbaraga nyinshi ugereranyije na poroteyine ya SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bihuye n'uko SARS-CoV-2 itatera ubwandu bukabije mu barwayi kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine nto nshya ishingiye kuri orf3b na poroteyine ihishurwa ishingiye kuri orf8.
SARS-CoV-2 orf3b ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma virusi igira ubwandu kandi igahagarika IFNβ; ariko, orf8 nta ruhare cyangwa impamvu z'imikorere izwi ifite.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al. bavuze ko ECA2 y'umuntu y'uburebure bwose ifite uburebure bw'ubugari bwa 2,9 Å mu buryo bw'amajwi hamwe n'umuvuduko wa amino acide B0AT1.
Basanze uruziga rufite imiterere ifunguye n'ifunze, rufite imiterere y'ibinyamubiri, kandi uruziga rwa ECA2-B0AT1 rushobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, ibyo bikaba bitanga ibimenyetso byo kumenya no kwandura CoV.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba icyerekezo cyo kuvura mu gupima imiti igabanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Inkomoko y'inyamaswa n'umuhuza
Byombi SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV bizwi ko byakomotse ku nyamanswa kandi ko byandujwe ku bantu binyuze mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa civette na za ngamiya.
Binyuze mu kugereranya kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'izindi koronavirusi, udusimba twafashwe nk'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 kuko virusi nshya ihuriyeho na 96% na koronavirusi ebyiri z'ingore zisa na SARS zitwa bat-SL-CoVZX45 na bat-SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko, nyir'ubwite wafashije virusi kwambuka inzitizi z'ubwoko no kwanduza abantu aracyari mu nzira zitazwi, kandi inzira y'ubwandu iracyari mu nzira yo kuvumburwa.
Ji, et al., bagaragaza ko inzoka zitwara virusi zivuye mu birura zigera ku bantu, ibyo bikaba byarajyanye no kongera guhuriza hamwe mu bwoko bwa poroteyine ya S.
Nk'uko ubushakashatsi bwabigaragaje, abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Guangzhou mu Bushinwa, bagaragaje ko ingona, inyamaswa zifite umunwa muremure zikunda kurya ibimonyo kandi zikoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, zishobora kuba ari zo zinyura muri SARS-CoV-2, bashingiye ku buryo ingirabuzima fatizo za CoV ziboneka mu ngona zifite ubushobozi bwo guhura na SARS-CoV-2 ku kigero cya 99%.
Ariko rero, itandukaniro ry'ibice 1 ku ijana by'utuntu tubiri tw'utugingo ngengakamere ni itandukaniro rinini cyane, bityo rero, ibisubizo byemeza ku bimenyetso bifatika birategerejwe (Igishushanyo).
Ibintu by'imiterere ya SARS-CoV-2 biracyari byinshi.
SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu byumba by'imashini amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'umwotsi, ndetse n'iminsi 5 munsi ya 20°C mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe buri hagati ya 40% na 50%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira ibintu nk'ibyo.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora guhangana n'imirasire y'umuriro wa ultraviolet n'ubushyuhe bwa 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; Etere, 75% ya éthanol, umuti wica udukoko ukoreshwa na chlorine, acide péracétique, chloroforme n'ibindi byuma by'imyororokere, ariko si chlorhexidine, ni byo bikora neza mu guhashya virusi.
Muri rusange, abantu bose ntibaba bafite ubwirinzi bwa SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora kwandura iyi virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu nta bushakashatsi burambuye bwakozwe ku bisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora kureba gusa ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere ku zindi koronavirusi, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.4).4).
Muri rusange, nyuma y'uko virusi yinjiye mu nyamaswa, imanza imanza imanza imanza imanza imanza z'umubiri binyuze mu byuma by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (PRRs), harimo ibifite uburyo bwo kwakira ibyokurya byitwa lectin (C-type), Toll-type receptor (TLR), NOD-type receptor (NLR) na RIG-I-type receptor (RLR).
Binyuze mu nzira zitandukanye, virusi ituma habaho kugaragaza ibintu by'ubuhumekero, gukura kw'ingirabuzima fatizo z'udutsi n'imikorere y'indwara z'imiterere ya mbere (IFNs), zigabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi kandi zigatuma imikorere y'imikorere y'indwara z'imiterere y'indwara yihuta.
Icyakora, poroteyine N ya SARS-CoV ishobora gufasha virusi guhunga ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Mu gihe gito, ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri buzafatanya n'ubundi kurwanya virusi.
Imyotsi ya T, harimo CD4+ na CD8+ igira uruhare runini mu kwivuna.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za CD4+ zitera ingirabuzimafatizo za B gukora abasirikare ba virusi, naho CD8+ zikangiza ingirabuzimafatizo zanduye virusi.
Ingirabuzimafatizo za T z'abafatanyabikorwa zitanga cytokines z'ubuhumekero zifasha mu kurinda ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ariko CoV ishobora kubuza imikorere y'utugingo twa T, igatuma utwo tugingo tuzima tuvaho.
Ubwugamo bw'umubiri, burimo n'ubundi bufasha nk'ubwirinzi bwa C3a na C5a, na bwo ni ingenzi mu kurwanya ubwandu bwa virusi.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bavuye mu murwayi wakize banesheje MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umubiri wongeye kugira imbaraga mu kurwanya indwara, habaho ingufu nyinshi z'ibyorezo bishobora kwangiza cyane ibihaha n'izindi ngingo, kandi mu gihe kibi cyane, ingingo nyinshi z'umubiri zirasenyuka, ndetse umuntu akicwa.
Indwara ya SARS-CoV-2, igaragazwa no kugaragaza ibimenyetso mu itsinda ry'abantu, yibasira cyane cyane abageze mu za bukuru bafite indwara ziterwa na yo hamwe n'abagore batwite.
Ni ibisanzwe ko abantu bagaragarizwa virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budafite imbaraga bagira amahirwe menshi yo kwandura kurusha abandi bantu.
Igihe ntarengwa cyo kubamo SARS-CoV-2 ni iminsi 1 kugeza kuri 14, kandi akenshi ni iminsi 3 kugeza kuri 7, bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye muri Wuhan.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 1.099 bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kuboneza urubyaro cyari iminsi 3, ku kigereranyo, kandi kikava ku minsi 0 kugeza ku minsi 24.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, bugaragaza ko igihe cyo kwiba cyari iminsi 4.8 (3.0 - 7.2), hashingiwe ku mibare y'abantu 8.866.
Ni ngombwa ko abayobozi b'ubuzima bahindura igihe cy'igenzura cy'ukuri hashingiwe ku gihe cy'igisibo gihamye, bityo bikabuza abantu banduye batagaragaza ibimenyetso kwanduza abandi.
Nk'uko bisanzwe bikorwa, abantu bagaragaweho virusi cyangwa bayanduye, akenshi bagomba kuguma mu kato iminsi 14.
Ese igihe cyo guhagarika abantu kigomba kongerwaho iminsi 24?
Ubusanzwe umuriro ni cyo kimenyetso cya mbere kandi cy'ingenzi cya COVID-19, gishobora kuza cyonyine cyangwa kiza giherekejwe n'ibindi bimenyetso, nk'inkorora yumye, guhumeka nabi, kubabara imitsi, isesemi, umutwe, kubabara mu muhogo, kurwara mu gatuza, kubabara mu gatuza, iseseme, kugira iseseme no gusubiranamo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje indwara y'umwijima n'igifu mu cyumweru kimwe nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Mu bihe bikomeye, abarwayi bahise batera indwara y'ubuhumekero, uburwayi bw'ubuhumekero, acidosis ya metabolic na coagulopathy.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukaze, ndetse n'abataragize ubwandu bw'ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bagomba gupimwa virusi kugira ngo babashe kubona indwara hakiri kare.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko ibimenyetso byari 98% ku ndwara y'umuriro, 76% ku ikorora ryumye, 55% ku ndwara ya dyspnea na 3% ku ndwara y'ibisebe; 8% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye inkunga yo guhumeka.
Ibisubizo nk'ibyo byavuzwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa bwakozwe ku muryango umwe no ku muryango umwe w'abantu batagira ibimenyetso.
Mu kugereranya, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV na bo bagaragaje umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%) na dyspnea (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi.
Icyakora, 80% by'abarwayi bari bakeneye gufashwa guhumeka, baruta cyane abarwayi ba COVID-19, ibyo bikaba ari byo bituma MERS ihitana abantu benshi ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Kurwara igifu (26%) n'ububabare bw'izuru (21%) nabyo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, basanze umuriro (99% kugeza 100%), inkorora yumye (29% kugeza 75%), indwara y'ubuhumekero (40% kugeza 42%), iseseme (20% kugeza 25%) n'ububabare bw'izuru (13% kugeza 25%) ari ibimenyetso by'ingenzi, kandi inkunga y'umwuka yari ngombwa ku barwayi bagera kuri 14% kugeza 20%.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umubare w'abapfa bishwe na COVID-19 wari 2%, ubwo imibare y'abanduye isi yose yageraga ku 66.576.
Mu kugereranya, umubare w'abapfa kubera SARS kugeza mu Gushyingo 2002 wari 10% by'abantu 8.096 bamaze kwandura.
Ku bw'indwara ya MERS, ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kwezi kwa Kamena 2012, umubare w'abapfa wari 37% by'abarwayi 2,494 bose.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa bwagaragaje ko umubare w'ibanze wa R0 wa SARS-CoV-2 wari 6.47 ufite intera y'icyizere (CI) ya 95%, 5.71 kugeza 7.23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4 gusa.
Kugereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV mu bijyanye n'ibimenyetso, impfu na R0 bigaragara mu mbonerahamwe.
Imibare iri hejuru igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko ko idashobora kwica cyane nk'izo ebyiri za nyuma.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni imbogamizi ikomeye cyane kugenzura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Kwibonera ibimenyetso mu itsinda ry'abantu akenshi biba mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu itsinda rimwe cyangwa mu modoka imwe, nk'ubwato bw'urugendo.
Abarwayi bakunze kuba baragize urugendo cyangwa bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi duce twatewe n'icyorezo, cyangwa se bakaganiriye n'abantu banduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri mbere y'uko bagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Icyakora, byagiye bivugwa ko abantu bashobora gutwara virusi mu gihe kirenga ibyumweru bibiri nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, kandi abarwayi bakize bakurwa mu bitaro bashobora kongera kwandura virusi, ibyo bikaba byateye abantu gukangurira abantu kongera igihe cyo kuba mu kato.
Abarwayi bafite umubare usanzwe cyangwa muke w' insoro zera z' amaraso (cyane cyane za ' lymphocyte ') mu ntangiriro.
Urugero, lymphopenia ifite umubare w'amaraso yera uri munsi ya 4 x 109/L harimo umubare w'amasohoro y'amaraso ari munsi ya 1 x 109/L, hamwe n'urwego rwo hejuru rwa aspartate aminotransferase na viremia byabonetse mu barwayi 1,099 bafite COVID-19.
Imyinshi mu ndwara z'umwijima n'iz'umwijima z'abantu benshi, zirimo indwara z'umwijima n'iz'umwijima.
Mu barwayi barwaye cyane, umubare wa dimer-D, ikorwa mu kuvanaho fibrin mu maraso, wariyongereye, kandi umubare w'indwara z'amaraso wariyongereye.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe ku mashusho ya radiyo y'igituza biri mu barwayi benshi bafite COVID-19, kandi bigaragaza ibicucu bidasanzwe cyangwa ibirahuri mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira uburwayi bw' ibihaha, kwangirika kw' ibihaha no guhumeka nabi cyane (ARDS).
Iyo ARDS ibayeho, kubyimba bidategekanywa, kwiyongera kw'amazi n'imyanya ndangagitsina bigenda birushaho kugabanya imikorere y'umwuka.
Imikorere mibi y'utugingo tw'ibihaha tw'ubwoko bwa mbere n'ubwa kabiri, ituma igipimo cy'umusemburo w'ibihaha kigabanuka kandi igatuma ibihaha byongera imbaraga, bityo bigatuma ibihaha bidabasha kwaguka, kandi bigatuma ibyago byo guhagarara byongera.
Ku bw'ibyo, ibisubizo bikomeye cyane bya radiographie y'igituza akenshi biba bihuye n'ubwoko bukomeye bw'iyo ndwara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryerekanye ko hari uduheri tw'ibihaha, uruhu rw'uruhu rw'amahembe, uturemangingo tw'amaraso n'utundi tw'amaraso twinjiye mu bihaha by'umurwayi wapfuye azize iyo ndwara, bihuye n'indwara y'ubwandu bwa virusi na ARDS, kandi bisa n'indwara z'abarwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kumenya RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu buryo bwa polymerase  reverse transcriptase chain reaction (RT-PCR) byakoreshejwe nk'uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gusuzuma COVID-19.
Icyakora, kubera ko abantu benshi bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'amabeshyi bishobora gutuma icyorezo gikomeza kwiyongera, ibimenyetso byo mu bitaro byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma indwara (bitari bivuye kuri RT-PCR yonyine) mu Bushinwa ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibintu nk'ibyo kandi byabayeho mu gihe SARS yagaragaye.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhuza amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, ibizamini byo muri laboratwari n'ibisubizo bya radiyo ni ngombwa kandi ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu agere ku kizamini kizima.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryasobanuye uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa SHERLOCK bushingiye kuri CRISPR mu gutahura SARS-CoV-2, bushobora gutahura ibice bya RNA byakozwe na SARS-CoV-2 kuri 20 x 10-18 mol/L kugeza kuri 200 x 10-18 mol/L (10 kugeza ku 100 kopi kuri microlitiro y'umusanzu) hakoreshejwe inkoni yo gupima mu gihe kitarenze isaha, nta bikoresho bikomeye bikenewe.
Turizera ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kongera cyane ibyiyumvo no kwifashishwa, niba bwemejwe mu bipimo byo mu buvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye kuri CoV nshya, abaganga bashobora gutanga uko bashoboye kose imiti yica COVID-19 mu gihe bagerageza imiti itandukanye yakoreshejwe cyangwa yatangijwe mbere mu kuvura izindi CoV nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara zituruka kuri virusi (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe2).2).
Muri izo miti harimo imiti ikoreshwa ubu n'ishobora gukoreshwa, imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri, imiti ya 'steroïde', plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze.
Ndetse n'umushongi w'abarwayi bakize watangajwe nk'uburyo bwo kuvurwa.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi arimo guhatana n'igihe cyo gukora antibody n'inkingo za virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane cyane ibihaha mu ntangiriro kandi birashoboka ko yibasira mu rugero ruciriritse izindi ngingo zigaragaza ECA2, nk'igifu n'impyiko.
Nyamara, guhumeka nabi no kunanirwa kw'ingingo ni byo bintu by'ingenzi bibangamiye abarwayi kandi ni byo bituma abantu benshi bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, ubufasha bwo guhumeka ni ingenzi mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima, kandi bukubiyemo imiti rusange ya ogisijeni, ogisijeni y'imashini nyinshi, guhumeka bidakoreshejwe n'imashini z'ubuvuzi, bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba guhabwa umwuka wa 'extracorporeal membrane oxygenation' (ECMO), uburyo bushya bwo kuvura umutima n'ubuhumekero bukoreshwa mu kuvura umutima cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ubusumbane bwa electrolyte, gukumira no kuvura indwara z'ibyorezo n'imyanda y'ibinyabutabire, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi na byo ni ingenzi ku barwayi ba SARS-CoV-2.
Byari bizwi ko cytocin cascade iterwa n'ingaruka z'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Cytokine cascade ni uburyo bwo guhangana n'indwara ziterwa n'ubukana bw'indwara, igaragazwa no kuzana cytokines nyinshi zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ, na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zisohora ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'umwidegemvyo, ari zo mpamvu nyamukuru y'indwara ya ARDS n'imikorere mibi y'ingingo nyinshi.
Immunosuppression ni ingenzi mu kuvura indwara z'imyakura, cyane cyane ku barwayi bakomeye.
Imiti yitwa corticosteroids na tocilizumab, umuti wa monoclonal anti-IL6, ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara ya cytocin.
Izindi miti yo kurwanya indwara zo mu mubiri zitera indwara zo mu mubiri zirimo: guhosha ibisubizo by'umubiri biganisha ku ngirabuzimafatizo za T; guhagarika IFN-y, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK, blinatumomab; guhagarika ibimenyetso bya cytokine 4; no kubuza HDAC.
Steroids, nk'imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse.
Icyakora, gukoresha ibipimo byinshi bya siteroide ntibyatanze umusaruro ku ndwara ikomeye y'ibihaha mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Zishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye cyane cyane osteonecrosis avascular, bigatuma umuntu atabasha kwivuza.
Icyakora, igihe gito cyo gukoresha imiti ya corticosteroid mu doze nke kugeza ku rugero ruciriritse cyasabwe gukoreshwa mu bwitonzi ku barwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane.
Mu gihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga, nta muti wa virusi ushoboye kwemezwa.
Icyakora, byaje kugaragara ko guterwa intravenously na remdesivir, analogue ya nucleotide, byagize ingaruka nziza ku murwayi wo muri Amerika ufite COVID-19.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa virusi wakozwe na Gilead, mu mizo ya mbere wari ugenewe kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma, remdesivir yagaragaje ko ishobora no kubuza izindi virusi z'urusyo rworoheje rwa RNA, harimo virusi za MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye Ubushinwa uwo muti kugira ngo ukoreshwe mu gupima abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, baricitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ ritonavir, na ribavirin byatanzwe nk'uburyo bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bukabije.
Kurwara igifu, kugira iseseme, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'ibindi bibazo bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufata imiti ivanze na lopinavir/ ritonavir.
Imikorere y'iyi miti hamwe n'indi miti ikoreshwa n'abarwayi igomba kugenzurwa cyane.
Plasma y'abarwayi bakize n'imikorere y'abasirikare
Gufata amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura kugira ngo bavurwe abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara, cyangwa kugira ngo barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwandura iyo ndwara, bimaze igihe kirekire.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira urugero rwagutse rw'abasirikare b'umubiri mu maraso yabo barwanya icyo cyorezo.
Antibodies ni immunoglobulin (lg) ikorwa na B lymphocyte zo kurwanya indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga, kandi zimenya molekile z'umwihariko mu ndwara kandi zikazica mu buryo butaziguye.
Bishingiye kuri ibyo, plasma yakuwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19, maze ishyirwa mu barwayi 10 bari bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Ibimenyetso bye byaragabanutse mu masaha 24, hamwe no kugabanya ubuhumekero n'ibiro bya virusi, no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko, ubugenzuzi no gusobanura birakenewe kugirango hategurwe gukoresha uburyo ku rwego runini mbere yo gukora imiti yihariye.
Byongeye kandi, kubera ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari ibyago bimwe na bimwe bifitanye isano na plasma bigomba gufatwaho mu buryo bwitondewe.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gutuma umubiri udakora neza, bigatuma habaho indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo mu mubiri, kandi ibyo bishobora gutuma umuntu apfa.
Umubare w'abanduye mu maraso ubusanzwe uba uri hasi, kandi plasma ikenerwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Biragoye guhanga no gukora udukoko tw'ubwirinzi bwihariye mu buryo bwihuse ku buryo twahangana n'icyorezo ku isi hose.
Ni ngombwa kandi birashoboka cyane gutandukanya uturemangingo twa B mu barwayi bakize no kumenya kode za jenoside zigaragaza abasirikare b'umubiri bafite ubushobozi cyangwa se gukosora abasirikare b'umubiri bafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi.
Ibyo bituma dushobora kongera ingano y'abasirikare b'umubiri mu buryo bwihuse.
Ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, TCM, bwakoreshejwe mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu Bushinwa.
Ariko ingaruka zabyo zishingira cyane ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo butandukanye bitewe n'uko indwara igaragajwe hashingiwe ku bitekerezo bya TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bikora neza biracyari ibyamamare cyangwa bidafite ibisobanuro kuko bigoye kubikuramo no kubisuzuma cyangwa guhuza neza.
Muri iki gihe, kubera kubura imiti yihariye kandi ikora neza ya COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti y'ingenzi ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje, cyangwa ku barwayi bakize indwara ikomeye.
Urugero, twabonye ko imiti ya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen igira ingaruka nziza mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ibipimo byiza byo gukira kw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byagaragariye mu ntara zitandukanye zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 87% harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), mu gihe Intara ya Hubei yakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 30% gusa ba COVID-19 yagize igipimo cyo gukira gito cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, ibyo biragoye kubigereranya, kuko hari ibintu byinshi bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bw'indwara, bigomba gushyirwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be bashyize ahagaragara ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'iburengerazuba bwonyine n'uburyo bwo kuvura bwo mu Burengerazuba bw'isi hamwe na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, guhosha ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu baganga bavuraga imiti y'iburengerazuba n'iyo mu bwoko bwa TCM ugereranyije n'abavuraga imiti y'iburengerazuba bonyine.
Umubare w'ibyago byo kuremba (kuva ku bitagira ingano kugeza ku bikomeye) wari muto cyane mu baganga bavuraga imiti y'iburayi n'imiti ya TCM ugereranyije n'abavuraga imiti y'iburayi yonyine (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%), kandi umubare w'abapfa wari muto mu baganga bavuraga imiti y'iburayi n'imiti ya TCM ugereranyije n'abavuraga imiti y'iburayi yonyine (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Icyakora, ubudahangarwa n'ubushobozi bwa TCM biracyategereje kugeragezwa ku kigero kinini kandi mu bigo byinshi.
Ni byiza kandi gusobanura uburyo bwo gukora no gusobanura ibice by'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura TCM cyangwa se ifatanyije na yo, niba bishoboka.
Abarwayi bagaragaweho COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho uburwayi, muri rusange bagira ubwoba bwinshi bw'iyo ndwara yandura cyane kandi ishobora kwica, kandi abantu bari mu kato na bo bumva bananiwe, bafite irungu kandi barakaye.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara, urugero nk'umuriro mwinshi, kugira ikibazo cyo kubura umwuka n'inkorora, hamwe n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti, urugero nk'ibitotsi biterwa na siteroyi, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira imihangayiko myinshi n'imibabaro.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya SARS, hari indwara zitandukanye z'imitekerereze zirimo kwiheba, guhangayika, ubwoba, guhungabana, ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu mutwe, ubwirasi ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana abantu no kubajyana mu kato nk'ibisabwa mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi rusange byo kurwanya icyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu barushaho guhangayika, kandi bashobora kumva bafite ikosa bitewe n'ingaruka z'ubwandu, kubajyana mu kato, no gutesha agaciro imiryango yabo n'incuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abantu bakekwaho uburwayi n'abahuye na bo, ndetse n'abaturage muri rusange bakeneye kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima, bagomba guhabwa ubufasha mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha mu by'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'indwara zo mu mutwe, gutangaza amakuru y'igihe cyose kandi adaca ku ruhande ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi y'ubuvuzi, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'imashini zo mu rwego rw'umwuga mu kwirinda guhura n'abantu imbonankubone.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu guhagarika ikurikiranyabiziga ry'ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima n'abantu banduye ku bantu bashobora kwandura, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa nk'inkunga mu kuvura virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi zigenda zivuka.
Hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S kugira ngo zitange abasirikare barwanya SARS-CoV bafite imbaraga kandi barambye.
Inkingo zagenzuwe mu nyamaswa mu gupima SARS.
Ariko, imbaraga muri in vivo z'izi nkingo z'abakandida mu bantu bakuze n'uburyo ziteza urupfu n'uburyo zirinda kwandura virusi z'amatungo biracyakeneye kumenyekana mbere y'uko ikigo gitangira.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 itakiriho kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze uvugwa kuva icyo gihe.
Ku rundi ruhande, hari izindi ndwara z'ibyorezo bya MERS zikomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati kandi zigakwira mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko hari ibyago by'indwara zo mu matungo mu duce tw'icyorezo.
Uburyo bwo gukingira bwagiye bukoreshwa mu kurwanya MERS hakoreshejwe virusi zidakora, plasmide za ADN, virusi, utuntu duto duto, utuntu tumeze nk'udukoko na poroteyine z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe, kandi hari n'abashakishijwe mu nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwiza kandi rwiza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo kiriho.
Ariko kandi, biragoye gutsinda iki kibazo bitewe n'igihe kirekire (amezi 18 ku kigereranyo) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo n'impinduka mu mikorere y'indwara ya CoV.
Nk'indwara nshya, COVID-19 imaze gutangira kugaragaza uburwayi bwayo bwose, igera ku barwayi babarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi barakira buhoro buhoro nta ngaruka.
Icyakora, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 na yo ifitanye isano n'uburwayi bwinshi n'urupfu mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije.
Kubaka uburyo bwo kubara indwara ni ngombwa kugira ngo inzego z'ubuzima zibanze gutanga serivisi, cyane cyane mu duce tudafite amikoro.
Dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka cyangwa bifitanye isano n'ubwiru bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 (Imbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe33)):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yabaye ingenzi mu kwemeza ko SARS izaza, kandi ni na ko bimeze kuri COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bafite hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65, aho 47,7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866, nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bari bakeneye kwivuza mu buryo bwihariye bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara no kurwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara, kandi bari bakuze cyane ugereranyije n'abarwayi batari bakeneye kwivuza mu buryo bwihariye (imyaka 66 ugereranyije n'imyaka 51), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ari yo ituma abarwayi ba COVID-19 barushaho kugira ubuzima bwiza.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yanduje abagabo benshi kurusha abagore (0,31/100.000 abagabo na 0,27/100.000 abagore), nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Indwara ziterwa n'indwara n'ibibazo: Abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurwa mu buryo bw'indwara z'ubuhumekero bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibikomere by'umutima cyangwa arrhythmie.
Indwara y'umutima ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu mu barwayi ba SARS.
Hari amakuru avuga ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwifatanya na cholangite z'indwara ya ECA2 zemeza, bishobora gutuma abarwayi bafite COVID-19 badakora neza mu myanya y'ububabare.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka n'indwara ziterwa na yo bifitanye isano ikomeye kandi bishobora guhungabanya bimwe.
Ibisubizo bidasanzwe by'ibizamini: Igipimo cya poroteyine igira ibyiyumvo (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa imvune mu mubiri kandi cyashyizwe imbere nk'ikintu gishobora kwemeza indwara, gusubiza imiti no gukira burundu.
Hatanzwe kandi igitekerezo cyo guhuza igipimo cya CRP n'uburemere bwa COVID-19 n'uko ishobora kwibasira umuntu.
Byongeye kandi, ibipimo byo hejuru bya lactate hydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza umusaruro.
Izi enzymes ziboneka cyane mu ngingo zitandukanye, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, kandi zisohoka mu gihe habaye imvune.
Ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'umutima cyangwa impyiko zidakora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'uburwayi: Igishushanyo cy'igituza n'iterambere ry'ibipimo by'uburwayi mu gihe runaka bigomba gusuzumwa hamwe n'ibindi bibazo mu kwitegereza ingaruka/ibibazo bya COVID-19.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti yica abarwayi ikoreshwa nk'umuti wunganira indwara zitandura mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse.
Kubera ko ibipimo byinshi bya corticosteroids byakoreshejwe cyane ku barwayi bafite SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barokotse basanzwemo indwara y'amagufa (osteonecrosis avasculaire) ibaviramo ubumuga budashira n'ubuzima budafite agaciro.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba ari ngombwa, siteroyi zigomba gukoreshwa ku gipimo cyo hasi kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
Imihangayiko yo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19, abarwayi benshi bahura n'imihangayiko myinshi, kuko baba bari mu bihe birebire byo gushyirwa mu kato no mu bihe bitoroshye, kandi bakibonera urupfu rw'ababo bakundaga n'abandi barwayi.
Ni ngombwa gutanga ubujyanama mu by'imitekerereze no gushyigikira aba barwayi igihe kirekire kugira ngo babafashe kwivana mu mihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku baturage kugeza ubu, COVID-19 isa n'ifite ibimenyetso by'icyorezo bitandukanye n'ibya SARS.
Uretse kuba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduza mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ishobora no kwanduza mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru kandi ntizitera ibimenyetso mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'ibanze (cyangwa zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa), kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi zitera ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu ntangiriro cyangwa mu gihe cyo kwihaza bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu gihe bakora imirimo yabo ya buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana cyane.
Icyakora, byemejwe ko SARS-CoV yandura iyo abarwayi barwaye cyane, kandi ko ubwandu bwinshi butaba mu ntangiriro.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi biragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe mu Bushinwa hari imbaraga nyinshi zirimo gukorwa, harimo gufunga Wuhan n'imijyi ihakikije, no gushyira mu kato abaturage hafi ya bose, mu rwego rwo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibyo bikorwa byagize ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragenda ugabanuka, bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo cyamaze kugabanuka.
Impinduka nziza cyane ni uko icyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, igihe cyo kugabanuka kikazamara amezi atatu cyangwa ane.
Ariko kandi, hari abandi bahanga batagira icyizere.
Paul Hunter, et al, batangaje ko COVID-19, isa n'iyandura cyane kurusha SARS, itazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Longini, et al., bashyizeho uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo, bagaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda rimwe ryo muri Kanada ryatangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu myenda yo mu muhogo no mu mahembe y'abarwayi bakize kandi bavuye mu bitaro mu byumweru 2 bishize, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko virusi nshya bamenye ishobora guhinduka icyorezo cy'ibicurane.
Ariko kandi, hari ibimenyetso by'uko mu Bushinwa hari abantu benshi barwaye indwara nshya, bigaragaza ko ingamba zashyizweho zishobora kugira icyo zigeraho.
Ebola yari yitezwe mbere ko ishobora guhitana abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe, naho ihitana abagera kuri miliyoni imwe.
Hagati aho, kubera ko abantu bari bashyizwe mu kato kandi bakirinda cyane, indwara yaje kugenzurwa.
Birashoboka ko SARS-CoV-2, kimwe na SARS-CoV, ishobora guhinduka ikagira intege nke mu kwanduzanya, kandi igihe kimwe ikazavamo virusi idateza indwara nyinshi ikorana n'abantu.
Gereranya icyorezo cya COVID-19 n'icy'indwara ya SARS na MERS biri ahagana hasi (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo.55)).
SARS-CoV-2 yandura cyane iyo ukoroye cyangwa ukoroye agatete, kandi wenda binyuze mu guhura n'ibintu byanduye virusi.
Virusi kandi yasanzwe mu busa, ibyo bikaba bitanga uburyo bushya bwo kuyandura: kwanduzanya mu kanwa n'ubwoya.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abo barwayi bashobora kuba baraterwaga n'indwara z'ibyorezo, harimo 17 barwaye indwara z'ibanze n'abakozi 40 b'ubuzima.
Ni yo mpamvu hagomba gufatwa ingamba zikomeye zo kurinda abantu, cyane cyane abakozi bo mu buvuzi, abakozi bashinzwe imibereho myiza y'abaturage, abagize umuryango, abo bakorana n'abantu bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'abarwayi cyangwa abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda bwakoreshwa mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa; kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero twitwa N95 (Uruzitiro rwa 1860s) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda udutonyanga tw'amazi tuva ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye gutembera mu kirere cyangwa kwifatanya n'ibintu bishobora kwanduza abandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa twa N95 (ruronde rwa 1860s) ni two gusa turinda umuntu guhumeka virusi iri hagati ya 10 nm na 80 nm, 5% gusa muri izo virusi akaba ari zo zishobora kuyinyuramo burundu; SARS-CoV-2 isa na SARS-CoV mu bunini, kandi zombi zifite ubunini bwa 85 nm.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora kwinjira mu masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi, abaganga bahura n'abarwayi bagomba kwambara masike za N95 (serie 1860s) ariko ntibagire masike z'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abakozi b'ubuzima bagomba kwambara amakanzu yo kwihererana kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya guhura na virusi.
Virusi kandi zandura umuntu binyuze mu maso.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2, nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu maso ye aremaye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abakozi b'ubuzima bagomba no kwambara udukingirizo tw'amaso cyangwa indorerwamo zirinda indwara mu gihe bita ku barwayi.
Ku baturage muri rusange bari mu duce twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, barasabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune, bagakomeza kuguma mu ngo zabo kandi bakirinda guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Metero imwe ifatwa nk'intera ikwiriye yo kuva ku murwayi.
Ibyo bikorwa ni uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura ndetse no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 yavutse ari virusi nshya ku bantu, kuba ifite aho ihuriye na SARS-CoV nk'uko byavuzwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, byagombye kuba byaratumye Ubushinwa buhagurukira cyane, hashingiwe ku mateka ya vuba y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003.
Icyakora, ku itariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe kurwanya indwara yahaye abaturage icyizere avuga ko iyi virusi nshya idashobora kwanduza abantu cyane kandi ko nta buryo bwinshi ishobora kwanduzanya n'abandi, kandi ko kwirinda no gukumira iyi ndwara bitoroshye.
Ubwo butumwa bwatumye abantu barushaho gutuza, cyane cyane ubwo igihugu cyose cyari kigiye kwitegura Umunsi Mukuru w'Umwaka w'Impeshyi, kandi igihe gikomeye cyo kugabanya ubwandu muri Wuhan ku kigero gito cyaratakaye.
Ibigo bishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa bishobora kubonera inyungu muri iri somo rikomeye no gukora ivugurura rikomeye mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, ibi bigo bigomba: (1) kwitonda cyane mu gutanga ibitekerezo ku mugaragaro, kuko ibyo bavuga byose byinjirwa mu baturage kandi bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myifatire yabo n'ibyemezo byabo; (2) kugira ibyiyumvo kandi bakitabira amakuru adasanzwe aturuka mu bitaro, aho gutegereza itangazo ry'imikorere y'abaganga n'abayobozi; (3) kugira ingamba zikomeye zo guhashya icyorezo gishobora kwaduka mu ntangiriro zacyo, aho kugerageza guhumuriza abaturage; no (4) gutangaza kenshi cyane igerageza rigamije no gukora neza mu kongera ubumenyi bw'abaturage ku ndwara z'ibyorezo no gupima no kunoza uburyo bw'imibereho y'abaturage.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangiye mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, cyakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi, nk'uko iyi nkuru yanditswe.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na SARS-CoV, kandi ibimenyetso na byo bikaba bisa cyane na COVID-19 na SARS, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatumye abantu bumva ko SARS yagarutse.
Icyakora, hari itandukaniro rikomeye hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS, ari na ryo rikomeye mu kurwanya icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 yibasira abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, abagabo kurusha abagore, kandi ubukana n'imfu na byo biri hejuru ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato.
SARS ifite igipimo cyo gupfa kiri hejuru ugereranyije na COVID-19 (10,91% ugereranyije na 1,44%).
Abarwayi ba COVID-19 batanga virusi iyo nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, mu gihe abarwayi ba SARS ubusanzwe bayitanga iyo barwaye cyane, ibyo bikaba bituma kurwanya ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 bigorana kurusha SARS.
Ibi bisobanura mu rugero runaka impamvu SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira vuba cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka mu turere twinshi kurusha SARS-CoV.
Igikorwa cyo gupima RNA buri gihe cya SARS-CoV-2 gishobora kugaragaza ko nta virusi itera COVID-19 mu barwayi bamwe na bamwe.
Ku rundi ruhande, abarwayi bakize bashobora kongera gupimwa bakongera bagasanga bafite virusi.
Ibi byagezweho byongereye cyane ibyago byo gukwirakwiza virusi.
Bitewe n'iterambere ryihuse mu bushakashatsi kuri COVID-19, ibibazo byinshi by'ingenzi biracyakeneye gukemurwa, nk'uko bikurikira:
SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse he?
Nubwo hari ihuriro ry'imiterere rya 96% ryabonetse hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na CoV ebyiri zo mu biremwa by'imbeba zisa na SARS, ntitwavuga ko SARS-CoV-2 yakomotse mu biremwa by'imbeba.
Ni iyihe nyamaswa yari ubwoko bw'ibanze bwanduriye virusi ku nyamaswa ya mbere, nk'ikinyugunyugu, ku bantu?
Ntituzi ibisubizo by'ibibazo bya mbere n'ibya kabiri, ntituzashobora guhagarika ubwandu mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza, kandi icyorezo gishobora kugaruka igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
