Inkomoko ya zoonotic ya koronavirusi z'abantu
Guhinduka no guhuza n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byatumye koronavirusi (CoVs) n'abanduye muri byo, harimo n'abantu, bihinduka mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bafite virusi z'ubwandu bw'agakoko bagaragaye ko batera indwara yoroheje, urugero nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icya MERS byahinduye uko abantu babonaga virusi z'ubwandu bwa koronavirusi kandi byerekana ukuntu kwandura virusi ya koronavirusi bishobora kwica no kwangiza.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 yongeye gushyira CoVs mu mwanya wa mbere kandi itangaza abantu bose kubera ubwandu bwayo buhanitse n'ubwandu buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu benshi bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, kandi hari abantu benshi bafite uburwayi bwo mu mutwe.
HCoVs nyinshi zakomotse ku ducurama, aho zitagira ubwandu.
Impamvu imwe ni uko hari abantu benshi batemera ko virusi ya coronavirusi ishobora gutera indwara.
Kumenya abarwayi bo mu nyamaswa bifite ingaruka ku burinzi bw'indwara mu bantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire y'abakira CoV mu nyamaswa bushobora gutanga amakuru y'ingenzi ku ndwara ya CoV mu bantu.
Muri iki cyigisho, twerekanye amakuru yose kuri izo HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'aho zavumbuwe, aho zakomotse n'aho zaturutse n'ubwandu bwazo.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ingenzi ni ubwo kugereranya no gutandukanya HCoV zitandukanye duhereye ku kuntu virusi ihinduka n'uko genome isubirana.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) kiri kuvugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibisabwa kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwiza bwo guhinduranya abarwayi n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku buremere bw'indwara na zo zirashyizwe ahagaragara.
Koronavirusi (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'ibyorezo zifite poroteyine nziza, z'impande zombi n'udufishi tw'indwara za RNA.
Izo virusi zifite genome nini cyane hagati ya kilobases 26 na 32 mu virusi za RNA, ziswe "CoVs" kubera imiterere yazo y'ingingo iyo zirebewe mu cyuma kigenzura uturemangingo duto cyane.
Ku bijyanye n'imiterere, CoV zifite genomes zitari zisanzwe zisanzwe zifite gahunda nk'iyo.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome birimo ibice bibiri by'ibisobanuro by'ibanze (ORF1a na ORF1b) bisobanurwa mu bice bibiri by'ibinyabuzima byitwa pp1a na pp1ab.
Izi poroteyine zongera guhinduka zigatanga poroteyine 16 zitari iz'imiterere, zitwa nsp1 kugeza nsp16.
Igice gisigaye cya jenome kirimo ORFs z'indemamubiri z'ingenzi zirimo spike (S), envelope (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine zimwe na zimwe z'inkomoko z'indwara z'ibyorezo na zo zigengwa n'indwara zitandukanye za CoV.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro mu mikoreshereze ya poroteyine, CoVs zashyizwe mu byiciro bine (alphaCoV, betaCoV, gammaCoV na deltaCoV), muri byo betaCoV irimo HCoVs nyinshi kandi igabanyijemo ibyiciro bine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekanye ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo bitanga amakuru y'imiterere y'indwara nyinshi za alphaCoV na betaCoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga amakuru y'indwara nyinshi za gammaCoV na deltaCoV.
Mu myaka ibihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura mu nzitizi z'ubwoko, kandi zimwe zabaye indwara z'ingenzi ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana abantu barindwi banduye koronavirusi (HCoVs).
Muri izo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alphaCoVs.
Ibindi bitanu bya betaCoVs birimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV), coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje, nk'ibicurane bisanzwe na/cyangwa iseseme.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kumenyekana, ni indwara zandura cyane kandi zitera indwara zikomeye mu nzira y'ubuhumekero mu barwayi benshi, kandi zigira amahirwe menshi yo gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ishozi (ARDS) n'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwigaragaje mu bantu barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi bwinshi bwungutse binyuze mu bushakashatsi bwimbitse kuri HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, byombi bitera ibimenyetso byigenga.
Mu by'ukuri, igitekerezo cy'uko kwandura na HCoVs muri rusange nta cyo bitwaye cyakiriwe cyane kugeza igihe icyorezo cya SARS cyatangiriye.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003 ni kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara zangiza cyane muri iki gihe, cyanduje abantu barenga 8.000, kigira igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abantu benshi ku bantu banduye cya 10% gusa.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyatumye kiza mu Karere ka Arabiya, kigafata indi ntera kigakwira isi yose.
HCoV nshya yo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), yaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni yo ituma habaho icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus yo mu 2019 (COVID-19), kimaze guhitana ubuzima bw'abantu barenga 3,120 no kwanduza abantu basaga 91,000 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020.
Umwirondoro uratangiye, kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiri hafi kuza.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zikomoka mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'zoonotic' mu birura, imbeba cyangwa inyamaswa zo mu ngo.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko HCoVs zose zakomotse ku mbeba, aho virusi zisanzwe zisanzwe kandi zitagira ubwandu, ariko zigaragaza amoko anyuranye.
