Gukurikirana inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoVs bitanga icyerekezo cyo gusobanukirwa amateka kamere, imbaraga zituma virusi yimuka n'ibikumira kwimuka kwayo mu zindi bwoko.
Ibi kandi bishobora kuyobora no koroshya ubushakashatsi ku bantu bakingira, abahuza n'abakomeza SARS-CoV-2, bifite ibisobanuro by'ingenzi mu gukumira mu gihe kizaza kwimuka kwa virusi hagati y'ubwoko.
Muri iyi nkuru, turareba uko HCoVs zakomotse ku nyamaswa, uko zinyura mu bwoko bumwe n'ubundi n'uko ziterwa n'ubwandu.
By'umwihariko, twasobanuye kandi tuganira ku ngingo rusange ivuga ko virusi z'ababyeyi ba HCoV zikunze kuba zidakora mu mubiri mu gihe zisanzwe zikorera mu mazi, ariko zikaba zikora mu mubiri nyuma yo kwanduzanya n'izindi.
