Mu myaka ibarirwa muri za mirongo ishize, HCoVs zirindwi zaramenyekanye.
Mu gihe hagiye habaho ubwandu bw'indwara ya HCoV, hari igihe abantu benshi bahura n'indwara ya HCoV.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E bwavumbuwe mu nzira y'ubuhumekero bw'abarwayi banduye ubwandu bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru mu mwaka wa 1966, nyuma buza guhindurirwa imiterere mu mikurire y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha WI-38.
