MERS-CoV yatangiriye mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari waratewe n'umusonga ukabije n'impyiko zidakora neza muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Mu gihe abenshi mu barwayi bemejwe n'abakora ubushakashatsi baturuka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari abanduye mu bihugu by'i Burayi na Tuniziya, kandi bakunze gukwirakwira mu buryo bw'ububanyi n'amahanga.
