Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero buturuka kuri SARS-CoV-2 ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage kandi ko ari icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, abantu 90,053 nibo bamaze kwandura ku isi, aho umubare w'abapfa ku buryo bw'ibanze ku bantu banduye wari 3,4%.
