Ku ruhande rumwe, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibintu bigaragara cyane mu gihe cy'ubwandu bwa HCoVs z'ubwoko bw'abaturage, harimo ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, hari itsinda rito ry'abantu barwaye COVID-19 cyane, nk'abanduye SARS-CoV, nubwo umubare wabo ari muto.
