Mu buryo bw'ibanze, ntibishoboka ko ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo ryatuma inkingo n'imiti igabanya ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2 bidakora vuba.
Icya kabiri, genomeri nini ya RNA muri CoVs ikoresha ubushobozi bw'inyongera mu guhindura genome kugira ngo ihinduke kandi isubire hamwe, bityo ikongera amahirwe yo guhinduka kwa interspecies, bikaba byungura CoV nshya iyo imimerere ibaye myiza.
Ibi byemezwa n'uburyo bwinshi bw'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima n'imikorere yabyo, mu bice bitatu bya nyuma bya genom.
Icya gatatu, CoVs zihindura imiterere mu buryo budasanzwe kandi kenshi mu gihe za RNA zisa n'izisubiramo binyuze mu buryo bwihariye bwo "guhitamo kopi".
Mu mugenzo ukorera nk'igikoresho cyo kuvanga, gusimbuza imirongo bikunze kubaho mu gihe cyo kwandukura RNA ya CoV.
RNA ndende zihuriyeho cyane kandi z'ibice bitandukanye z'ingirabuzimafatizo zishobora kongera kwihuza zigatanga CoV nshya.
Ibipimo bya filijenetike byerekana ko ubusanzwe HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-OC43 zishobora kongera kuvuka, ndetse n'izindi CoV zo mu matungo nka SL-CoV yo mu birura na batCoV-HKU9.
Imikorere ya virusi-umwakira ku bijyanye no kwanduzanya
Usibye ibintu bitatu bya virusi byavuzwe haruguru, ikoranabuhanga rya virusi n'umwakira ni ikindi kintu cy'ingenzi kigira ingaruka ku kwanduzanya.
Aha, SARS-CoV yongeye kwibumbiraho ifatwa nk'urugero rusanzwe, rwagaragaje kandi ibimenyetso by'amahitamo meza mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'ubwoko.
Dushingiye ku isesengura rigereranya SARS-CoVs zatoraguwe mu bantu n'iz'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa civet, SARS-CoV yitezwe guhindurirwa imiterere mu buryo bwihuse mu bantu batandukanye, cyane cyane mu guhinduka kwa DLR ya poroteyine ya S.
Muri rusange, DLR iri kuri poroteyine S ya CoV ikorana n'urwunganira rw'ingirabuzimafatizo kandi ikoroherwa cyane n'igisubizo cy'umurwayi.
Muri SARS-CoV, DLR iri kuri amino acide 318 kugeza 510 mu gice cya S1, gifatanya na ECA2 y'umuntu ndetse n'indwara z'ibyorezo.
DLR ya SARS-CoV ishobora kumenya ibinyamubiri bitandukanye bifite ECA2 harimo udusimba, ibinyamanswa, imbeba n'imbwa z'ingore, bityo bikaba byatuma virusi ishobora kwanduzanya.
Mu by'ukuri, byagaragariye ko ibisigisigi bitandatu by'amino acide ari byo byonyine bitandukanye n'ibisigazwa bya virusi y'umuntu n'iy'inyoni mu DLR, kandi bine muri byo biri mu buryo bwo guhuza receptor kugira ngo bihuze na receptor ya ECA2.
SARS-CoV yo mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa civet ifite impinduka za K479N na S487T muri DLR yayo, zishobora kongera ubushobozi bwa poroteyine ya spike bwo gukorana n'indwara ya ECA2 mu bantu.
Mu yandi magambo, ibyo bisimbuzo byombi bya amino acide bishobora kuba ingenzi mu guhinduranya virusi mu bantu.
Birakwiriye ko tumenya ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano n'iyo virusi.
Itandukaniro ry'ibice 30% hagati ya SARS-CoV-2 na SARS-CoV mu gice cya S1 cya poroteyine S ryumvikanisha ko ubushobozi bwo guhuza poroteyine S na ECA2 y'umuntu bushobora kuba bwarahindutse.
Mu by'ukuri, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe hakoreshejwe mikorosikopi ya elegitoronike bugaragaza ko ubwo bufatanye bukomeye inshuro 10 kugeza kuri 20 kurusha ubwo hagati ya ECA2 y'umuntu na poroteyine S ya SARS-CoV.
Nanone kandi, bizaba ari ingirakamaro kumenya niba hari indi korereceptor ishobora gukenerwa mu guhererekanya SARS-CoV-2.
Igishishikaje ni uko HCoV-NL63 nayo ifitanye isano na ECA2, ariko ifitanye isano n'igice cy'indwara ya S.
Hariho izindi mpumyi nyinshi za HCoV, nka aminopeptidase N ya HCoV-229E na 9-O-acetyl sialic acid ya HCoV-OC43.
Zishobora kandi kuba zifite uruhare mu gutuma izo virusi zifata neza abantu nyuma yo guhererekanywa hagati y'ubwoko bwazo n'inyamaswa.
Uretse abakira utwo ducurama, ingaruka z'ubwandu bw'udukoko twitwa HCoVs hagati y'ubwoko na zo zigengwa n'ibindi bintu bibangamira no gushingira ku nyamaswa.
Ibi bituma abantu benshi batandura cyane, cyane cyane mu gihe hari abantu bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona.
HCoVs zigomba kwigarurira ibintu bituma umuntu ahorana n'inyamaswa kandi zikongeraho ibintu bituma inyamaswa zidakomeza kuba mu nyamaswa kugira ngo zigere ku bantu.
Muri ubwo buryo, ibintu bigena ingirabuzimafatizo muri aka gace gakomeye k'imikoranire ya virusi n'umwakiriye biracyakeneye kumenyekana no gusobanurwa.
Gushakisha nta kwibeshya ku rwego rwa genom ku bijyanye n'ubwirinzi n'impamvu zituma SARS-CoV-2 idashobora kwandura hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rigezweho rya CRISPR bishobora gutanga umusaruro mwiza.
Gucika kwa HCoVs nshya: gusubira ku murongo wa mbere
Impamvu ya mbere ni uko hari abantu benshi bafite ibyago byo kwandura virusi z'ubwoko butandukanye.
Muri ubwo buryo, CoVs zo mu birura zikora nk'ikigega cy'imiterere ya HCoVs.
Byongeye kandi, ihinduka ry'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo mu buryo bwihuse no kongera guhuriza hamwe ibinyabuzima nabyo bituma HCoV ihinduka kandi ni intambwe ebyiri z'ingenzi muri ubu buryo.
Urugero, kubona cyangwa gutakaza ingirabuzima fatizo nshya z'indwara ya virusi bishobora guhindura cyane ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Mu maporoteyine y'inyongera ya SARS-CoV, ORF8 bivugwa ko ari ingenzi mu kuyigirira abantu, kuko virusi z'ikinyugunyugu zifitanye isano na SARS-CoV zatoranyijwe, ariko zasanze zigena poroteyine zitandukanye za ORF8.
Ikintu cy'ingenzi cyatumye SARS-CoVs itarandura nucleotide 29 cyavumbuwe mu bwoko bw'indwara z'ibyorezo bya mbere.
Gucika bigabanya ORF8 mu ORF8a na ORF8b, kandi byemezwa ko ari ihinduka ry'imiterere rituma habaho guhinduranya abarwayi.
Byongeye kandi, SARS-CoV ifite amateka ashoboka yo kongera kwibumbira mu bwoko bwa alphaCoVs na gammaCoVs, aho umubare munini w'uturere duto twongera kwibumbira twamenyekanye muri RNA polymerase ishingiye kuri RNA.
Ahantu ha kabiri habonetse ni muri nsp9, muri nsp10 hafi ya yose, no mu bice bya nsp14.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, byagaragaye ko icyorezo cya MERS-CoV cyabayeho mu buryo bwo kongera guhuriza hamwe ibinyabuzima byo mu moko atandukanye, bikaba byarabaye mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa camédaires zo muri Arabie Saoudite.
Uretse SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, habayeho kongera kwihuza no ku zindi HCoV, aho HCoVs zisubirana n'izindi CoV zo mu matungo mu maraso yazo adafite imiterere.
Ikindi kigomba kubwirwa abantu ni uko amahitamo y'abantu ashobora gutuma habaho impinduka mu bwoko bwa virusi, zishobora guturuka ku kugabanya ingufu zo gutoranya virusi, nk'iz'abasirikare b'umubiri.
Urugero rw'ingaruka nk'izi ni ukubura ORF4 ndende mu bwoko bw'ibanze bwa HCoV-229E, bitewe no gusesa nucléotide ebyiri.
Mu gihe ORF4 idafite icyo ihuriyeho ishobora kugaragara muri virusi z'ingore n'ingore zifitanye isano na HCoV-229E, alphaCoV ya alpaca igaragaza ko ifite nucleotide imwe gusa, bigatuma habaho impinduka mu mashusho.
Icya nyuma ariko cy'ingenzi, iterambere rya HCoV nshya kandi riterwa n'ibibazo byo gutoranya mu bantu bazirinda.
Nta bimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso byoroheje byigaragaza mu ducurama igihe twanduye CoVs, byerekana ko CoVs n'uducurama byisungaga bimwe.
Birashoboka ko udusimba twemewe na CoVs mu buryo bw'umubiri no mu mubiri.
Urugero, amakosa mu gutuma udukoko dukunda kurwara mu maraso dufasha mu kugabanya indwara ziterwa na CoV.
Byongeye kandi, ibikorwa by'utugingo tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'Natural killer cells' mu ducurama birahagarikwa kubera ko utwo tugingo tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'Natural killer cells' (NKG2/CD94) tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'Natural killer cells' (NTCs) twemewe, kandi tukaba tudafite ubushobozi bwo kugaragaza neza imikorere y'uduporoporozi tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'Class I' (Class I) tw'uduporoporozi tw'inyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa 'Main histocompatibility complex').
Byongeye kandi, urugero rwagutse rw'ubwoko bwa ogisijeni (ERO) buturuka ku mikorere ya metabolic iri hejuru mu mibu, rushobora kugabanya uburyo CoV ikwirakwira kandi rugatuma isuzumwa na exorribonuclease, bityo bigatuma habaho igitutu cyo guhitamo uko virusi z'ubwandu bukabije zishobora kuvuka igihe zashyizwe mu nyamaswa nshya.
Hari kandi uburyo bwo kuvura indwara z'ubwoko bushya bwa CoV, bushobora kwiyongera bitewe no kongera kwihuza, bigatuma haboneka poroteyine nshya cyangwa imiterere ya poroteyine kugira ngo umuntu ahinduke.
Ku bw'ibyo, si ibintu byapfuye kubaho gutya gusa kuko mu myaka 20 ishize hagiye haboneka izindi HCoV eshatu.
CoVs ntabwo ziterwa n'indwara, cyangwa ziteza ibimenyetso byoroheje mu bantu bazikomoraho, nk'imbeba n'ingamiya.
Zisubiramo cyane zitagaragaje ko umubiri w'umuntu ufite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara.
Muri iyi nyandiko harimo ibisobanuro ku bijyanye no kuvumbura abanduye batagira ibimenyetso n'impamvu y'ubwandu bukomeye mu bantu.
Ibimenyetso bikomeye biterwa ahanini n'uko umubiri utera cyane kandi ikinyabutabire cy'umubiri kikagira imbaraga nyinshi, aho uko umubiri urushaho kugira imbaraga, ari na ko ibihaha byongera kwangirika.
Ku rundi ruhande, ku bantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso, ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bwahagaritswe ku buryo nta CoV ikomeza kwigaragaza.
Ubwo buryo bwo guhagarika ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bushobora kugira ingaruka nziza mu buvuzi bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Igisubizo cya Interferon ni gikomeye cyane mu miyonjora.
Ku bw'ibyo, guterwa interferon y'ubwoko bwa I mu ntangiriro y'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu bigomba kugira akamaro.
Ikindi ni uko mu mibuvu nta kintu na kimwe cy'ingenzi kiboneka mu byo bita NLRP3.
Dukurikije iyo mitekerereze, kubuza NLRP3 inflamasome na MCC950 bishobora kuba ingirakamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
SARS-CoV-2 yavuye mu bintu bimwe na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Mu gihe byabonetse ko betaCoV y'imbeba ifite 95% by'ubwoko bwa nucleotide ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV, hari CoV y'imbeba ifite 96% by'ubwoko bwa nucleotide ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo byagiye bigaragara ko udukoko two mu bwoko bwa civette n'utundi dukoko two ku masoko dufite virusi zisa na SARS-CoV, nta bakiriya ba SARS-CoV-2 bamenyekanye.
Habonetse betaCoVs z'ibinyamanswa, zifite ubukana bukomeye na SARS-CoV-2, byerekana ko ibinyamanswa bishobora kuba kimwe mu byitwa ko bifite ubwandu bw'ibinyamanswa, cyangwa se betaCoVs z'ibinyamanswa zishobora gutanga ibice by'imiterere y'igihimba cya nyuma cya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibibazo bikomeje kubazwa, nta gihamya igaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 yakorewe ku bushake cyangwa se mu buryo bw'impanuka.
CoVs zongeye kugarukwaho cyane ku isi kubera icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 giherutse kwaduka.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe n'ibindi nyamaswa byahinduye cyane uko tubona akamaro k'inkomoko ya zoonotic n'ibikoresho byazo mu bantu.
Ibihamya byinshi bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 bikomoka ku bamotari kandi ko byandura ku bantu binyuze mu bantu bazima.
Kubera ko ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV bwatangiriye mu bantu bahuriye n'inyamaswa zo mu masoko, gufunga amasoko y'inyamaswa z'inzitane no kuzica muri ayo masoko byari gutuma icyorezo cya SARS gihagarara.
Hakurikijwe imyumvire imwe, ingona zagombye kuvanwa ku masoko y'amazi kugira ngo zirinde ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibinyamaswa, bitewe n'uko habonetse ubwoko bwinshi bwa betaCoVs z'ingona zifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV-2.
Icyakora, mu bushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kizaza, biracyakenewe ko hamenyekana niba SARS-CoV-2 yandura ku bantu binyuze mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin n'izindi nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa mameloni, n'uburyo yandura.
Ku rundi ruhande, MERS-CoV imaze igihe kirekire mu nyamaswa zo mu bwoko bwa camédaires.
Izo ngamiya zikora nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gutwara abantu, kandi ni isoko y'ingenzi y'inyama, amata, uruhu n'ubwoya ku baturage baho.
Zirakwirakwijwe cyane mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati no muri Afurika.
Ku bw'ibyo, ntibishoboka gutamba ingamiya zose mu rwego rwo kurwanya MERS, nk'uko byakozwe mu masoko y'inyamaswa mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2.
Kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwo guhashya ibyorezo bya MERS, hakwiye gushyirwaho uburyo bufatika bwo gukora inkingo z'indwara ya MERS-CoV ku ngamiya, hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa byo kugenzura ubwandu.
Kubera ko tutashobora kurandura izo virusi, hari ubundi bwoko bushya bw'iyo virusi bushobora kwaduka bugateza ibyorezo.
Hari ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoVs ziterwa n'inyamaswa zikunda gukwirakwira mu ishyamba.
By'umwihariko, CoV z'imbeba zishobora kwanduza inyamaswa zitandukanye cyane.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kubona ko izo virusi zoonotic zishobora kwiyongera no kongera kwibumbira hamwe, bigatuma habaho izindi virusi zo mu bwoko bwa CoV zishobora kwanduza no kwica abantu mu gihe kizaza.
Umuco wo kurya inyamaswa zo mu gasozi mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa ugomba gucibwa kugira ngo abantu n'inyamaswa badakomeza guhura.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS, MERS na COVID-19, hakenewe uburyo bwiza bwo kwitegura no gusubiza.
Mu by'ukuri, hari virusi nyinshi zimaze igihe kirekire ku isi.
Ziguma mu bigega byazo bisanzwe kugeza igihe habonetse uburyo bwo kwimukira mu zindi nyamaswa.
Nubwo udusimba dufite ibintu byinshi bituma virusi ikwirakwira, amahirwe yo guhura n'udusimba n'utundi dukoko two mu gasozi ashobora kugabanuka cyane iyo abantu bigishijwe kutayirwara.
Gukurikirana mu binyabuzima birakenewe kugira ngo dusobanukirwe neza ibidukikije bya CoV n'ibinyabuzima byazo, bizadufasha kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibyorezo mu gihe kizaza.
Mu gusoza, uburyo bwiza bwo kwirinda indwara y'ibimera ni ukubuza abantu kujya ahantu h'ibidukikije hatangirwa virusi z'ibimera.
Ibice byinshi by'ikibazo cy'inkomoko ya SARS-CoV-2 yaturutse ku nyamaswa biracyari ibura.
Mbere na mbere, niba udusimba two mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 twandurira virusi ya kera mu ducurama, ni ngombwa kumenya imimerere udusimba n'uducurama bishobora kubamo mu buryo bumwe.
Icya kabiri, niba udusimba tugira uruhare rugaragara mu kwanduzanya n'abantu, uburyo abantu bagirana imibonano n'udusimba bugomba gusuzumwa.
Icya gatatu, niba inyamaswa y'inkazi ya gatatu ifite uruhare rw'umucumbitsi nyakuri, uburyo ikorana n'ubwoko butandukanye, harimo abantu, udusimba n'utunyoni, bugomba gusobanurwa.
Amaherezo, kubera ko inyamaswa nyinshi zirya ibinyamubiri, harimo n'amatungo yo mu ngo, zishobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2, hakwiye gukorwa ubugenzuzi n'igerageza ry'ubwandu.
Niba ari uruhu, ingunzu cyangwa indi nyamaswa, byitezwe ko SARS-CoV-2 cyangwa virusi z'ababyeyi zayo zimeze kimwe, zizagaragara mu bantu bazitera mu gihe kiri imbere.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeje muri aka gace buzasobanura inzira SARS-CoV-2 yanyuzemo mu nyamaswa, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku gukumira no kugenzura COVID-19 mu bantu.
Hakenewe kuvugurura ibipimo byo gusuzuma "umuntu ukekwaho" na "umuntu wemejwe" COVID-19
Ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ryacu ryasohoye igitabo cy'amabwiriza yihuse yo gusuzuma no kuvura ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV). Icyo gitabo cyerekana ubunararibonye bwacu kandi ni urugero rwiza rwo kurwanya iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Icyakora, indwara ya koronavirusi yo mu mwaka wa 2019 (COVID-19) ni nshya. Ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi no mu buvuzi; ku bw'ibyo, uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma no kuyivura na bwo burajya buvugururwa.
Muri iyi baruwa, dusubiza igitekerezo cyatanzwe ku muyobozi wacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gusuzuma "uburwayi bukekwaho" n'"uburwayi bwemejwe" nk'uko biri mu mabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Inyandiko ya karindwi) yasohowe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Ubushinwa.
Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyitwa coronavirus 2019 disease (COVID-19), kandi virusi yitwa coronavirus 2 y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize COVID-19 mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye igitabo cyihuse cy'amabwiriza cyasohotse kuri interineti mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare ku ya 6 Gashyantare 2020.
Yateje abantu benshi cyane amatsiko kuva yashyirwa ahagaragara.
Icyakora, wibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya. Ubumenyi n'ubumenyi dufite bigenda byiyongera bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi no mu buvuzi; ku bw'ibyo, uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma no kuyivura na bwo burajya buvugururwa.
Urugero, Amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yasohowe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abaturage y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) kuva ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, afite inyandiko zirindwi z'igihe cyose, zimwe muri zo zarahindutse cyane.
Ubuyobozi bwacu bwahawe igitekerezo na Zhou et al., watanze igitekerezo cy'amanota yoroheje ashingiye ku buhanga bwe mu buvuzi.
Iki gikorwa cyongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku muyoboro wacu kandi kandi gitanga ibisobanuro by'ingirakamaro kuri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Turashimira umurimo w'ingenzi wakoze kandi turagushimira.
Ariko kandi, ibyo bakoze na byo bikeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya agenga icyorezo cya COVID-19 (igitabo cya karindwi cy'igerageza) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'igazeti ya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu yemererwe ko yanduye, bisaba ko habaho kimwe mu bintu by'amateka y'indwara hamwe n'ibintu bibiri by'ibintu by'uburwayi kugira ngo haboneke isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa se bisaba ko habaho ibintu bitatu by'ibintu by'uburwayi mu gihe nta mateka y'uburwayi asobanutse:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu duce duturanye cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bakoze ikizamini cya nucleic acid bakemeza); (3) amateka y'abamenyanye n'abarwayi barwaye umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu duce duturanye cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abamenyanye n'itsinda ry'abantu banduye (barengeje cyangwa bangana n'abantu babiri banduye umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu byumweru 2 mu duce duto, nk'inzu, ibiro, ishuri n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso byo kwifashisha amashusho mu gupima ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'amaraso yera yose ugaragaza umubare usanzwe, ugabanutse cyangwa ugabanutse w'utugingo ngengabuzima mu gihe cy'ibimenyetso.
Gushakisha umuntu wemejwe ko arwaye bigomba gushingira ku kuba ahamwa n'ibi bikurikira: (1) ibipimo bya PCR byerekana ko SARS-CoV-2 ari yo ndwara ya mbere; (2) gukorakoranya genome yose ya virusi igaragaza ko hari ibintu byinshi bihuza na koronavirusi nshya; (3) kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite IgM na IgG mu isuzuma ry'amaraso; cyangwa se kuba hari igisubizo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 igaragaza ko IgG yaranduye cyangwa se ko ifite indwara y'ibicurane by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yavuye ku ndwara ya mbere ikajya ku ndwara ya mbere cyangwa se ko ifite indwara y'ibicurane ya mbere irenze iya mbere.
Twavuga ko isuzuma rya PCR ry'igihe nyacyo ku aside ya nucleic mu maraso cyangwa mu nzira y'ubuhumekero ryongerewe ku nshuro ya kabiri n'iya gatatu (ku ya 18 na 22 Mutarama 2020, ku buryo buhuriranye).
Kumenya indwara mu cyiciro cy'amaraso byongerewe ku gice cya kane n'icya gatanu (ku ya 27 Mutarama 2020 no ku ya 8 Gashyantare 2020, ku buryo buhuriranye), kandi ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerewe ku gice cya karindwi.
Izi mpinduka zishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi mu gushakisha igikoresho cyiza cyo gupima aside ya nucleic ku bipimo bya vuba no ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero, harimo no gufata ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye ubushobozi bwo kubona ibipimo bitandukanye kandi bifasha gutanga umusaruro mwiza w'abasirikare b'umubiri ku bipimo byemejwe.
Ikindi kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwita ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso n'abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, uruhu rwa Zhou et al. rugomba kuvugururwa kuko ruvuga ko umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi ari "ubw'ibyago bike".
Iyi gahunda yo gutanga amanota ikeneye kandi kwemezwa mu bushakashatsi n'imikorere y'ivuriro.
Mu gusoza, turategereje ko haboneka ibindi bimenyetso by'imvaho kandi turasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Ku bijyanye no gusuzuma "ubwandu bukekwa" n'"ubwandu bwemejwe", turasaba ko wakurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byanyu.
Abakozi bacu bazajya basubiramo amakuru mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo badufashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko abantu batanu bishwe na COVID-19, umubare munini ku munsi
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virusi.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe iby'indwara, kugenzura no gukora ubushakashatsi (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abamaze kwemezwa ko banduye harimo 114 bari barwaye n'abandi 33 bakize bari mu rugo.
Abantu 17 bose hamwe bapfuye.
Mu makuru yo kuri interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Dr. Meerjady Sabrina Flora, yavuze ko abapfuye barimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Meerjady abivuga, babiri muri abo bantu bari bafite imyaka isaga 60, babiri bari bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 51 na 60, naho umwe yari afite imyaka iri hagati ya 41 na 50.
Yavuze kandi ko babiri mu bishwe bari baturutse i Dhaka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe.
Umukozi w'ibitaro yabwiye Anadolu Agency, ikigo cy'amakuru cyo muri ako gace ko umwe mu bapfuye ari Jalal Saifur Rahman, umuyobozi wa Komisiyo ya Bengali yo kurwanya ruswa, wavurirwaga mu bitaro bya Kuwait Maitree.
Ku wa Gatandatu, mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri videwo, Minisitiri w'ubwikorezi bw'imihanda n'ibiraro Obaidul Quader yavuze ko imodoka zitwara abagenzi zizamara igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe mbere, kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Uru rugendo rw'ingendo mu modoka z'abantu bose rwatangiye ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, kandi rwari ruteganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Gucuruza ibintu by'ingenzi (imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa) byari byarabyemerewe.
Abantu ba mbere banduye COVID-19 muri Bangladesh banditswe ku ya 8 Werurwe, ku bantu babiri bari bavuye mu Butaliyani, ndetse n'umugore wa umwe muri bo.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, bose uko ari batatu bari bamaze koroherwa.
SARS-CoV-2 irenga miliyoni y'ubwandu ku isi
Ku wa Kane, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ku isi urenga miliyoni, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ibikoresho bya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Nibura abantu ibihumbi 52 bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19, indwara iterwa na coronavirus.
Uyu munsi w'ingenzi waje ku munsi umwe na Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus na Zambia yabonye urupfu rwa mbere rw'umuntu ufitanye isano na virusi.
Koreya ya Ruguru yatangaje ko kugeza ku wa Kane, yari kimwe mu bihugu bike byari bisigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Kugeza ejo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko abantu 1,051,635 banduye, harimo 79,332 mu masaha 24 yabanjirije saa kumi z'ijoro z'i Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC) ku ya 4 Mata.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, habonetse abarwayi ba coronavirus basaga 244.000, bahitanye abantu bagera ku 5.900.
CBS News yatangaje ko hari abantu barenga 1.000 bapfuye muri Amerika bishwe n'indwara ya coronavirus ku wa Gatatu, ivuga ko ibi byavuye muri Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ku wa Kane, Meya wa Moscou Sergei Sobyanin yongeyeho ko umujyi wose ufunze kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko Abanyarwanda bazakomeza guhembwa batavuye ku kazi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Portugal yatoye kongera iminsi 15 ku bihe by'ibiza by'igihugu.
Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo gutaha ku munsi wose mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina, aho mbere yari kuva saa tatu kugeza saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo.
Thailand irateganya gushyiraho amasaha yo gutaha kuva saa kumi z'ijoro kugeza saa yine za mu gitondo
Guverineri wa Ohio, Mike DeWine, yatangaje ko leta yongereye amasaha yo kuguma mu rugo kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku gicuruzwa
Ku mugoroba wo ku wa Gatandatu no ku Cyumweru, amaduka yo muri Ositaraliya yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije amategeko agenga kugura impapuro z'isuku, ku buryo buri mudandazo wabaga ufite amakarito abiri n'akarato kamwe.
Ku wa mbere, ALDI nayo yashyizeho umupaka w'igiciro.
Ibyo bihano byatangajwe n'ubutumwa mu mabaruwa no ku mbuga za Facebook z'izo mbuga.
Kubera gutinya COVID-19, abaguzi bavugaga ko bari kubikora mu gihe byaba ngombwa ko bajya mu kato.
Ku wa Gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije ibicuruzwa by'impapuro z'isuku ku isoko ku ifatabuguzi rimwe ku icyifuzo.
Ayo mahinduka yaje nyuma y'ikumira ry'amapaji ane ku gicuruzwa ryashyizweho na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe, ku rutonde.
Coles mu itangazo ryayo ryo ku ya 8 Werurwe, yatangaje ko nubwo hari ibigo bine by'ibikoresho, "amaduka menshi akomeje kubura ibicuruzwa mu gihe kitarenze isaha nyuma yo gutangwa" maze yita ko ibyifuzo "bitigeze bibaho", mu gihe ALDI yo yabise "bitunguranye" mu butumwa kuri Facebook ku wa Kabiri.
Ubucuruzi bwagaragaje "ukwiyongera gukomeye" mu cyumweru gishize, nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths.
Ubucuruzi bwa Costco muri Canberra nabwo bwagabanyije umubare w'ibikoresho byemewe ku bipimo bibiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo barusheho kugabanya ubukene, Coles yasabye ibicuruzwa byinshi ku bakiriya kandi yongera umubare w'ibikoresho, Woolworths yasabye ibicuruzwa by'inyongera, mu gihe ALDI yatangaga ibicuruzwa by'inyongera biteganyijwe ku wa gatatu.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'akarere agenga uko bakoresha imodoka batwara ibicuruzwa ababuza kubikora.
Yiteze ibiciro byo gukora biri hejuru, kuko abaguzi bagerageza guhaza ibyifuzo, kandi n'ibicuruzwa bike.
Ku wa kabiri, ALDI yatangaje ko nyuma yo gufungura hakiri kare ibicuruzwa, amaduka amwe na amwe atazashobora gukora igitaramo cyo ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru yo ku rubuga rwa News.com.au, Dr. Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi muri kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka ashyira ibicuruzwa mu bubiko buri mugoroba.
Yashimangiye ko impapuro z'isuku ari ikintu kinini gifite umubare muto w'ibikoresho, kandi iyo zimaze gufungurwa, zisigara zitagira aho zikorera, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumva ko zibuze.
Coles na Woolworths bafite igitekerezo [cy'uko] niba hari ibintu byinshi ku mbuga, niba ibintu nk'impapuro z'isuku n'imiti yica udukoko bishobora [gucuruzwa] kandi bikaba biriyo mu bwinshi, ushobora kugabanya ubwoba, Russel Zimmerman yabwiye ABC News.
Uruganda rukora impapuro z'isuku zisubiwemo rwitwa Who Gives a Crap, rwatangaje ko ku wa gatatu w'iki cyumweru rwari rugiye kurangira.
Kimberly-Clark, ikora impapuro z'isuku za Kleenex, na Solaris Paper, ikora Sorbent, byashimangiye ko bari gukora amasaha 24 ku munsi, iminsi 7 mu cyumweru kugira ngo bakomeze kubona ibicuruzwa, nk'uko bivugwa na News.com.au.
Urubuga rw'imicungire y'imitungo domain.com rwatangaje ko bamwe mu bacuruzi b'imitungo bari guha impapuro z'isuku ku buntu aba mbere mu gutanga isoko muri Melbourne, ubwo hageragezwaga imicungire y'imitungo ku buntu n'abaguzi bari mu kiruhuko cy'izabukuru mu mpera z'icyumweru cy'umunsi w'akazi.
Ku wa Kane, ikinyamakuru cyitwa NT News, cyandikirwaga buri munsi i Darwin, cyashyizemo ingingo y'amapaji umunani yari igenewe gutemwa no gukoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Mu mizo ya mbere, amaduka yari afite impungenge zo gushyiraho amategeko, nk'uko byavuzwe na ABC Australia ku ya 3 Werurwe aho yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ibyo guhaha.
Russell Zimmerman yongeyeho ko ibindi bikoresho na byo bikenewe cyane, nk'udupfukamunwa, imiti yica udukoko, ibyokurya bikonjesha, isabune zo gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Nk'uko byari bimeze muri Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nijoro, isoko ryo mu Bwongereza ryifashisha imbuga nkoranyambaga rya Ocado ryashyizeho imipaka ku bicuruzwa by'impapuro z'isuku za Andres, ku buryo zari zigizwe n'udupaki tubiri tw'imikufi 12.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19  indwara iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2  ari icyorezo.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku rugero rw'ikwirakwira ry'indwara, aho kwerekeza ku buryo indwara runaka iteje akaga, OMS yashimangiye ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza guverinoma kugira icyo zikora:
Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo.
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko ibihugu bigomba kuba bifite ubushobozi bwo gutahura, gupima, kuvura, gushyira abantu mu kato, gukurikira no guhuza abaturage kugira ngo bagire icyo bakora.
Dufite impungenge nyinshi ku bijyanye n'ubukana n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, ndetse n'ukuntu abantu batabikora.
Dukurikije uko Dr. Tom Frieden, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzihagarika, yabivuze, ni icyorezo "kitigeze kibaho mbere hose".
Mu magambo yatangajwe na CNN mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, yavuze ko "uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigenzurwa kuva zitangira kugeza ku ikwirakwira ry'isi yose".
Ghebreyesus yavuze ko na we yari afite imyumvire nk'iyo, avuga ko "atari yarigeze abona icyorezo cyatangijwe na coronavirus".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi nta cyorezo twigeze tubona gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iki cyorezo gishya gikurikiye icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage gihangayikishije amahanga yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Ibitera Mbonera n'Indwara Zandura, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko icyo cyorezo "mu by'ukuri kizarushaho kuba kibi".
Ku wa Kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari nibura abantu 126.000 banduye COVID-19, hapfa abantu barenga 4.600.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus 201920 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa na coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Kuboza 2019, gitangazwa nk'icyorezo mpuzamahanga ku isi ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020, kandi gitangazwa nk'icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1,61 banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kumenyekana mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, hapfa abagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Umubare w'abapfa mu Bushinwa ugereranywa na 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose ugera kuri 13,04% muri Algeria na 0,08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora guterwa n'indwara y'ibihaha n'indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba.
Igihe kuva umuntu ahumanyijwe kugeza igihe ibimenyetso bitangiriye ni iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri 14.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wihariye wa virusi uraboneka.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvurwa ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso n'ubufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa harimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa mu gihe ukoroye, kugendera kure abantu no kugenzura no gushyira mu kato abantu bakekwaho ubwandu.
Abategetsi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, gushyira abantu mu kato, amasaha yo gutaha, kugenzura ibyago ku kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Icyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye mu mibereho y'abaturage n'ubukungu ku isi, ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'umuco birasubikwa cyangwa birahagarikwa, kandi hakunze kubaho ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa, byatewe n'ibicuruzwa byatewe n'ubwoba.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa ku rwego rw'akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99,4% ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yakwirakwiriye kuri interineti, kandi habayeho ibikorwa by'ivangura n'ubwugarizi ku bantu b'Abashinwa, abantu bakomoka mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo ashyira Uburasirazuba bwa Aziya n'abandi baturutse mu duce dufite abantu benshi banduye iyi virus.
Kubera kugabanya ingendo no gufunga inganda zikomeye, habayeho kugabanuka kw'ibyuka bihumanya ikirere no kugabanya imyuka ihumanya ikirere.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari abantu benshi banduye indwara y'ibicurane ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, kandi iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Byinshi mu bibazo by'ubwandu byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'umusaruro w'inyanja rya Huanan, bityo virusi ikaba ishobora kuba yaturutse ku nyamaswa.
Virusi iteza iki cyorezo ni SARS-CoV-2, virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifitanye isano ya hafi na koronavirusi y'ikiburindi, ingona na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'iyi ndwara yarwaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 kandi nta sano bigaragara yari afitanye n'itsinda ry'abantu bari mu isoko ry'ibinyampeke.
Mu itsinda rya mbere ry'abatangajwe mu Ukuboza 2019, bibiri bya gatatu byabonetse ko bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo itari yemewe yo mu kinyamakuru cya South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko hari umuntu umwe wari ufite imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, wari waranduye ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, ushobora kuba ari we wa mbere. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko kubera ko ubwandu bushya bwatangajwe bwagabanutse mu Bushinwa ariko bukaza kwiyongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Hashobora kubaho kubura amakuru y'ibyago, cyane cyane mu bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, hari abantu bake cyane bari bamaze kwandura mu rubyiruko ruri munsi y'imyaka 19, bangana na 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Umushakashatsi ukomeye mu bya siyansi mu Bwongereza, Patrick Vallance, yavuze ko 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere y'uko ubwirinzi bw'ingurube bukora.
Ibibazo byerekeza ku mubare w'abantu bapimwe bagasanga bafite COVID-19 kandi bagaragayeho ibimenyetso bifatika.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyaragejeje abantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi ibihugu byinshi byari bifite politiki zemewe yo kudapima abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa, urugero nka Italiya, U Buholandi, Esipanye n'Ubusuwisi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, abantu bagera kuri 86% banduye COVID-19 batari barigeze bamenyekana, kandi ko abo bantu banduye mu buryo butanditse ari bo bateje 79% by'abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warutaga cyane umubare w'abamaze kwandura.
Ibipimo bya mbere by'umubare w'ibanze w'abandura (R0) kuri COVID-19 byari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara bwagaragaje ko ishobora kuba 5.7.
Abantu benshi barwaye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku batazakira, igihe kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugeza bapfuye kiri hagati y'iminsi 6 na 41, aho iminsi 14 ari yo ikunze kugaragara.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 bamaze gupfa bazize COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, abagera kuri 80% by'abapfuye bari bafite imyaka 60 kuzamura, naho 75% bari bafite uburwayi bw'umutima n'igisukari. Umubare w'abapfuye bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 ubusanzwe ni abantu bapfuye basanzwemo COVID, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Umubare nyawo w'abahitanywe na COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane, kuko ushobora kuba utarimo abantu bapfuye batakoze ikizamini, urugero nk'abapfuye bari mu ngo zabo, mu bigo byita ku bageze mu za bukuru n'ibindi.
Ibipimo by'igice by'Ubutaliyani byagaragaje ko umubare w'abamaze gupfa muri iki cyorezo warenze umubare w'abamaze gupfa bishwe na COVID ku buryo bungana n'incuro 4-5.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abishwe ku mugaragaro] utavugwaho byinshi", amagambo ashyigikiwe n'amakuru y'ibihe bidasanzwe byo kubura amakuru muri Amerika. Uku kubura amakuru akenshi bibaho mu ndwara z'ibyorezo, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube H1N1 mu 2009. Urupfu rwa mbere rwemejwe rwabereye i Wuhan ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa yabonywe ku ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya aboneka mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'Ubushinwa, abantu barenga icumi na babiri bari bamaze gupfa muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu n'uturere birenga mirongo ine byari byatangaje ko abantu bapfuye, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica. Hari ibipimo bitandukanye bikunze gukoreshwa mu gupima umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi biganzwa n'umubare w'ibipimo, ubwiza bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe kuva icyorezo cyatangira, n'ibintu biranga abaturage, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange. Umubare w'abapfa ugereranya umubare w'abapfa ugabanyijwe n'umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Dushingiye ku mibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins, umubare w'abapfa ku isi yose ni 6,0% (97.039/1.617.204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare uratandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'abapfa yavuye kuri 17,3% (mu bantu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso hagati ya tariki ya 1 na 10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0,7% (mu bantu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso nyuma ya tariki ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'urupfu (CFR), kigereranya igipimo cy'abantu basanganywe indwara bapfa bazize indwara, n'igipimo cy'urupfu rw'ubwandu (IFR), kigereranya igipimo cy'abanduye (basanganywe n'abatarasanganywe) bapfa bazize indwara.
Izi mibare ntabwo zihoraho mu gihe kandi zikurikirana umubare runaka w'abantu banduye binyuze mu gukemura ikibazo.
Hari intiti zagerageje kubara iyo mibare ku bantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso, gitekereza ko ubusanzwe igipimo cy'ubwandu buhitana abantu benshi mu gihe cy'icyorezo kiri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Igitekerezo cyo hejuru cy'icyo cyiciro gihuje n'ibyavuye mu igerageza rya mbere rya COVID-19 mu Budage n'inyigo y'ibarurishamibare yasuzumye ingaruka z'ibigeragezo ku bitekerezo bya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo kwiyongera n'igihe kirekire cyane cy'icyo cyorezo ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora guhinduka bitewe n'aho kiri.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Pennsylvania, yavuze ko "iyo indwara zanduye zidakoreshejwe neza, akenshi zigera ku ndunduro yazo, hanyuma zikagenda zigabanuka igihe nta bandi bantu bafite ubushobozi bwo kuzirwanya.
Ariko kandi, gukora igishushanyo mbonera gihuje n'igihe cy'aho ibyo bizaba bigeze, biragoye cyane".
Umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubuvuzi muri guverinoma y'Ubushinwa, Zhong Nanshan, yavuze ko "bishobora kurangira muri Kamena" ibihugu byose bikomeje gukurikiza inama za OMS ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere i Londres, yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "ishobora gukomeza gukwirakwira mu gihe cy'umwaka cyangwa ibiri".
Nk'uko bivugwa n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Imperial College, bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson, kwirinda abantu no gufata izindi ngamba bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (hashobora kuba mu mezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko iyi koronavirusi idashobora kuzashira burundu kuko yandura cyane" kandi "ishobora kuba indwara y'igihe runaka, igaruka buri mwaka".
Uburemere bw'ingaruka z'iki cyorezo buzaba bushingiye ku bushobozi bw'umubiri n'ubw'ubwoko bw'indwara.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu bayanduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro (88%) n'ikinya (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo umunaniro, guhumeka (kuvirirana mu mwuka), kubura ibyiyumvo byo guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, kubabara kw'amagufa n'ibice by'umubiri, kubabara mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira ubwoba, gusuka, kuvira amaraso, iseseme cyangwa cyanoze. OMS ivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe muri batandatu arwara cyane kandi afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso by'ibiza ari ugusonza, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa gukomera mu gatuza, guhinda umushyitsi, kugorwa no kugenda no mu maso cyangwa iminwa ifite ibara ry'ubururu. Ni byiza gushaka ubufasha bw'abaganga niba ibi bimenyetso bihari. Iterambere ry'indwara rishobora gutera amapifumo akomeye, indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba, sepsis, sepsis, no gupfa.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi bafite, ariko ibipimo byabo bikemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abantu bahuye n'umuntu wanduye bakagenzurwa neza kugira ngo bamenye niba nta bwandu bafite.
Ibitekerezo by'Ubushinwa ku kigero cy'abantu badafite ibimenyetso bya virusi bikomoka kuri bamwe bigera kuri 44%.
Igihe gisanzwe cyo kubamo (igihe kuva ubwandu butangira no kugaragaza ibimenyetso) kiri hagati y'umunsi umwe na 14 ariko ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rw'ibihe bidashidikanywaho ni uko, umubare w'abantu barwaye COVID-19 batakaje ibyiyumvo byo guhumurirwa wari 30% mu ntangiriro, nyuma biza kugabanuka bikagera kuri 15%.
Hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe byerekeranye n'uko iyi ndwara ikwirakwira bikiri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Iyi ndwara bivugwa ko yandura cyane cyane binyuze mu guhura n'abantu benshi ndetse no mu matembabuzi mato cyane avuka mu gihe umuntu akoroye, atetse cyangwa avuze, aho guhura cyane bivugwa ko ari hagati ya metero 1 na 2.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu akoroye atambaye umwitero, ayo maraso ashobora kuba areshya na metero 15 cyangwa metero 8.2.
Hari abantu batanze igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora no gutangwa n'udutonyanga tumara igihe kirekire mu mwuka, dushobora kuba twarakozwe mu gihe cy'ikiganiro. Udutonyanga tw'umwuka dushobora no gutangwa mu gihe cyo guhumeka, harimo no kuvuga, nubwo ubusanzwe virusi idashobora kuba mu kirere.
Utwo duce dushobora kugwa mu kanwa no mu mazuru y'abantu bari hafi yacu cyangwa tukava mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura, nko guterwa akato no gufashwa mu buvuzi bw'umutima (CPR), bushobora gutuma umwanda w'imyuka y'ubuhumekero usakara, bigatuma ikwirakwira mu mwuka.
Nanone kandi, umuntu ashobora kwandura iyo akoze ku kintu cyanduye, harimo n'uruhu, hanyuma agakora ku maso ye, ku zuru cyangwa ku munwa.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu busa, byemezwa ko ibyago byo kuyikwirakwiza ari bike.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu kanwa binyuze mu busa. Virusi yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo bishobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara no mu bihe bya nyuma by'indwara.
Hari ibipimo byerekana ko umuntu yanduye mbere y'iminsi itatu ibimenyetso bitangiye kugaragara, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ushobora kwandura mbere y'uko ibimenyetso by'ingenzi bigaragara.
Hari raporo nke z'abantu bafite ibimenyetso byemejwe na laboratwari, ariko ubwandu butagira ibimenyetso bwagaragaye mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe mu gihe cyo gukora iperereza ku bantu bahuye n'abo bantu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uko ubwandu bwandura, umuntu umwe ubusanzwe yandura abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, byaje kugaragara ko iyi virusi ishobora kugaragara mu minsi itatu mu plastiki (polypropylene) no mu byuma 304 bitagira ingese, umunsi umwe mu ikarito, n'amasaha ane mu muringa.
Ibi ariko biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Inyamaswa zo mu ngo n'izindi nyamaswa zigeze kugeragezwa zigasanga zifite COVID-19.
Nta kimenyetso na kimwe kigaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, ariko abategetsi bo mu Bwongereza bagaragaza ko ari ngombwa gukaraba intoki nyuma yo guhura n'inyamaswa, ndetse no gukaraba ahantu hashobora gukorwako n'abantu banduye.
Koronavirusi ya 2 y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya, yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu batatu barwaye ibicurane by'ibihaha bafitanye isano n'ubwoko bw'indwara y'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 bisa n'iby'indwara za coronavirusi mu byaremwe. Hasi mu mubiri w'umuntu, virusi yica isabune ikorwa mu rugo, ikangiza igifu cyayo cy'ubwirinzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV y'umwimerere.
Bivugwa ko byaturutse ku nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bwoko bwa virusi ya corona bwerekanye ko coronavirus ifitanye isano n'ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus, ubwoko bw'ubwoko bwa Sarbecovirus (ubwoko B).
Ifite umwihariko ungana na 96% ku rwego rwa genom yose, ku zindi koronavirusi z'urusobe z'imbeba (BatCoV RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi b'Abashinwa bavumbuye ko hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa rya aminoacide mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya genomic sequences hagati ya virusi ya pangolin n'iy'abantu.
Kugereranya ibinyabuzima byose kugeza ubu, byagaragaje ko virusi ya Corona yo mu bwoko bwa pangolin na SARS-CoV-2 bihuriyeho mu bice 92% by'ibinyabuzima, ibyo bikaba bidahagije kugira ngo bigaragaze ko inguge ari zo zigize iyi virusi.
Indwara ya virusi ishobora kwemezwa by'agateganyo hakurikijwe ibimenyetso, ariko icyemezo cya nyuma ni inyandiko isubiramo ikurikirwa n'imikorere ya polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) y'imyanda yanduye cyangwa tomography (CT).
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan bugereranya rRT-PCR na CT bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva neza, nubwo idakomeye cyane, kuko byinshi mu bimenyetso byayo bihuza n'ibindi byorezo by'ibicurane n'ibindi byorezo.
Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika Gishinzwe Imikorere y'Imiradiyo cyatangaje ko "CT idakoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza ry'imbere mu gupima COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye amabwiriza menshi yo gupima RNA ya SARS-CoV-2, iya mbere yasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Iki kizamini gikoresha inyandiko isubiramo ikurikirwa n'imikorere ya polymerase na simbi (rRT-PCR) mu gihe nyacyo.
Isuzuma rishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo bikunze kuboneka mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi.
Ubusanzwe iki kizamini gikorwa mu guswera mu muhogo, nubwo guswera mu muhogo nabyo bikoreshwa.Ibikigo byinshi n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi biri gukora ibizamini bya seroloji, bishobora gutahura abasirikare b'umubiri.
Ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibyo cyari cyaragaragaye ko gihuje n'ukuri bihagije ku buryo cyemewe gukoreshwa mu buryo bwagutse.
Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'amaraso cyakozwe na Cellex cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika cyemerewe gukoreshwa mu buryo bwihutirwa n'ibigo byemewe gusa.
Ibintu by'umwihariko by'amashusho ya radiographie na tomographie (CT) y'abantu bafite ibimenyetso birimo udusate tw'ibirahuri tudafite uburemere kandi tudafite ubukana bw'imvune.
Umuryango w'Abanyamakuru b'Igihugu w'Igihugu cy'Ubutaliyani uri gushyira hamwe urubuga mpuzamahanga rwa interineti rw'ibisubizo by'amashusho mu barwayi bemejwe.
Kubera ko hari ibindi byanduye nk'indwara ya adenovirus, amashusho adafite PCR yo kwemeza afite umwihariko muto mu kumenya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakorewe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibisubizo bya CT yo mu gatuza na PCR, bwerekana ko nubwo iyi mashusho idakenewe cyane mu kwandura, ariko ko yihuta kandi ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ishobora gukoreshwa nk'igikoresho cyo gukora ubushakashatsi mu by'icyorezo.
Imikorere y'imitsi y'ubwonko ishingiye ku bwenge bw'ikoranabuhanga (AI) yashyizweho kugira ngo imenyere ibimenyetso by'amashusho ya virusi kuri radiographie na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura iyi ndwara ni ugukomeza kugira isuku rusange, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa udakaravye intoki, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura ku gakaye no gushyira ako gakaye mu kintu gisiga imyanda.
Abamaze kwandura barasabwa kwambara agapfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Ingamba zo kwirinda kwanduzanya na zo zirasabwa. Leta nyinshi zashyizeho amategeko abuza cyangwa zisaba abantu kutajya mu bihugu n'uturere byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nyamara, iyi virusi yageze ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice byinshi by'isi.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage kandi bamwe mu baturage batazi aho banduye cyangwa uko banduye. Abakozi b'ubuzima bita ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye barasabwa gukoresha ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'abandi no kwirinda amaso. Gukurikirana guhura n'abandi ni uburyo bw'ingenzi ku bayobozi b'ubuzima bwo kumenya aho ubwandu bwaturutse no gukumira ubwandu.
Gukoresha na leta amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni zigendanwa mu bikorwa nk'ibi byateje ibibazo by'ibanga, Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 asohora itangazo risaba ko ibyo bikorwa byo kugenzura bihagarikwa.
Porogaramu zitandukanye za terefone zigendanwa zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zatanzwe ku bushake. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'abahanga arimo gukora ku bisubizo bikunda ubuzima bwite, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango bandike aho umukoresha aherereye ku zindi terefone zigendanwa.
Abakoresha bahabwa ubutumwa niba baragiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19. Hari ibitekerezo bitari byo ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura byakwirakwijwe, urugero nko gusukura izuru no gukorora mu mazi, ariko bikaba byaragaragaye ko bidafite akamaro.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruriho, ariko imiryango itandukanye irimo gukora kugira ngo ruvumburwe.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
CDC irasaba abantu gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje amazi n'isabuni nibura amasegonda makumyabiri, cyane cyane nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zabo zanduye cyane.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi ivuye mu mubiri w'umuntu, yica isabune yo mu rugo, ikamenagura uruhu rwayo rw'ubwirinzi.
CDC kandi itera inkunga yo gukoresha umuti wica udukoko ufite alcohol nibura 60% mu gihe nta isabune n'amazi bihari.
OMS itera inkunga abantu kwirinda gukorakora amaso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa batabanje gukaraba intoki.
Imyanya ishobora guhanagurwa mu buryo butandukanye (mu gihe kitarenze umunota umwe uhuye n'imiti y'ubuvuzi ku gice cy'icyuma kidafite ingese), harimo ethanol 6271%, isopropylic alcohol 50100%, sodium hypochlorite 0,1%, hydrogen peroxide 0,5% na iodopovidone 0,27,5%.
Ibindi bikoresho, urugero nka benzalkonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate, ntibikora cyane.
CDC itera inkunga ko mu gihe COVID-19 ikekwa cyangwa yemejwe ahantu nk'ibiro cyangwa mu kigo cy'abana, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki abantu bakoresha nk'utubati, utwuma dukoresha utwuma two gukorakora, konti, udupande n'udufaranga abantu barwaye bakoresha, bigomba kwandurwamo udukoko.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuzima avuga ko ari byiza gukinga umunwa n'izuru ukoresheje igituza gipfukamye cyangwa umwenda w'impapuro igihe ukorora cyangwa ukorora, kandi ukirinda gukoresha umwenda w'impapuro.
Ibikoresho byo gupfuka mu gihe cyo kubaga birasabwa ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye, kuko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ubunini n'intera ibitonyanga by'umwuka bivaho mu gihe uvuga, ukorora cyangwa ukoroga.
OMS yasohoye amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yavuze ko "kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya abantu guhora bakora ku maso, ari na cyo kintu cya mbere kibasira abantu iyo badafite isuku y'intoki".
OMS yasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku bantu barwaye COVID-19, nubwo yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Mu bihugu byinshi, kwambara udupfukamunwa ku maso n'abaturage muri rusange byatangiye gushishikarizwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC itera inkunga ikoreshwa ry'udupfukamunwa tudafite ubumara dukorwa mu mwenda. Ubushinwa bwatanze inama yihariye yo gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubumara tw'abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza muri rusange, cyane cyane mu gihe bahuye n'undi muntu (guma muri metero 1 cyangwa munsi yayo).
Muri Hong Kong, byasabwe kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe ukoresha imodoka cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abategetsi bashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gutera abantu inkunga yo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo no kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza gukaraba buri munsi.
Muri Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya, kubuza abantu kujya hanze batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa ngo bitwikire umunwa n'amazuru birabujijwe.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari hanze mu ruhame kugira ngo birinde kandi barinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yasabye ko abantu bose binjira mu maduka manini bagomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Muri Israel, abaturage bose basabwe kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Taiwan, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi n'imodoka zitwara abagenzi mu mijyi yose kwambara udupfukamunwa guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Muri Panama, ni itegeko kwambara agapfukamunwa iyo uvuye mu rugo, ariko nanone hatanzwe inama yo gukora agapfukamunwa mu rugo ku badashobora kukigura.
Udupfukamunwa tw'amaso twaraje dukoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwirinda abantu (nanone bita kwirinda kujya kure) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kurwanya ubwandu bigamije kugabanya umuvuduko w'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Muri ubwo buryo harimo gushyira abantu mu kato, guhagarika ingendo no gufunga amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu bushobora gukoreshwa na buri wese mu kuguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamukanyo zitagaragara no kugirana n'abandi imishyikirano.
Kuri ubu, leta nyinshi zirasaba cyangwa zigatanga inama yo kwirinda abantu mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu benshi bari bateraniye hamwe watanzwe n'inzego za leta ya Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima wagabanutse vuba uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta makuru y'ikwirakwira rya COVID-19 mu karere) ugera ku bantu 50, hanyuma ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije abantu benshi guteranira hamwe mu ruhame bari hejuru y'abantu babiri. Abakuze n'abafite indwara z'ibanze nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye no kurwara indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi, CDC ikaba ibasaba kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo. Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye gusimbuza "kwirinda" "kwirinda mu buryo bw'umubiri", kugira ngo bisobanure ko intego ari ukugabanya guhura mu buryo bw'umubiri mu gihe ukomeza imishyikirano y'abantu, yaba mu buryo busanzwe cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha ijambo "kwirinda abantu" byatumye abantu bumva ko bagomba kwitandukanya n'abandi aho gushishikariza abandi kubana na bo. Hari abayobozi bashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza ajyanye n'ubuzima bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri izo nama harimo kuryamana n'umuntu ubana na we gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwishyira mu kato mu rugo byasabwe ku bantu basanzwemo COVID-19 n'abatekereza ko banduye.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwitarura abantu mu buryo bukwiriye. Leta nyinshi zasabye cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose baba mu duce twatewe n'iyo ndwara bajya mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye yo kwishyirira mu kato yatanzwe ku bantu bari mu matsinda afite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba baragaragaye ku bandi bafite COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere gafite ubwandu bw'ubwoko bwinshi bagiriwe inama yo kwiherera iminsi 14 uhereye igihe bagaragaye bwa nyuma.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukugihagarika cyangwa kugikumira no kugigabanya.
Gufunga abantu bikorwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo kandi bigamije kubarinda no gushyira mu kato abanduye, ndetse no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kubarinda no gukingira abantu kugira ngo badakwirakwira.
Iyo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara bitagishoboka, imbaraga zitangwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya: ingamba zifatwa ubu zigamije kugabanya umuvuduko wo gukwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku buzima ndetse no ku baturage.
Ingamba zo kugabanya no gukumira indwara zishobora gufatwa icyarimwe, mu buryo bumwe.
Gukumira bisaba ingamba zikomeye cyane mu kugarura icyorezo ku kigero cyo hasi cy'ubwandu bw'indwara yanduza, mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubwandu. Ibyo twita "kugabanya icyorezo".
Ibyo bigabanya ibyago byo kuremerera serivisi z'ubuzima, bigatuma haboneka igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo by'ubutabazi bitari ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gucunga iki cyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku mu ntoki, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwisanzura; ingamba zo mu muryango zigamije gutandukanya abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibirori bituma abantu benshi bahurira hamwe; uruhare rw'abaturage mu rwego rwo gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura aho bahurira n'abandi. Ingamba zikomeye cyane zo guhashya iki cyorezo zafashwe mu Bushinwa ubwo byamenyekanaga ko iki cyorezo gikomeye. Urugero, imijyi yose yashyizwe mu kato kandi hashyirwaho amategeko abuza abantu gutembera.
Mu bindi bihugu, hafashwe ingamba zitandukanye zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Urugero, Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho uburyo bwo gupima abantu benshi no gushyira mu kato abantu bari mu duce dutandukanye, kandi leta yatanze amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu banduye.
Muri Singapuru, abanduye bahawe inkunga y'amafaranga igihe bari mu kato, kandi abatabigenje batyo baciwe amande akomeye.
Muri Tayiwani, hagiye habaho kongera imikorere y'udupfukamunwa, kandi ababikoraga bagahabwa ibihano. Imyitozo y'ubushakashatsi yakorewe mu Bwongereza no muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika igaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya umuvuduko w'ubwandu, ntibuhagarike ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (ni ukuvuga gusubiza inyuma ubukana bw'icyorezo) bibangamiye cyane.
Politiki nziza yo kugabanya ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa n'abapfa mu gihe umubare w'abapfa ku isi wiyongeraho bibiri bya gatatu, ariko ibyo byatuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa, kandi bigatuma inzego z'ubuzima ziremererwa.
Gukumira bishobora kuba inzira nziza, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bantu cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba mbere yaho. Bitabaye ibyo, ikwirakwira ry'indwara rishobora kongera kugaruka mu gihe ingamba zizaba zaragabanyijwe.
Gushyiraho ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka ku mibereho myiza y'abaturage no ku bukungu.
Nta muti wa virusi wemewe wihariye kuri COVID-19, ariko hari imbaraga mu gukora imiti, harimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Gukoresha imiti ya common cold idakoreshwa n'abaganga, kunywa amazi menshi no kuruhuka bihagije bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'ikibazo, gukoresha imiti ikoreshwa mu guhumeka, umwuka wa ogisijeni, guterwa amazi mu mitsi cyangwa imashini ifasha guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma iyi ndwara irushaho kuba mbi.
Imiti myinshi yari yemewe mbere mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima na ryo ryavuze ko hari imiti "y'iwabo n'imigenzo gakondo" ishobora koroshya ibimenyetso biterwa na virusi ya SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza ubuvuzi n'ibikenewe bitewe na COVID-19 ari ingamba z'ingenzi zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara, ECDC, n'ibiro bya OMS mu Burayi byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze kugira ngo bimurikire hamwe umutungo wabyo ku byiciro bitandukanye, harimo gushyira hamwe serivisi za laboratwari mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ibikorwa bidasabwa no gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi bagaragayeho COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi barwaye indwara z'uburwayi bukabije binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibitanda n'imashini zitanga umwuka.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku byabayeho kw'urwo rubanza rwa mbere (rwitwa "umuganga wa zero").
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho coronavirus nshya ni uwa mbere mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri ako karere wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byaha byari bifitanye isano cyane n'isoko ry'umusaruro w'ibishyimbo rya Huanan. Isoko kandi ryakundaga kugurisha inyamaswa nzima, ibyo bikaba byaratumye havuka igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye muri imwe muri izo nyamaswa. Mu yandi magambo, byemezwaga ko ifite inkomoko yo mu bwoko bw'inyamaswa. Ku ya 26 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abarwayi ryararebwe kandi rivurwa na Dr. Zhang Jixian, ku bitaro by'intara ya Hubei. Bukeye bwaho, umuganga yamenyesheje Ikigo cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara cya Wuhan Jianghan.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku "coronavirus imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri abo, barimo Li Wenliang, bakosowe n'igipolisi kubera gukwirakwiza inkuru z'ibinyoma. Undi muganga witwa Ai Fen, yakosowe n'abamusumbaga kubera ko yatanze amakuru.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza, yatangaje itangazo ku baturage kandi imenyesha OMS.
Abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ibicurane bataramenyekana, bari bamaze kubwirwa inzego z'ubuzima z'i Wuhan ko bagomba gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abarwaye wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice, hafi.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yakwirakwiriye mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, byatewe n'impunzi zo mu mwaka mushya w'Abashinwa no kuba Wuhan ari ikigo cy'ingendo, ndetse n'ahantu h'ingenzi hakoreshwa gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwagaragaje abarwayi bashya bagera ku 140 ku munsi, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzen.
Amakuru yemewe nyuma y'aho agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatsinze Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani, aho zari zifite umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1,61 baranduye ku isi hose; abantu basaga 97,000 barapfuye, abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Ibihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200 byamaze kugira nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi biri mu masezerano ya Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu kandi bishyiraho inzego zishinzwe ku mipaka.
Mu bihugu byagize icyo bikora harimo gushyira abantu mu kato (bitwa kandi amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo cyangwa gufunga) no gufunga. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 300 (abagera kuri 90% by'abatuye isi) bari mu kato mu buryo runaka muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bari mu kato muri Filipine, abagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari mu kato muri Afurika y'Epfo n'abantu bagera kuri miriyari 1,3 bari mu kato mu Buhinde.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari bamaze gufungwa mu buryo runaka, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri biyongera bagera kuri miliyari 2,6, bangana na kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 yabonywe i Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Dr Zhang Jixian yarebye itsinda ry'abarwayi barwaye indwara y'ibihaha z'impamvu zitazwi ku ya 26 Ukuboza. Ibitaro bye byatangaje ikigo cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara cya Wuhan Jianghan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019, ku bipimo byavanywe ku barwayi byerekanye ko coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa SARS iriho.
Itangazo ryatanzwe n'akanama gashinzwe ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza.
OMS yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
Ubwo izo nkuru zabaga, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bagabishijwe n'abapolisi ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya isobanutse" y'uko abantu bashobora kwandura.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye, nyuma bwiswe n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa, Xi Jinping, "intambara y'abaturage", mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa cyo gushyira abantu mu kato kinini mu mateka y'isi", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe gahunda yo gufunga abantu kugira ngo batongera kujya cyangwa kugaruka i Wuhan, aho abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57 bamaze kugera mu mijyi 15 yo mu ntara ya Hubei.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byarabuzanyijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama byahagaritswe mu duce dutandukanye.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko hari hubatswe ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Ibitaro by'i Leishenshan byubatswe nyuma kugira ngo bifashe abarwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na za sitade. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera ikiruhuko cy'Ibirori by'Ubutwari.
Kaminuza n'amashuri hirya no hino mu gihugu na byo byafunzwe.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zafashe ingamba zitandukanye cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Ingamba zo gukora ku buryo bwa kure zafashwe mu turere twinshi tw'igihugu.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zashyizweho muri Hubei no hanze yayo.
Imodoka zitwara abantu mu ruhame zarahindutse, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Gucunga urujya n'uruza rw'abantu byashyizwe mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byatekerejwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari bafite uburyo bwo kugabanya ingendo. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyerekeje ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda "kuzana" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato iminsi 14 ku bantu bose bavuye mu bindi bihugu baza muri uwo mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bw'ibanze bwagize ubwandu bw'umuntu umwe gusa mu minsi itanu, muri iki gihe bwari bwanduye umuntu wari waturutse muri Istanbul agaruka i Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwo mu gihugu ryahise rihagarikwa kandi ko iki cyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo z'ingendo zagabanyijwe muri Hubei uretse Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho Guma mu Rugo. Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira kw'abantu bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta bisobanuro bidasanzwe byatanzwe ku gihe iyo politiki izavaho.
Umuntu wese wifuza kwinjira mu Bushinwa agomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula z'Ubushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ibigo n'inganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, itanga inguzanyo ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kuboroga, utangira n'umunsi wo guceceka w'iminota itatu mu gihugu hose ku ya 4 Mata saa kumi z'amanywa, bihuye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming. Icyakora, leta nkuru yasabye imiryango kwibuka ku rubuga rwa interineti, ikurikiza amabwiriza yo gutandukanya abantu kugira ngo birinde ko COVID-19 yongera kwaduka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, byemejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo ivuye mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera gukomeye mu barwayi bemejwe ku ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini biterwa n'iteraniro ryabereye i Daegu ry'umuteguro mushya w'idini, uzwi ku izina rya Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abantu bakeka ko abantu bari baje gusura Shincheonji i Daegu bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9,336 b'iryo torero, 1,261, cyangwa abagera kuri 13%, bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari umuburo ukomeye ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hari hamaze kuvugwa abarwayi barenga 2.000, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bagera ku 3.150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare byo muri Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyo virusi.
Amasaha y'indege na yo yarahindutse kandi irahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho icyo cyafashwe nk'igikorwa kinini kandi gitunganijwe neza ku isi mu gupima abaturage kuri virusi. Igihugu kandi cyashyize mu kato abantu banduye kandi cyakurikirana kandi gishyira mu kato abahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagaragaje ko abantu bose bari bavuye mu ngendo mpuzamahanga bagomba gutanga raporo ku giti cyabo, gupima virusi ku modoka, ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima, bituma abantu bagera ku 20.000 bapimwa ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'ifitwe n'ingaruka nziza mu kurwanya iki cyorezo, nubwo itashyize imijyi yose mu kato.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon acibwa ku butegetsi kubera ko leta itakoresheje neza icyo cyorezo, cyangwa se bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byavuzwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yagize umubare muto w'abanduye mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bashya bavuye hanze bagomba kujya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yahawe ubufasha mu gupima virusi buturutse mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yemeje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi ivuga ko abantu babiri bapfuye uwo munsi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, siporo n'ibirori by'idini ku wa Gatanu, gufunga za kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Iran ifite miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga ya Riais yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda afite yo gushyira abantu mu kato mu duce twagwiririwe n'iki cyorezo, kandi ko abantu bonyine ari bo bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imigi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo imodoka nyinshi hagati y'imigi mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Persian Nowruz zakomeje.
Ahantu hatagatifu ha Shia muri Qom hafunguye ku bayoboke b'idini rya Islam kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe hari ibirego byo guhisha ko iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abanduye muri iki gihugu ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha abanduye 388 leta ya Irani yari imaze gutangaza kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, 23 mu bagize 290 bagaragaweho virusi ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye bikomeye abayobozi ba gereza ya Irani kurekura burundu abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira kutumvikana mu mahoro, no gufungura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zikwiriye.
Ikigo cyavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bigo bifunze nk'ibigo by'ifungwa, nabyo bihangayikishwa no kubura ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, umubare munini kuva icyorezo cyatangira muri icyo gihugu.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 bariho cyangwa bari mu kiruhuko cy'iza bukuru n'abayobozi ba leta barapfuye bazize iyi ndwara kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abarwayi bashya 50 buri saha, n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota icumi azize Coronavirus.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuhagarariye OMS, muri Irani hashobora kuba hari abantu barwaye kurusha uko bivugwa, ku kigero cy'incuro eshanu.
Hari abavuga ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kuba bibangamiye ubushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo kwitabira icyorezo cya virusi.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Uburenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu bigabanywa ku bihugu byazahajwe cyane n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani.
Icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga bagasanga baranduye SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zijya n'iziva mu Bushinwa kandi igatangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Itsinda ry'abantu batagendana n'abanduye COVID-19 ryaragaragajwe nyuma, ritangira n'abanduye 16 bemejwe muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko nshinga rigamije gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu bice by'icyorezo, abantu babujijwe kwinjira no gusohoka.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yasabye ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza zose zo mu gihugu zose zifungwa ubwo u Butaliyani bwageraga ku bantu 100 bapfuye.
Ibikorwa byose bikomeye bya siporo, harimo imikino ya Serie A, bigomba kubera mu nzu zifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, siporo zose zahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yasabye ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bifungwa, uretse amaduka manini n'amafarumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abaganga, Abatabara, Abafasha mu Bwihutirwa (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'imyifatire y'abaganga ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo gupima bashobora gukoresha.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwasize u Bushinwa bufite umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye bazize Coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga raporo y'abantu 3.405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'igisirikare zifite ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128.948, hapfuye 15.887 kandi habonetse abarwayi 21.815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu bageze mu za bukuru kandi ntibashobore gupima abantu bose bari baranduye virusi kugeza icyo gihe, bishobora kuba byaratumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri virusi cyabanje kugaragara nk'icyoroshye mu bihugu byazahajwe, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gutandukanya abantu cyangwa gushyira abaturage bayo mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko itita ku bibazo byugarije abaturage, kandi ko itita ku bibazo byabo. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatanze itangazo ry'inama yo guhagarika ingendo zose zidakenewe no guhura n'abantu, asaba abantu gukora mu rugo uko bishoboka kose no kwirinda ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no muri za sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, nk'amabyiniro na za siporo bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi yiyemeza kwishyura 80% by'imishahara y'abakozi kugeza ku gipimo cya £2,500 ku kwezi kugira ngo birinde ubushomeri mu gihe cy'icyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gutandukanya abantu, abuza abantu benshi guteranira hamwe n'abantu babiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze ku rugero ruto rukenewe.
Bitandukanye n'ingamba za mbere, izi ngamba zashyizweho n'igipolisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gutatanya abantu.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwasabwe gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi bufatwa nk'ubw'ingenzi, harimo amaduka y'ibikoresho, farumasi, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibyuma, za lisansi n'aho bakorera imodoka.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere uzwiho COVID-19 yemejwe mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Washington mu mugabo wari wavuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Inteko ishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus yashyizweho ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ingutu mu buzima, kandi buhagarika abagenzi bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara  ikigo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage cya mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika  cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye gupima vuba, bituma abantu batamenya uko icyo gihe icyo cyorezo cyari gikomeye.
Ibizamini byaranzwe n'ibikoresho byo gupima bidakora neza byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemerwa na leta ya leta ku bikoresho byo gupima bitari ibya leta (ku bigo by'imyitozo ngororamubiri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'amabwiriza abuza abantu gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (ibisabwa n'abaganga nyuma yaho).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru Washington Post cyatangaje ko hasigaye ibipimo 4,000 byo gupima muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari hasigaye ibipimo 14,000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite icyifuzo cy'abaganga bagombaga gutegereza amasaha cyangwa iminsi kugira ngo bapimwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika rwatangajwe muri leta ya Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyaje gukurikiraho mu buryo bwihuse n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu mpera z'icyumweru cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yari afunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yabwiwe n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu Bwongereza bo muri Imperial College i Londres ko hari icyizere cy'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'ingengo y'imari y'inyongera yo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ryatanze miliyari 8,3 z'amadolari mu nkunga z'ibigo bya leta mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi gukora ingendo, yahagaritse inama, kandi ashishikariza abakozi gukora mu rugo.
Ibikorwa n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo mu Burayi bwose, usibye Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguyeho ibihano bigera no mu Bwongereza no muri Ireland.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, bituma amafaranga ya leta aboneka kugira ngo iki kibazo gikemuke.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha yabyo hirya no hino muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu rwego rwo kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York wari ufite abantu 10,700 banduye Coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye bose muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bigaragara ko biri gukora, kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse iva ku minsi 2.0 igera ku minsi 4.7.
Guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, abantu 32,308 nibo bamaze kwandura iyi virus mu mujyi wa New York, naho abantu 672 nibo bamaze gupfa. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zanduye Coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Guhera ku ya 8 Mata, abantu 400,335 nibo bamaze kwandura iyi virus muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, naho abantu 12,841 barayipfushije.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibitangazamakuru, ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000 bwageze i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yabonye umubare ntarengwa w'abantu 884 bishwe na Coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Mu ntara ya New York, abantu barenga 100.000 ku ya 3 Mata. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kubera gupfobya akaga no kugenzura ubutumwa mu gutegeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi guhuza ibyatangajwe n'abantu n'ibyatangajwe na perezida wungirije Mike Pence.
Kwemera muri rusange uburyo Trump yakemuye iki kibazo byagiye bihinduka bitewe n'amashyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze icyizere Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zifite cyo kwinjiza ibikoresho by'ingenzi, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi, bivuye mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'imiterere y'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu kwerekana no guhanura imiterere y'ikwirakwira ryayo, ryatangajwe mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere hagati 2020.
Dushingiye ku makuru yo mu 2018 y'ishyirahamwe ry'ingendo z'indege ku isi, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo byagize umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byavuzwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abantu baturukaga mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Bali ni yo yavuzwe ko idashobora cyane mu bihugu 20 bikunzwe cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yo yavuzwe ko ishobora cyane. Ositaraliya yemeje gahunda yayo yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko hari byinshi bigikeneye kumenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'ubwiyongere bw'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza abantu bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye ko abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi bavanwa muri ako gace, mbere na mbere binyuze mu ndege zafatiwe mu gihugu cy'iwabo, nyuma y'uko abategetsi b'Ubushinwa babirekuye.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande biri mu bihugu bya mbere bitegura gutahukana abaturage babyo.
Pakistani yavuze ko itazasubiza inyuma umuturage n'umwe uvuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuyemo Abanyabrezili 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bahagurukiye muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yahagaze mbere yo kujya muri Brezil.
Abaturage ba Burezili bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari ikodeshejwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan boherezwa ku Kigo cya Trenton Air Force Base kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanaada 185 bari baturutse i Wuhan yageze ku Kigo cya Gisirikare cya Kanada i Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Australia bafashe abaturage 277 ku ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare babajyana ku Kigo cyo Gufunga ku Kirwa cya Noheli, nyuma cyongera gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cy'ihererekanya, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
Indege yo guhungisha abaturage ba Nouvelle Zélande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe bo muri Ositaraliya na Pasifika) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cy'i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gukura Abanyamerika ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abantu 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bakuwe muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye kuvana abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe indege ya South African Airways yari yaraguzwe na guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije abaturage 112 b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo.
Igerageza ry'ubuvuzi ryakozwe mbere yo kwambuka, kandi Abanyafurika y'Epfo bane bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basigaye inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaje ko nta bwandu bafite nibo basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibyavuye mu bizamini byemereye abaturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, barimo abakozi ba ndege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, ko baguma mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu rwego rwo kwirinda.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje ubufasha Ubushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri Kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice byibasiwe na virusi mu Bushinwa, hamwe n'itsinda rihuriweho mu karere ka Chicago bivugwa ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ibihumbi 50 ku bitaro byo mu Ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango wita ku butabazi Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa tw'ubuso ibihumbi 200 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi birimo utwenda two mu maso n'imyambaro, binyuze mu gutwara abantu mu buryo bw'impanuka mu ndege ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union Hospital ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku kigo cy'isi cyita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo kifashe mu bushakashatsi bw'inkingo no mu bikorwa byo kuvurwa, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 muri Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Maleziya yatangaje ko izatangaza impano y'utugati tugera kuri miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo imyenda 10,000 yo kurinda, Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya ibindi bifaranga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bufasha bw'amafaranga mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo. Nyuma y'uko abanduye mu Bushinwa bahagaze, iki gihugu cyakomeje kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu bitandukanye byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu gufasha u Butaliyani gucunga icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'imiti, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda abantu i Addis Abeba muri Ethiopia kugira ngo itangirwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'imashini 5 zo guhumeka muri Panama.
Ma kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque bagaragaje impungenge ku bipimo by'amasike n'ibikoresho by'imiti byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yakiriye ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima Coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bifite 30% gusa by'ukuri, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwasubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 twari dufite inenge.
Ububiligi bwakusanyije udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bw'ibanze ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga kutagira amakuru atuma kwirinda no gukumira bidashoboka, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho guverinoma nkuru "yatangaga amakuru buri gihe kugira ngo ikureho ubwoba buza mu minsi mikuru yo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu rwego rwo kwamagana icyemezo cy'abategetsi bakuru cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Gauden Galea, uhagarariye OMS, yavuze ko "ibyo nta gushidikanya ko bitari inama ya OMS" kandi ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'uko twiyemeje kugabanya icyorezo mu gace cyari cyiganjemo". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye hanze y'u Bushinwa kandi umubare w'abanduye ukongera kwiyongera mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga (PHEIC), kikaba ari icya gatandatu PHEIC kivugwa kuva icyo cyemezo cyatangira gutangwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cyo mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC yakoreshejwe kubera "ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abiciriritse bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibihano ku ngendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "WHO idatanga inama yo kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika yo gushyigikira gahunda yo kwitegura mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abiganjemo, ivuga ko byihutirwa gufasha ibyo bihugu "bitafite uburyo bwo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, ndetse n'iyo yagaragaye".
Tedros nyuma yaho yagize icyo avuga avuga avuga ko "turi abanyembaraga nk'aho turi abanyantege nke" maze asaba amahanga "gushora imari ubu cyangwa kwishyura nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'iyo ndwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "imbaraga z'umuryango w'Abibumbye wose mu gusubiza".
Ikipe y'umuryango w'abibumbye ishinzwe kurwanya ibiza yashyizwe mu bikorwa, bituma habaho guhuza ibisubizo byose by'umuryango w'abibumbye, ibi OMS ivuga ko bizatuma "bibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora kwinjira n'ubunararibonye bwazo mu rwego rw'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere biterwa n'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya WHO Joint Mission Team n'u Bushinwa ryemerewe guha ubufasha abahanga mpuzamahanga n'ab'ishami rya WHO bari ku butaka bw'u Bushinwa mu gucunga indwara mu gihugu no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubwandu bw'iyo ndwara" binyuze mu mahugurwa n'inama n'inzego z'ibanze ku rwego rw'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo gusura "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'imirenge, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko "isi ikwiriye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya Coronavirus gishobora kubaho", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ko icyorezo cyagwira, ibihugu bigomba gushyiramo "icyiciro cyo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo kiri gutera imbere muri Irani, OMS yohereje Itsinda ry'Ibikorwa Rihuriweho kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abakozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyiciro cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus ku isi yose kizazamurwa kiva ku "cyinshi" kijya ku "cyinshi cyane", kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cyo kugabanyirizwaho umuburo no gusuzuma ibyago.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo cy'ubuzima bw'imvura, yatanze umuburo mu itangazo agira ati "Iri ni ijambo ry'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: Mukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi mugomba kuba mwiteguye", ashimangira ko ingamba nziza zo guhangana na yo zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko kuvuga ko kizaba ari "gukomeza kwemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi azahura n'iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko OMS yari "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ikwirakwira n'uburemere, ndetse n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba byo kutagira icyo ikora". OMS yahuye n'ibitotezo byinshi kubera ibyo yabonaga ko ari imicungire mibi y'icyorezo, harimo gutangaza hakiri kare ko ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Mu bitabiriye iki gikorwa harimo n'icyemezo cyo kwegura cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku wa 6 Mata, cyasabaga umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zashimangiye kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufashwa mu kurokora ubuzima kandi ko leta ari yo igomba kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amafaranga cyangwa gahunda y'ubuzima bitagombye na rimwe kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bagaragaje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, abanyamuryango b'amadini mato mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abafite ibibazo byo mu mutwe, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'andi matsinda adasobanuwe akeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga ya leta irimo gusuzuma ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage zatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane n'Iterambere mu by'Ubukungu watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru yuzuye kandi ku gihe ku bisubizo by' politiki mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza uburyo bwo kwita ku buzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ingaruka z'ibihano byo gufunga no kugabanya ingendo, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga kirimo na Country Policy Tracker, ifasha ibihugu kwigira ku bihugu byaho no koroshya uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubwongereza, Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro ku buryo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi bo mu ntara z'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe kubera uburyo bakiriye ibikorwa byo gushyira abantu mu kato mu Burasirazuba bw'Ubushinwa, mu kugaragaza ko badashimishijwe n'uko inzego za politiki z'aho zitabiriye iki cyorezo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko iki gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'Abashinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera mbere y'igihe ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan, bahitamo kwemera ibitekerezo by'ubuhotozi kuri COVID-19 byaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump bwa Leta Zunze Ubumwe bwa Amerika bwise Coronavirus "Virus y'Abashinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan" buvuga ko gusesa amakuru mu Bushinwa "byateye virusi ubu yabaye icyorezo ku isi", ibyo na byo byavuzwe nabi n'abamunenga bamwe na bamwe ko ari ivangura ry'amoko kandi ko ari "uburyo bwo gukebanura abategetsi ku kudakora neza mu kurwanya iki cyorezo".
Daily Beast yakuye kuri ka kabare ka Leta ya Amerika gahunda y'itumanaho irambuye bigaragara ko ikomoka mu nama y'umutekano w'igihugu, aho hari igitabo cyavuze ko "Ibi byose bifitanye isano n'Ubushinwa.
Byanasabwe ko tugerageza kandi tukabona ubwo butumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, harimo inama n'amateraniro y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo. "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byazahajwe n'iyi virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa byo kwamamaza kugira ngo bigire ingaruka ku isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki z'amahanga mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya politiki kirimo no guharanira kugira uruhare binyuze mu buryo bwo kubona ibintu mu buryo butandukanye n'uko abantu babibona, ndetse n'uburyo bwo gutanga".
Borrell kandi yavuze ko "Ubushinwa buri gukwirakwiza cyane ubutumwa ko, bitandukanye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Ubushinwa bwasabye kandi Amerika guhagarika ibihano yafatiye Syria, Venezuela na Iran, mu gihe bivugwa ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu.
Impano ya Jack Ma y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 yagenewe Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika na bo bashinjwa kuyobya imfashanyo zigenewe ibindi bihugu zikajya mu gihugu cyabo.
Kandi wumva impaka zijyanye n'udupfukamunwa zivugwa mu bindi bihugu, nk'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi; na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe ibyuma bihumanya amagana byari bigenewe Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi utagaragaje ubufatanye n'abazahajwe na Coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yagize ati "Ubushinwa bwonyine ni bwo bwashubije mu buryo bw'impande zombi.
Nta gushidikanya ko ibyo atari ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye ingabo z'u Burusiya kohereza abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zo kwanduza indwara, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyasubiyemo "isoko rya politiki ryo ku rwego rwo hejuru" ritavuzwe amazina, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'ibyo u Burusiya butanga "nta cyo bimaze cyangwa nta cyo bimaze ku Butaliyani".
Uyu mushinjacyaha yashinje u Burusiya gukora "ibikorwa bya politiki n'ibya dipolomasi".
Perezida w'akarere ka Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, ntibatangaje amakuru yatanzwe n'itangazamakuru kandi bagaragaje ko bashimira.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje indege y'ubutabazi iherekejwe n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gutanga ubufasha ku bagenzi be b'Abanyamerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abashinzwe ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byo muri Amerika bazaba bari mu bihe byiza, na bo bazakora ku buryo buhuje n'ibyo bakeneye".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO yateguwe "Defender 2020" mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, imyitozo ya gisirikare ikomeye ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangiye, izakomeza ku kigero gito.
Umunyamabanga mukuru wa Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, Kate Hudson, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati "Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho ubu, ntabwo byangiza ubuzima bw'ingabo za Amerika gusa n'ibihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi biri muri iyo myitozo, ahubwo byangiza n'abaturage bo mu bihugu bikoreramo". Leta ya Irani yibasiwe cyane na virusi, aho abanyamuryango bagera ku icumi na babiri b'inteko bashyizwe mu majwi, ndetse n'abanyapolitiki ba politiki cumi na batanu cyangwa bavuye mu butegetsi.
Perezida wa Iran, Hassan Rouhani yanditse ibaruwa y'umugaragaro ku bayobozi b'isi asaba ubufasha ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, avuga ko igihugu cye gifite ibibazo byo guhangana n'iki cyorezo kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga nk'ingaruka z'ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ifata politiki rusange y'imibereho myiza mu bindi bihugu byateye imbere, harimo ubuvuzi busanzwe, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango uhembwa, n'amafaranga menshi yo gushyigikira ubuzima rusange.
Abasesengura politiki bari baravuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorerwa kuyobora u Buyapani mu matora yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yarushijeho kuzamba kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira abantu mu kato idafite ishingiro kandi idafite icyo ivuze, nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko umuntu wese uza aturutse muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twatoranyijwe na leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wari waratangiye ufite amacakubiri ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yitabiriye iki kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Moon acibwa ku butegetsi kubera ibyo bise gucunga nabi icyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo. Icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo kubisubiza.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma ubutegetsi bwongera ububasha bwabwo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye uburyo bwo kwemerera Minisitiri w'Intebe, Viktor Orbán, gutegeka binyuze mu itegeko ry'iteka, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora no guhana abantu bafatwaho gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku byerekeye virusi n'uburyo leta itegura ibibazo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus ni cyo cyateje ibibazo byinshi by'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, biturutse ku kwiyongera kw'ibikoresho ku isi hose byo kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu bitewe n'ubwoba, no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze amabwiriza yo kwirinda ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abantu benshi bayikoresha kandi ababaha imiti bakabura aho bayitanga.
Ahantu henshi kandi habaye ibikorwa byo guhaha kubera ubwoba, bituma ibicuruzwa by'ibanze birangira bidafite aho biherereye, nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku, amazi mu macupa, harimo n'ibikoresho bike.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga cyane cyane rwamye ruvuga ko ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitinda koherezwa.
Dukurikije umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, ibisabwa ku bikoresho byo kwirinda byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibyo byatumaga ibiciro byiyongera bikagera ku ncuro makumyabiri z'igiciro gisanzwe, kandi byatumaga ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bidatangwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byateje ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda ku isi hose, OMS ikaburira ko bishobora gushyira ubuzima bw'abakozi mu kaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatumye abaguzi b'Abashinwa babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Nubwo umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, n'ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, utwo duce twombi twakijijwe ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Ingamba zafashwe n'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ubucuruzi n'ubwikorezi butemewe bw'ibikoresho by'ingenzi zagize icyo zigeraho, birinda ibura ry'ibiribwa ryari ryitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Amajyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani afite umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi ntibyagabanyutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera nkuko abahagarariye inganda babivuga.
Amashuka y'ibiribwa yari ubusa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa bashyize hanze ibigega by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo aboneka mu Butaliyani asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibicuruzwa byabo mu gihe habaye impanuka.
Ingaruka mbi ku bukungu bw'isi yose byumvikaniye mu Bushinwa: nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20,5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bukomeye ari ubukungu bukomeye kandi ari ikigo cy'inganda, iki cyorezo cyafashwe nk'ikibazo gikomeye cyateje ihungabana mu bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'iperereza cya The Economist, yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe hazabaho isesengura ry'ibishoboka.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kuzagera ku rugero ruruta urwa SARS yo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke mu by'ubwikorezi muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, yavuze ko ingaruka z'ibyo bishobora kuzagira ku muyoboro w'ibikoresho ku isi, zishobora kugera kuri miriyari 300 z'amadolari, kandi ko zishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Umuryango w'ibihugu bitanga peteroli (OPEC) bivugwa ko "wacitse intege" nyuma y'ihindagurika rikomeye ry'ibiciro bya peteroli bitewe n'ibyifuzo bike by'Ubushinwa.
Amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yaguye ku ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ubwiyongere bukomeye bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'Ubushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, imibare myinshi y'imigabane muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, harimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500, n'ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cya Dow Jones, byagize igihombo gikomeye cyane kuva mu 2008, Dow ikagwa amanota 1.191, ari na yo igihombo gikomeye cyane cyabayeho mu munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari byo mu 2007-08.
Indi mibare itatu yose yarangiye icyumweru igeze hejuru ya 10%.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje indangamuntu ya Leta y'Ubushinwa ariko ikomeza kuba mbi.
Imigabane yongeye kumanuka bitewe n'impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, ku wa 16 Werurwe ni bwo yagabanutse cyane.
Abantu benshi babona ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohamed El-Erian yashimye ingamba z'ibihe bidasanzwe zafashwe n'ibihugu na banki nkuru.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu ziri guhita zisubiza ibintu vuba kurusha uko zisubizaga imari y'isi mu 2008.
Ubukerarugendo ni kimwe mu bice byazahajwe cyane n'ibihano ku ngendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'ahantu ho gutemberera, ndetse na guverinoma zigira inama abantu kutagira ingendo ku isi.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, ingendo z'indege nyinshi zahagaritswe kubera ko abantu bari bake, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines, na Qantas, mu gihe ikigo cy'indege cyo mu Bwongereza cya Flybe cyarasenyutse.
Ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'amato y'ubwato bw'ubwato bwabaye ku rugero rutazwi.
Ibigo byinshi by'amagare ya moshi n'ibibuga by'indege na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye na Chunyun, igihe kinini cy'ingendo kijyanye n'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Ibikorwa byinshi birimo imbaga y'abantu benshi byahagaritswe na guverinoma z'ibihugu n'uturere, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka by'umwaka mushya, ndetse n'ibigo byigenga byugaritse amaduka n'ahantu nyaburanga nko muri Disneyland muri Hong Kong na Shanghai.
Ibikorwa byinshi by'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi n'ahantu nyaburanga ho gutemberera byafunzwe kugira ngo hatagira abantu benshi, harimo Umujyi Wambuwe i Beijing n'ibirori by'abasenga Imana.
Mu ntara 24, mu ntara 31 zo mu Bushinwa, mu mirenge no mu turere, abayobozi bongeyeho ikiruhuko cy'Umwaka Mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ahantu henshi hakorerwa imirimo hatongera gufungura kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice byatanze 80% bya GDP y'igihugu na 90% by'ibyoherezwa mu mahanga.
Hong Kong yongereye ibikorwa byo guhangana n'icyorezo ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi itangaza ko ari mu bihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika ibirori byayo byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi rwagize ingaruka ku isi hose, ku buryo amaduka yagabanyijwe amasaha cyangwa agafungwa by'agateganyo.
Gusura abacuruzi mu Burayi na Amerika y'Amajyepfo byagabanutseho 40%.
Abacuruzi bo muri Amerika ya Ruguru no mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati babonye igabanuka rya 50-60%.
Ibi kandi byateje igabanuka ry'ibice 33-43% by'abagenzi bajya mu bigo by'ubucuruzi muri Werurwe ugereranyije n'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare.
Abakora ibigo by'ubucuruzi hirya no hino ku isi bashyizeho izindi ngamba zirimo isuku nyinshi, gushyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe kugira ngo barebe ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi, no guhagarika ibirori. Nk'uko Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Epfo ibivuga, byatekerejwe ko ubukene buterwa n'icyorezo bushobora gutuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 barushaho gukena muri Amerika y'Epfo kurusha uko byari kugenda iyo hataza kubaho icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 bo mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi kabo.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bo mu byaro bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu Bushinwa basigaye iwabo mu ntara zo hagati cyangwa bafungiwe mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo maze basaba leta ubufasha.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus gishobora gutwara akazi miliyoni 47 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kandi umubare w'abashomeri ushobora kugera kuri 32%, nk'uko byemezwa na Banki y'Igihugu y'Igihugu ya St. Louis. Gufunga mu Buhinde byatumye abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde babarirwa muri za miriyoni mirongo (bahembwa binyuze mu mushahara w'umunsi) batagira akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Angus Reid bwagaragaje ko 44% by'imiryango ya Kanada yagize ubushomeri bw'uburyo runaka. Abakozi hafi 900.000 batakaje akazi muri Esipanye kuva igihugu cyakiriye gahunda yo gufunga hagati muri Werurwe 2020.
Mu mpera z'icyumweru cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa bagera kuri miliyoni 4 basabye ubufasha bwo kubura akazi, abakozi b'Abongereza bagera kuri miliyoni basabye inguzanyo rusange.
Porogaramu y'imishahara y'akazi k'igihe gito y'Abadage yashizweho n'u Bufaransa n'Ubwongereza.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco byahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye z'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango ndetse n'abantu - baba abikorera n'abikorera - ku isi hose.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuhanzi n'umuco yagerageje gukomeza inshingano zayo (akenshi zitangwa na leta) zo gutanga uburenganzira ku mutungo ndangamuco ku baturage, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi bayo n'abaturage no gufasha abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi no ku rwego rutandukanye, inzu ndangamurage, amaduka acuruza ibitabo, ibigo by'imyidagaduro n'ibindi bigo by'umuco byafunzwe igihe kitazwi, imurika, ibirori n'imyidagaduro byahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe.
Mu gusubiza, hakozwe ingufu nyinshi mu gutanga serivisi zindi hifashishijwe uburyo bwa digitale. Ikindi kintu giherutse kandi kiri kwiyongera cyane muri iki cyorezo ni ukuhagarika imirimo y'idini, ibirori bikomeye bya siporo, n'ibindi bikorwa by'iterambere nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'ibirori by'imideri.
Uruganda rwa filimi na rwo rwarabayeho ihungabana. Vatikani yatangaje ko imihango y'Icyumweru cya Pasika i Roma, yagombaga kuba mu cyumweru cya nyuma cy'igihe cya Kristendomu cya Karema, yahagaritswe.
Amadini menshi yasabye abakristu bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo zabo aho kujya mu misa ku Cyumweru; amwe mu matorero yatumye ibikorwa by'itorero biboneka kuri radiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo mu gihe andi yatangaga amasengesho yo mu modoka.
Kubera ko Diyosezi Gatolika y'i Roma yafunze insengero zayo n'insengero zayo, kandi St. Peter's Square ikaba yari irimo ubusa nta bakirisitu bayirimo, izindi nzego z'amadini na zo zahagaritse imirimo kandi zigabanya abantu benshi mu nsengero, mu misigiti, mu masinagogi, mu nsengero no mu masengero.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Irani yatangaje ko amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu yahagaritswe mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo kandi nyuma yaho insengero zarafunzwe, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abanyamahanga bakora ingendo z'ubutagatifu kwinjira, ndetse n'abatuye ahantu hatagatifu i Maka na Medina.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye cyane mu mikino mpuzamahanga kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Ibikorwa byinshi bikomeye byahagaritswe cyangwa byasubitswe, harimo UEFA Champions League ya 2019-2020, Premier League ya 2019-2020, shampiyona ya NBA ya 2019-2020, n'umwaka wa NHL wa 2019-2020.
Icyorezo cyateje ibibazo gahunda y'imikino ya Olympic yo mu mpeshyi ya 2020, yari iteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Olempike Mpuzamahanga yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iri rushanwa "rizasubikwa ku itariki nyuma ya 2020, ariko bitarenze impeshyi ya 2021".
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi bakina imikino yo kuri interineti, hamwe n'imbuga zitandukanye z'imikino yo kuri interineti zanditse ko biyongereye cyane ku bipimo by'abakinnyi bashya.
Amakinamico menshi akomeye nka Broadway na yo yahagaritse ibitaramo byose.
Bamwe mu bahanzi barimo gushaka uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangiza abandi ibihangano byabo kuri interineti nk'uburyo bwo guhitamo ibikorwa bisanzwe byo kumurika ibihangano byabo, nko gukora ibitaramo cyangwa gukora "ibirori" kuri interineti ku bahanzi kugirango bamare, basangire kandi bamenyekanishe ibihangano byabo.
Kuri interineti, ibintu bitandukanye byo kuri interineti ku byerekeye coronavirus birakwirakwizwa, kuko benshi bashakisha urwenya n'imyidagaduro mu gihe nta cyizere.
Kuva COVID-19 yatangira, habayeho kwiyongera kw'ivangura, kwanga abanyamahanga no kuvangura ku bwoko ku bantu bakomoka mu Bushinwa cyangwa muri Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, no ku bantu bo mu duce tw'ibanze mu Burayi, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika no mu bindi bihugu.
Ibihe by'ubwoba, kutizerana no kwanga abantu byagaragariye mu bihugu byinshi, cyane cyane mu Burayi, Aziya y'iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru, no mu karere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Ibyavuye mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare (igihe abenshi mu barwayi bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) byagaragaje ibyiyumvo by'ivangura byumvikanishijwe mu matsinda atandukanye ku isi hose ku birebana n'uko Abashinwa bakwiriye iyi virusi cyangwa bakaba bari guhabwa igihano gikwiriye kubera ibyo bateje.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe muri Afurika na byo byatangaje ko umwuka wo kurwanya Ubushinwa wiyongereye.
Abaturage benshi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei bavuze ko barenganwaga bitewe n'aho bakomokaga.
Ibi byashyigikiwe n'Abashinwa haba kuri interineti no hanze yayo, kandi bigenewe abantu bo mu duce twugarijwe n'iyi virusi.
Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyateye imbere mu bihugu bishya by'ibanze, abaturage b'u Butaliyani, igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyahuye n'icyorezo gikomeye cya COVID-19, na bo bashoboraga kugirirwa urwikekwe no kwanga abanyamahanga. Abaturage bo mu bihugu birimo Malaysia, Nouvelle-Zélande, Singapuru na Koreya y'Epfo babanje gusinya impapuro zisaba ko Ubushinwa bubuzwa kwinjira mu bihugu byabo mu rwego rwo guhashya iki cyorezo.
Mu Buyapani, hashtag #ChineseDontComeToJapan yagiye mu ngingo zikunzwe cyane kuri Twitter.
