Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yise coronavirus "virusi y'Ubushinwa", ijambo ryakiriwe n'abamurwanyaga bavuga ko ari irondaruhu kandi ko arwanya Ubushinwa.
Abigaragambya muri Ukraine bagabye igitero kuri bisi zitwara Abanyukureyini n'abanyamahanga bakuwe mu mujyi wa Wuhan berekeza i Novi Sanzhary.
Abanyeshuri bo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde, buhana imbibi n'u Bushinwa, n'abanyeshuri bo mu mijyi minini y'u Buhinde bivugwa ko batotejwe kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Perezida w'ishyaka Bharatiya Janata mu ntara ya Bengal, Dilip Ghosh, yavuze ko Abashinwa basenyeye ibidukikije kandi "ni yo mpamvu Imana yabahindukiriye".
Nyuma yaho, ibyo byavuzwe n'ibiro by'Ubushinwa biri i Calcutta byamaganye ibyo byavuzwe, bivuga ko "bidakwiriye". Mu Bushinwa, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura rishingiye ku moko ku baturage batari Abashinwa byongerewe n'icyorezo, abanyamahanga bavugwaho ko ari "amasimbi y'abanyamahanga" kandi bagashyirwa mu "bikorwa byo kujugunya".
