Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus ya 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi itera SARS - CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura virusi n'ubundi bwo gutahura abasirikare b'umubiri bakomoka mu guhangana n'ubwandu.
Kuba virusi iri mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iki kizamini ni icy'umwihariko kandi cyakozwe hagamijwe gutahura RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyangwa bukiriho.
Kumenya ko hari abasirikare b'umubiri (serology) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gusuzuma no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyane ku buryo batabivuga cyangwa batagira ibimenyetso.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu bw'indwara n'ubwirinzi bw'umukumbi mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana neza binyuze mu bushakashatsi.
Kubera gupima ku rugero ruciriritse, muri Werurwe 2020 nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku bijyanye n'ubwandu bwa virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyakoze ibizamini ku bantu barenga 3% by'abaturage bacyo, kandi hari itandukaniro rinini mu bipimo bikorwa mu bihugu.
Ibi bishobora gutuma umubare w'abandura wiyongera cyane, ariko bishobora kuba biri hejuru cyane mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga rya Real-time reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR), isuzuma rishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo no guswera mu mazuru cyangwa mu marira.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make cyangwa mu minsi ibiri.
Igikorwa cya RT-PCR cyakozwe hakoreshejwe isuku y'urwungano rw'umunwa ni icyo kwiringirwa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara gusa.
Nyuma, virusi ishobora kuzimira mu muhogo mu gihe ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye bapimwe mu cyumweru cya kabiri, kimwe mu byagufasha, ibikoresho by'ibipimo bishobora gukurwa mu mwobo w'ubuhumekero binyuze mu cyuma cyo kunyoha cyangwa ibikoresho byatawe n'imyanda (umwanda) bishobora gukoreshwa.
Imwe mu ncuro za mbere y'igeragezwa rya PCR yakozwe muri Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 hakoreshejwe uburyo bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) ikora mu gihe cy'igihe, ikaba ari na yo ishingiyeho ibikoresho 250.000 byo gukwirakwiza ku Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech cyakoze ubwoko bw'ivuriro, kit yo gupima SARS-CoV-2 ishingiye kuri PCR (PowerCheck Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Ashakisha ubwoko bwa "E" busangirwa na virusi ya koronavirusi ya beta zose, n'ubwoko bwa RdRp, bwihariye SARS-CoV-2. Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni imwe mu masosiyete ya mbere yahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu Gishinzwe Ibicuruzwa by'Ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ku gikoresho cy'ubushakashatsi cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR. Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) kirimo gutanga ikigega cy'ubushakashatsi cya RT-PCR cya Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) mu gihe cyihariye ku bigo by'ubuvuzi mpuzamahanga binyuze mu ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cya Reagent Resource.
