Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyigeze byemerwa ko ari byo by'ukuri kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, ari bwo laboratwari z'inzego z'ibanze n'iz'intara zemerewe gutangira gukora ibizamini.
