Guhera ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ikizamini cya COVID-19 gishingiye kuri RT-PCR kizaba kiboneka mu gihugu cyose.
Quest Diagnostics kandi yatumye ibizamini bya COVID-19 biboneka mu gihugu cyose guhera ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gihagararo cy'umubare cyatangajwe; isuzuma n'imikorere y'ibipimo bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu by'Ubwanduzi n'Ikoranabuhanga, VECTOR.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe na Federal Health Watch Service. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Mayo Clinic yatangaje ko imaze gukora ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3,5 ku gipimo kinini, bityo bigatuma imashini ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse (USA) ku bigo by'ubushakashatsi bya Abbott kugirango bikore igerageza kuri sisitemu ya Abbott m2000; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya ku Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid na yo yahawe USA na FDA mu igerageza ryamaze iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingufu za nucleic acid mu mwanya wa PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko habaho imirongo myinshi y'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota itanu gusa, n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Ubu muri Amerika hari ibyuma nk'ibyo bigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott yiteze ko izongera umusaruro wayo kugira ngo itange ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Ikigeragezo gikoresha umuti wa monoclonal kandi kikayihuza na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (poroteyine N) ya koronavirusi nshya kiri gukorwa muri Tayiwani, biteganyijwe ko kizatanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo bya rubagimpande.
