Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika Gishinzwe Imiti n'Ibiribwa (American College of Radiology) cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'igerageza rya mbere ryo gupima COVID-19". Guhera muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yongeye gutanga inama yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima mbere.
