Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu mu bantu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso mu minsi 7 cyangwa nyuma gato y'aho, mu gupima ubudahangarwa, no kugenzura abaturage. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi (CLT) cyangwa binyuze mu gupima mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi (PoCT).
Sisitemu zikoranabuhanga zifite umusaruro mwinshi mu mavuriro menshi zizashobora gukora ibi bizamini, ariko kuba zihari bizaterwa n'umubare w'ibikoresho bizakora.
Ku CLT, hakoreshwa icyitegererezo kimwe cy'amaraso y'ibanze, nubwo ibipimo byinshi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana igisubizo cy'umubiri.
Ku bw'iyo poroteyine, amaraso amwe atangwa mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, intambwe yo gukusanya ntiisaba mbere yo gupimwa. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, FDA yagaragaje ibigo 29 byamenyesheje ikigo nk'uko bisabwa, kandi ubu byemerewe gutanga ibizamini byabo by'abasirikare b'umubiri.
Guhera ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ikigo kimwe gusa nicyo cyemejwe na FDA gifite uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics byahawe imyanzuro y'iburayi ku bikoresho byabo byo gupima, bishobora gutahura IgG na IgA antibodies kuri virusi mu bipimo by'amaraso.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima ni ibipimo amagana menshi mu masaha make, bityo bikaba byihuta cyane kurusha ibizamini bisanzwe bya PCR bya RNA ya virusi.
