Hong Kong yashyizeho uburyo bwo kurinda abarwayi bakekwaho ubwandu kuguma mu rugo, "urwego rw'ubutabazi ruzaha umurwayi uruziga rwo gufata ibipimo", bagomba gusuka amacandwe mu ruziga, bakayasubiza hanyuma bakabona umusaruro nyuma y'igihe gito. NHS y'Ubwongereza yatangaje ko irimo guhuza uburyo bwo gupima abarwayi bakekwaho ubwandu mu rugo, bigabanya ibyago byo kwanduza abandi umurwayi niba bagiye kwa muganga cyangwa gukenera kuvura ambulansi niba hari ikoreshwa. Mu gupima imodoka kuri COVID-19 ku bantu bakekwaho ubwandu, umukozi ushinzwe gukusanya ibipimo afata ingamba zikwiye.
