Ibiciro by'ibizamini bitangwa n'ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima iyo umuganga abisabye.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi busesuye bwo gupima abantu 160.000 mu cyumweru.
Kuva ku ya 19 Werurwe, abantu batangiye kugeragezwa mu modoka mu mijyi minini.
Kuva ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwamenyekanye kuko ibizamini byemewe gusa ari byo byanditswe.
Ikigo cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi cyagaragaje ko kuva mu cyumweru cya 12 cya 2020 hatangiye gupimwa nibura ibipimo 483,295 kugeza mu cyumweru cya 12 cya 2020 kandi ibipimo 33,491 (6,9%) byageragejwe ko bifite SARS-CoV-2. Muri Isirayeli, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam bakoze kandi bagerageza uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo by'abarwayi 64 icyarimwe, bakoranya ibipimo kandi bagakora ibindi bipimo gusa mu gihe ibipimo by'abapfuye byose hamwe byaba byemejwe ko bifite ibimenyetso. I Wuhan, ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyagenewe cya metero kare 2000 cyiswe "Huo-Yan" (mu Gishinwa: 火眼, cyangwa "Fire Eye" mu Cyongereza) cyatangijwe ku ya 5 Gashyantare 2020 na BGI, gishobora gutunganya ibipimo birenga ibihumbi 10 ku munsi.
Kubera ko imirimo yo kubaka yari iyobowe n'uwashinze BGI, Wang Jian, kandi ikaba yaramaze iminsi 5, imiterere yagaragaje ko ubwandu muri Hubei bwari kuba ari bwinshi ku kigero cya 47% kandi ikiguzi cyo guhangana n'ikurwa mu kato cyari kuzikuba kabiri iyo ubu bushobozi bwo gupima butaba bufite uburyo bwo kugera kuri interineti.
Laboratwari ya Wuhan yahise ikurikirwa na Huo-Yan Laboratories i Shenzhen, Tianjin, Beijing, na Shanghai, mu mijyi 12 yose yo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 4 Werurwe 2020, umusaruro w'umunsi wose wari ibihumbi 50 by'ibizamini ku munsi. Ibishushanyo mbonera by'isoko rusange bya Origami Assays byashyizwe ahagaragara ko bishobora gupima ibipimo byabarwayi 1122 kuri COVID-19, hifashishijwe ibizamini 93 gusa. Ibi bishushanyo mbonera byuzuye bishobora gukorerwa muri laboratwari ntoya bidakeneye imashini za robo zikora amazi.
Muri Werurwe, ibura cyangwa kutagira ibipimo bihagije by'imiti byabaye imbogamizi mu gupima abantu benshi mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
Ibi byatumye bamwe mu banditsi biga ku mabwiriza yo gutegura ibipimo by'ibipimo bigizwe no gushyushya ibipimo ku gipimo cya 98 °C (208 °F) mu gihe cy'iminota 5 kugira ngo genome za RNA zishobore kugeragezwa. Ku ya 31 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Abarabu ubu ziri gukora ibizamini byinshi ku muturage wacyo kuri Coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu, kandi ko ziri mu nzira yo kongera igipimo no kugera ku baturage benshi.
Ibi byatewe n'ihurizo ry'ubushobozi bwo gutwara abantu, no kugura ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku gipimo cy'abaturage cya Group 42 na BGI (cyatewe inkunga na laboratwari zayo zo gupima byihuse "Huo-Yan" mu Bushinwa).
Yubatswe mu minsi 14, iki kigo gishobora gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ku munsi kandi ni cyo cya mbere ku isi cyakozwe hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Uburyo butandukanye bwo gupima bugamije kureba ibice bitandukanye by'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo ya koronavirusi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa, u Bufaransa, u Budage, Hong Kong, u Buyapani na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyize mu bikorwa uburyo bw'u Budage bwo gukora ibikoresho byo kohereza mu bihugu bifite amikoro make bidafite ubushobozi bwo kubyikorera.
Uburyo bw'Abadage bwatangajwe ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; porogaramu yakozwe n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ntiyabonekaga kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, habayeho gutinda mu bipimo byahawe Amerika n'u Bushinwa, kandi Amerika yahuye n'ibibazo bijyanye no kwiringirwa kw'ibikoresho byo gupima hakiri kare mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, kandi ibyo bihugu hamwe na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo guhaza ibyifuzo n'inama z'abaganga ku bipimo.
Ku rundi ruhande, impuguke zivuga ko kuba Koreya y'Epfo ifite ubushobozi bwinshi bwo gupima byafashije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya koronavirusi nshya.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima, ahanini mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi by'abikorera, bwatewe imbere mu myaka myinshi na leta ya Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko kongera gahunda zo gupima ari bwo buryo bwiza bwo kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo cya COVID-19. Ibyifuzo byinshi byo gupima bitewe n'ikwirakwira rya virusi byatumye amajana y'ibihumbi by'ibizamini mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga byo muri Amerika bidindira, kandi itangwa ry'ibikoresho by'ibishyimbo n'ibikoresho by'imiti by'imiti byarabangamiwe.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari ibibazo by'ubunyangamugayo mu bikoresho by'ibizamini.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, ibikoresho by'ibizamini byakozwe na CDC byagaragaje "amakosa"; leta yahise ikuraho inzitizi z'ubutegetsi zabuzaga abantu kwipimisha. Espagne yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini byakozwe n'ikigo cyo mu Bushinwa Shenzhen Bioeasy Biotechnology Co Ltd, ariko ivuga ko ibisubizo bitari byo.
Iryo shyirahamwe ryasobanuye ko ibisubizo bitari byo bishobora guterwa n'ikosa mu gufata ibipimo cyangwa gukoresha nabi ibikoresho.
Minisitiri wa Espagne yavuze ko azahagarika ibikoresho byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo, akabisimbuza ibindi byatanzwe na Shenzhen Bioeasy. 80% by'ibikoresho by'ibizamini Repubulika ya Tchèque yaguze mu Bushinwa byatanze ibisubizo bitari byo. Slovakia yaguze ibikoresho by'ibizamini miriyoni 1,2 by'u Bushinwa byemejwe ko bidafite ukuri.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Matovic yagaragaje ko bazabijugunya mu Ruzi rwa Danube. Ates Kara wo muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Turukiya yavuze ko ibikoresho byo gupima bya Turukiya byaguzwe mu Bushinwa byari bifite "ibipimo byinshi by'ikosa" kandi ko "atazabikoresha". Ubwongereza bwaguze ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 3.5 mu Bushinwa, ariko mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020 butangaza ko nta kamaro bifite.
Gupima, hakurikiwe no gushyira mu kato abantu bagaragayeho ko banduye no gukurikirana abantu bahuye n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, byagize ingaruka nziza.
Abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Vò mu Butaliyani, ahishwe umuntu wa mbere azize COVID-19 mu Butaliyani, bakoze ibizamini bibiri ku baturage bose bagera ku 3.400, mu gihe cy'iminsi igera ku icumi.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abantu basanze bafite ibimenyetso nta bimenyetso na kimwe bari bafite, kandi abamaze kuboneka bose bashyizwe mu kato.
Kubera ko abantu batemerewe kujya muri komine, byatumye nta muntu urwara.
Kubera ko abantu benshi bagenzurwa, ingendo zikabuzanywa, gupimwa no gushyirwa mu kato, icyorezo cya koronavirusi muri 2020 muri Singapuru cyateye imbere buhoro cyane kurusha mu bindi bihugu byateye imbere, kandi nta ngamba zikomeye zashyizweho nko gufunga amazu y'ubucuruzi n'amaresitora.
Ibikorwa byinshi byahagaritswe, kandi Singapore yatangiye guha inama abaturage ku buryo bukomeye ko baguma mu ngo zabo ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko amashuri yongeye gufungura nyuma y'ikiruhuko ku ya 23 Werurwe.
Ibihugu byinshi na byo byayoboye iki cyorezo binyuze mu kugenzura cyane abo byagiye bigiraho ingaruka, kugabanya ingendo, gupima no gushyira mu kato, ariko mu buryo budahangayikishije cyane, urugero nka Isilande na Koreya y'Epfo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe bwagaragaje ko ibihugu byakoze ibizamini byinshi, ku bijyanye n'umubare w'abapfuye, byagize umubare muto w'abapfa, wenda kubera ko ibyo bihugu bishobora gutahura neza abafite ibimenyetso bike cyangwa nta na kimwe.
OMS irasaba ibihugu bidafite ubushobozi bwo gupima kandi bifite laboratwari z'igihugu zifite ubumenyi buke kuri COVID-19 kohereza ibipimo bitanu bya mbere by'abanduye na cumi bya mbere by'abanduye muri imwe muri laboratwari 16 za OMS zishinzwe gupima kugira ngo zibemeze ko byanduye.
Muri za laboratwari 16 z'ibanze, 7 ziri muri Aziya, 5 ziri mu Burayi, 2 muri Afurika, 1 muri Amerika ya Ruguru na 1 muri Ositaraliya.
Mu mbonerahamwe ikurikira, umurongo 'Igice cy'abakoze ibizamini byagize umusaruro mwiza' uterwa n'itegeko ry'igihugu rigenga ibizamini.
Igihugu kigenzura abantu bari mu bitaro gusa, kizaba gifite igipimo cy'abantu benshi bapimwe neza kurusha igihugu kigenzura abaturage bose, baba bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa nta byo bafite, ibindi byose ni kimwe.
Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, ni igikorwa cyo gukaraba intoki hagamijwe gukuraho umwanda, ibinure, mikorobe, cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni buri gihe mu "bihe bikomeye" by'umunsi, bifasha kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibiheri na kolera, zikwirakwizwa mu kanwa n'amaraso.
Abantu bashobora no kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane bisanzwe, urugero niba badakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa akanwa (ni ukuvuga muhogo).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa harimo: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo guhanagura umwana cyangwa kumuhindurira indabo, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere na nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, inyama cyangwa amafi.
Iyo amazi n'isabune bidahari, intoki zishobora gukaraba n'imyotsi. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritanga inama yo gukaraba intoki:
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura ibyokurya.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Nyuma yo guhindura inda cyangwa gusukura umwana wakoresheje ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo cyangwa umwanda w'amatungo.
Isuku y'intoki mu buvuzi ni isuku ijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwita ku barwayi bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Intego y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki ni ukuzimya udukoko dutera indwara (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bintu bishobora gutera indwara) n'imiti ishobora kwangiza cyangwa kurwara.
Ibi ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakoresha ibiribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zitandura; gukumira indwara zandura ziterwa n'umushishito; kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko imyitwarire myiza yo gukaraba intoki ishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura neza.
Mu bihugu byateye imbere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ibiheri n'izindi ndwara z'ubuhumekero ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hagize ibintu bihinduka mu myitwarire yabo, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo myifatire yoroheje ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abahitanwa n'ibyo byorezo ugera hafi kuri 50%.
Gushyiraho ingamba zo gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya indwara z'ibiheri ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, bikaba bisa no kugeza amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
48% by'igabanuka ry'ibyago byo kuribwa n'umushishito bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no gukaraba intoki n'isabuni. Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ni bwo buryo bwiza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda kuribwa n'umushishito n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (IRA), nk'uko bikorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Imyotsi, icyorezo cy'indwara ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero, ni cyo kintu cya mbere kihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, kikaba cyica abana bagera kuri miriyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Indwara y'ibisebe n'imyotsi hamwe ni byo bituma abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3,5 bapfa buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri umubare w'abapfa bazize iseseme, n'icyiciro kimwe cya kane cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bijyana n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku nk'igice cya gahunda z'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki kandi birinda impetigo yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi idasanzwe yo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma umubiri uhomba bitewe n'uko umubiri wumye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ikibazo cy'uruhu rufite ibihuha bita eczema cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, kandi ngo bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi na byo bigaragara nk'ikimenyetso cy'indwara y'ubushake bukabije (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi ku munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'umuhogo n'iz'amaraso: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (gukoropa, kohereza), nyuma yo gusukura amabere y'umwana (guhindura indabo), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, na mbere/nyuma yo gutegura ibiryo cyangwa gukorana n'inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko itarimo.
Mu bindi bihe aho gukaraba intoki neza bigomba gukoreshwa mu kwirinda kwandura indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo gukira igikomere cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo guhekenya, gukorora cyangwa gukorora; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorana n'amatungo; no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, hari umubare muto w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi ku gukaraba intoki mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, imiryango 38.7% yari ifite akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabuni. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ifite igipimo kiri hejuru ku kigero cya 97%, Amerika iri hafi ku kigereranyo cya 77%, naho Ubushinwa bukaba bufite igipimo kiri hasi ku kigero cya 23%. Uburyo butandukanye bwo guhindura imyitwarire ubu buraboneka kugira ngo bongere kwemerwa ku muco wo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mu bihe bikomeye. Gukaraba intoki mu matsinda ku bana mu mashuri mu bihe runaka by'umunsi ni ubundi buryo mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere bwo gucengeza imikoreshereze y'intoki mu bana.
"Gahunda y'Ibikorwa by'Ubuzima Binyuranye n'Icyiciro cy'ibanze" ishyirwa mu bikorwa n'Urwego rw'Uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'ibikorwa bikomeye byo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana.
Gukuraho udukoko kabiri mu mwaka, byuzujwe no gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabuni, gukaraba amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fluorine, biri mu by'ingenzi muri iyi gahunda y'igihugu.
Ryakorewe kandi neza muri Indonesia.
Gukuraho udukoko duto two ku ruhu birashimangirwa no kongeramo amasabune n'imiti yo gusukura amazi.
Igikorwa cy'ingenzi cy'amasabune n'imiti yo gusukura ni ukugabanya inzitizi ku muti, no kongera uburyo bwo gusukura.
Amazi yonyine ni umuti ufasha mu gusukura uruhu, kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ibintu bigize umwanda w'ibinyabuzima, ntibishobora gukama mu mazi.
Ariko kandi, isuku irushaho koroherwa n'amazi ahagije...
Amasabuni yo mu miba, bitewe n'imiterere yayo ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ashobora gukomeza mikorobe z'ibyakoreshejwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwakozwe ku mikorobe zituruka ku isabune yanduye mu kabati bwerekanye ko nta mikorobe ishobora kuyandura kuko iyo mikorobe ikoreshwa mu gusukura.
CDC yongeyeho ko "isabune y'amazi ifite amabwiriza y'imiti ikoreshwa ari yo ikwiye".
Amasabune arwanya za mikorobe yamenyekanye cyane ku baturage bazi ubuzima.
Kugeza ubu, nta kimenyetso na kimwe kigaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yo guhashya cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura indwara ishobora gutuma habaho ibinyabuzima bidashobora kurwanya imiti mu ishyamba.
Ariko kandi, amasabune arwanya za mikorobe arimo imiti isanzwe irwanya za mikorobe, urugero nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rurerure rw'udukoko twirinda.
Bityo, nubwo imiti irwanya ibiyobyabwenge idashobora gukoreshwa mu myambaro igabanya ubukana bwa za mikorobe, ishobora kuba idakora neza nk'uko bivugwa.
Usibye ibicuruzwa by'ibinyabutabire n'ibikoresho byo kurinda uruhu, uburyo buhambaye bushobora kuba bufite aside (acide acétique, ascorbic acid, acide lactique) nk'umuyobozi wa pH, acide benzoïque ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bikoresho byoroshya uruhu (aloe vera, vitamini, menthol, ibimera). Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oregon School of Public Health bwagaragaje ko isabune isanzwe igira ingaruka nziza mu gukumira indwara no gukuraho mikorobe ku biganza nk'isabuni z'abakoresha imiti igabanya mikorobe zirimo triclosan.
Amazi ashyushye akwiriye gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ku buryo yica mikorobe.
Iyo umubiri ufite ubushyuhe bwa dogere 37 (Celsius 37), mikorobe zikura vuba.
Ariko kandi, amazi ashyushye n'isabune ni meza cyane kurusha amazi akonje n'isabune mu gukuraho amavuta asanzwe abamo imyanda na za mikorobe.
Ariko kandi, mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko abantu benshi babitekereza, ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi bwagaragaje ko gukoresha amazi ashyushye bidatuma udukoko two mu maboko yacu tugabanuka.
Umwandazi w'amaboko cyangwa umuti w'ibicurane ni umuti w'amaboko udakoreshwa amazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki bitagira amazi bishingiye ku nzoga (bizwi kandi nka alcohol-based hand sanitizer, antiseptic hand sanitizer, cyangwa hand sanitizer) byatangiye kwamamara.
Byinshi bikorwa ku bw'inzoga za isopropylique cyangwa za ethanol zikozwe mu buryo bw'imiti ikomeza, nka karubomeri (polymère cyangwa acrylic acid), mu mazi, cyangwa mu buryo bw'amazi, nka glycérine, cyangwa mu busa kugira ngo byorohereze imikoreshereze no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumeneka kwa alcohol.
Kongeramo hydrogen peroxide byongera ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe. Amata y'ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki arimo nibura 60 kugeza kuri 95% by'inzoga yica mikorobe neza.
Imiti ikoreshwa mu gusukura umubiri ikoresheje inzoga yica mikorobe, mikorobe zidakira indwara nyinshi (MRSA na ERV), igituntu, na za virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo virusi itera SIDA, herpes, RSV, mikorobe z'amahembe, urukingo, ibicurane n'indwara y'umwijima) na fungus.
Imiti yo gusukura intoki ifite alcohol 70%, yica 99,97% (igabanuka rya logarithme 3,5 nk'igabanuka rya decibel 35) y'udukoko two ku maboko, hashize amasegonda 30 uyikoresheje, na 99,99% kugeza kuri 99,999% (igabanuka rya logarithme 4-5) y'udukoko two ku maboko nyuma y'umunota umwe uyikoresheje. Imiti yo gusukura intoki igira ingaruka nziza ku mikorobe ariko ntiyifashe neza ku mikorobe zimwe na zimwe.
Imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga nta cyo imaze na gato ku virusi ya norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk), yo ituma indwara y'igifu idakira. Imiti yo gusukura intoki cyangwa imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga ishobora gukoreshwa mu gusukura intoki cyangwa kuyitwikira neza.
Nyuma n'ibiganza, hagati y'intoki n'ibice by'intoki, bisukwaho amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugeza amazi, ifu cyangwa umutobe byumye.
Ibikumwe by'intoki na byo bigomba gukaraba neza, bikanyunyuzwa intoki zombi. Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imiti yo kwiyuhagira, cyane cyane iyo intoki ziba zanduye.
Imikoreshereze y'ibyo bikoresho iri kwiyongera ishingiye ku kuntu bikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye kandi bwihuse mu kurandura mikorobe; ariko, ntibikwiye gusimbura gukaraba intoki neza, keretse niba isabune n'amazi bihari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga bishobora gutuma uruhu rukama keretse iyo imyuka ihumura cyangwa imyenda y'uruhu yongeyeho.
Ingaruka zo gukama za alcohol zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa zikarandurwa no kongera glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bintu by'imishinga mu buryo.
Mu igerageza ry'imiti, imiti yo guhanagura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo imyanda ituma umuntu agira isesemi n'irondaruhu ku mubiri, byagabanutse cyane ugereranyije n'amasabune cyangwa imiti yo guhanagura indwara.
Indwara y'uruhu ituma umuntu ahura n'indwara y'uruhu, indwara y'umwanda w'uruhu cyangwa kumva inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu bikoreshwa mu gusukura intoki z'abantu bafite inzoga, si kenshi biba.
Kuba abantu badafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'uruhu, byahindutse ikintu cyiza ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo bikora neza, imiti itagira amazi ntiyuhagira intoki z'ibinyabuzima, ahubwo irazihumanya gusa.
Niyo mpamvu imiti yo gusukura intoki idakora neza nk'amazi n'isabuni mu gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, kuko indwara zikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Imikorere y'imiti yo gusukura intoki idafite alukoro ishingiye cyane ku bikoresho n'uburyo ikoreshwamo, kandi mu mateka yagiye iri inyuma cyane y'imiti yo gusukura intoki ikoresha alukoro n'imiti ikoresha alukoro.
Mu minsi ishize, imiti ikoresha benzalkonium chloride yagaragaye ko igira umuti wa 'antimicrobial' ukomeza kandi ugenda wiyongera nyuma yo gukoreshwa, bitandukanye n'inzoga, yagaragaye ko igira ingaruka nke nyuma yo gukoreshwa kenshi, bishoboka ko bitewe n'ingaruka mbi z'uruhu.
Abantu benshi mu baturage badafite amikoro menshi ntibashobora kwigurira isabune, ahubwo bakoresha imyanda cyangwa ubutaka.
Ivu cyangwa ivumbi bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi meza, ariko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi kurusha isabune.
Hari impungenge ko niba ubutaka cyangwa ivu byanduye mikorobe, kwandura kw'indwara bishobora kwiyongera aho kugabanuka.
Kimwe n'isabune, imivu ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo ihuye n'amazi ihinduka umunyu.
OMS itera inkunga umwotsi n'umusenyi nk'uburyo bwo gusimbuza isabune iyo nta sabune ihari.
Uburyo bwiza bwo gukaraba intoki bwasabwe n'Ikigo cya Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara, bukubiyemo intambwe zikurikira:
Gukaraba intoki n'amazi ashyushye cyangwa akonje.
Amazi yo mu mazi ni yo akwiriye kuko imifuka ihoraho ishobora kwandura, mu gihe ubushyuhe bw'amazi busa n'aho nta cyo buvuze.
Gukaraba intoki, ukazikorakora isabune nyinshi, harimo n'inyuma y'intoki, hagati y'intoki n'inyuma y'amano.
Amasabune akura mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakunda gukaraba intoki neza iyo bakoresheje isabune aho gukoresha amazi meza.
Gusigaho nibura amasegonda 20.
Gukaraba bituma uruhu ruhuha, bigatuma habaho gutakaza mikorobe ku ruhu, kandi gukaraba igihe kirekire cyane bituma habaho gutakaza mikorobe nyinshi.
Jya usukura neza amazi arimo.
Gukaraba mu isuku bishobora kongera kwanduza intoki.
Kumesa n'umwenda ushyushye cyangwa ukabisiga hanze.
Ibiganza byumye cyangwa byumye birushaho kwandura vuba. Ibice bikunze kwibagirwa ni urutoki, ikiganza, hagati y'intoki n'imbere y'amano.
Inzara z'ibihimba by'umubiri n'amabara y'ibinyabuzima bishobora kuba bifite mikorobe.
Akenshi, imiti ikomeza umubiri kugira ngo amaboko yawe agume afite amazi, irabafasha kuko uruhu rwumye rushobora gutuma rukomereka, bigatuma indwara zandurira mu mubiri.
Hari uburyo butandukanye bw'igiciro gito bushobora gukorwa mu koroshya gukaraba intoki aho amazi y'amazi n'isabune bidahari, urugero nko kuvoma amazi mu kabindi cyangwa mu isuku ifite imyobo ikwiriye, no/cyangwa gukoresha imyanda niba ari ngombwa mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere. Mu bihe aho amazi aba make (urugero nk'amashuri cyangwa uduce two mu cyaro mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubika amazi, nk' "amacupa y'imashini" n'ubundi buryo buhendutse.
Igikarabiro cy'imashini ni ikoranabuhanga ryoroshye rikoresha urwabya ruhagaze ku mugozi, n'inkokora ikoreshwa n'ibirenge kugira ngo basuke amazi make mu ntoki n'isabune.
Kumesa neza intoki ni ikintu cy'ingenzi mu gusukura intoki, ariko hari impaka ku buryo bwiza bwo kuzimesa mu bwiherero rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bugenda bwiyongera bugaragaza ko impapuro z'ibyatsi ari nziza cyane kurusha utwuma two kurotsa intoki dukoreshwa n'amashanyarazi dusanga mu byumba byinshi by'ubwiherero.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, i Londres, kandi bwatewe inkunga n'uruganda rw'impapuro z'impu, European Tissue Symposium, kugira ngo bagereranye igipimo cy'isuku cyatanzwe n'impapuro z'impu, ibyuma bishyushya intoki n'ibyuma bishyushya intoki bigezweho.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki mu gihe cy'imvura, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange wariyongereyeho 194% mu gice cy'intoki kiri hafi y'intoki, naho mu gice cy'inyuma cyacyo ho wiyongeraho 254%.
Gukoresha ibyuma byo kumesa by'umwuka byongereye umubare w'indwara muri rusange, ku kigereranyo cya 42% mu gice cy'ikiganza kiri hafi y'intoki, na 15% mu gice gisigaye cy'ikiganza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no kumesa intoki bakoresheje impapuro z'igikarabiro, umubare w'udukoko muri rusange wagabanutse ku kigereranyo cya 76% mu gice cy'ikiganza kiri hafi y'intoki no ku kiganza gisigaye cyagabanutseho 77%. Abashakashatsi bakoze n'ibizamini kugira ngo bamenye niba hari ibyago byo kwandura abandi bakoresha n'aho mu bwiherero bitewe n'uburyo bw'umwuko.
Umushongi w'umwuka uturitsa umwuka mu cyumba cy'ubwiherero ku muvuduko wa metero 180/s (650 km/h; 400 mph), washoboye kwirukana mikorobe mu biganza no mu cyumba cy'ubwiherero, zishobora kwanduza abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ahandi hantu mu ntera ya metero 2.
Gukoresha umwumazi w'amaboko ushyushye wangiza mikorobe mu metero 0,25 z'umwumazi.
Impapuro z'igitambaro ntizagaragaje ikwirakwira ry'udukoko duto cyane. Mu mwaka wa 2005, mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt na Umwelt, uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa intoki bwaranenzwe.
Dore impinduka mu mubare wa bagiteri nyuma yo kumesa intoki:
Hari ababikora batandukanye, kandi ibyo bikoresho byagereranywa no gukaraba mu rupapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje utwenda tw'amaboko tw'isuku ni uburyo bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cyo kubura isabune n'amazi mu gihe cy'ingendo.
Ibikoresho byo gusukura intoki bikoresha inzoga bigomba kuba bifite nibura 60% bya inzoga.
Gukaraba intoki mu bitaro byabaye itegeko nyuma y'igihe kirekire umuganga w'Umunyahongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis avuze ko ari ingirakamaro (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
