Niba uhuye n'umuntu mu buryo butaziguye mu gihe cyo gufata, abakozi bagomba gusukura no guhanagura udukingirizo n'ibindi bikoresho byabo mbere yo kongera kubikoresha bakoresheje isupu cyangwa umwenda usanzwe wo gusukura urugo kandi bagakurikiza inzira zisanzwe z'imikorere yo gukingira no gutunganya PPE yambaye no gukingira no gukaraba imyenda.
OSHA ifata abakozi bamwe na bamwe mu by'ubuzima n'abakora mu birindiro nk'abafite ibyago byinshi cyangwa byinshi byo guhura n'ibiyobyabwenge.
Imirimo ishobora guteza abantu indwara harimo abakora mu bijyanye no gutanga imiti, kwita ku barwayi, mu by'ubushakashatsi no mu gutwara abagwayi, bashobora guhura n'abarwayi bagaragaweho cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Ibyago byo kwandura birushaho kwiyongera iyo abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo kuvura abarwayi bafite COVID-19 yemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho, cyangwa bakorakoranya cyangwa bagakora ku bipimo by'abo barwayi.
Imikorere yo gukora aérosols ikubiyemo guterwa intanga, gutera inkorora, gusohora umwuka, imikorere imwe n'imwe n'ibizamini byo kwa muganga cyangwa gutoragura ibipimo by'imiti.
Imirimo ikorerwa mu bigo by'ubupfumu birimo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imibiri y'abantu bafite COVID-19 yemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho uburwayi mu gihe bapfuye; ibyago byo kuboneka birushaho kwiyongera iyo bakoze ubushakashatsi. Ibindi bikorwa by'ubwubatsi kuri abo bantu bafite ibyago birimo ibyumba by'ubwigunge by'abarwayi bafite COVID-19 yemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho uburwayi, harimo n'igihe hakorwa uburyo bwo gukora imashini zitanga umwuka.
Umuvuduko uhagije wo guhumeka ushobora kuba ukwiriye mu bihe bimwe na bimwe byo gupfusha no mu rwego rw'ubuzima.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa mu buryo bw'ubwitonzi bwo ku rwego rwa 3 mu bijyanye n'ubuziranenge.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) risaba ko abarwayi binjira ibitaro batandukanywa mu bice bibiri bitandukanye by'indembe bitewe n'uko bakekwaho COVID-19. Usibye ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, OSHA isaba ko abarwayi bakorera ku birometero 6 uvuye ku barwayi banduye cyangwa bakekwaho SARS-CoV-2, n'abakora ibikorwa byo gukora imashini zitanga umwuka.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, udupfukamunwa two mu maso dufite udukoko twitwa N95 twemewe na NIOSH cyangwa udupfukamunwa tw'ubwiza bwo hejuru tugomba gukoreshwa mu rwego rw'igikorwa cy'ubwirinzi bwo guhumeka cyuzuye kandi cyanditse kirimo gupimwa, amahugurwa no gusuzumwa n'abaganga.
Ubundi buryo bwo guhumeka bushobora kurinda no gutuma umukozi arushaho kumererwa neza. OMS ntidushishikariza kwambara amakoti kuko COVID-19 ari indwara y'ubuhumekero, kandi idashobora kwandura binyuze mu mazi atari y'ubuhumekero.
OMS itera inkunga abasirikare bakora mu rwego rwo gupima abarwayi ku mupaka gusa kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Ku bakozi bakusanya ibipimo by'ubuhumekero, bavura cyangwa batwara abarwayi bafite COVID-19 badafite uburyo bwo gukora umwuka, OMS itera inkunga y'uko umuntu akenera agapfukamunwa, indorerwamo cyangwa udukingirizo tw'amaso, umwenda w'indorerwamo n'utugati.
Niba hakorwa uburyo bwo gukora aérosol, agapfukamunwa ko mu gihe cyo kubaga gasimbuzwa agapfukamunwa ka N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ibikoresho bya PPE ku isi yose bidahagije, OMS irasaba kugabanya cyane ibyo bikenerwa binyuze mu kuvura hakoreshejwe terefone, inzitizi z'umubiri nko kugira amadirishya asukuye, kwemerera gusa abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi kwinjira mu cyumba kimwe n'umurwayi ufite COVID-19, gukoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe mu kazi runaka, gukoresha umufasha guhumeka umwe nta kumukuraho mu gihe uvura abarwayi benshi bafite icyorezo kimwe, kugenzura no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho bya PPE no guca intege abantu batagaragaza ibimenyetso byo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
