Ingingo ya 2 ihindura angiotensin (ECA2) ni ingirabuzimafatizo ifatanye n'urusobe rw'inyuma (urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) rw'ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ECA2 ihagarika ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin II kandi igatuma Ang (1-7) yiyongera, bituma iba umuti wizeye mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ECA2 ikora kandi nk'aho abanduye koronavirusi bamwe binjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme ku bantu bukunze kwitwa hECA2.
Ingingo ya 2 ihindura angiotensin ni metaloenzym irimo zinc, iba ku gice cy'umubiri w'umubiri n'ibindi byuma.
Poroteyine ya ECA2 ifite igice cya N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal domain itwara amino acids na colectin mu gitsina.
ECA2 ni ubwoko bw'indimu ya poroteyine ya 1 y'uruhu, ifite uruziga rw'urusobe rw'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu zindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Uruhare rwa ECA2 rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo rurasenyuka ruva ku rundi ruhande rw'urusobe rw'umubiri n'indi ngirabuzima yitwa sheddase, maze poroteyine ivamo ikagenda mu maraso, hanyuma ikajya mu rukanga.
ECA2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ECA2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bwa II, uturemangingo two mu mara duto, uturemangingo tw'amaraso n'utw'amaraso n'utw'umusatsi n'utw'umusatsi mu ngingo nyinshi.
Igikorwa cya mRNA ya ECA2 kiboneka no mu bwonko, mu mubiri wa striatum, hypothalamus, no mu bwonko.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ECA2 ni ugukora nk'urwego rwo kurwanya ECA.
IDA ikora ikuramo ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin ya I ikayigira ingirabuzima fatizo ya II, bigatuma amaraso atangira kuvira mu maraso.
ECA2 nayo ihindura phenylalanine ya amino acide ya carboxytermine ikoresheje angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikongera ikayivanga na angiotensin yo kwa muganga (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-Gist-Pro-OH).
ECA2 nayo ihindura ibindi bice byinshi bya peptides, harimo [des-Arg9]- bradicinine, apeline, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na ghrelin.
ECA2 kandi itegeka uburyo bwo gutwara amino acide mu buryo butandukanye SLC6A19 kandi byanagize uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'indwara y'uruhu, ECA2 ikora nk'ahantu h'ibanze ha virus zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 ku gice cya ECA2 ku rwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo bigatuma virusi na enzyme byinjira mu mubiri no mu byuma biri mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira kandi isaba ko poroteyine S itegurwa na TMPRSS2 serine-protease, ikumira iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'umuti ushobora gufasha, ibyo byatumye bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ECA2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Ariko kandi, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe amategeko, zasabye ko hakomezaho uburyo bwo gukumira ACE n'uburyo bwo kuvura ARB.
Isesengura ryagaragaye ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 ryasanze "ikoreshwa rya ACE inhibitors rifite ingaruka ku kugabanya cyane ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abatabifite".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara ibicurane byaragabanutse no ku barwayi bahabwa imiti igabanya ubukana bwa ACE bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibicurane, cyane cyane abafite indwara y'uruhu n'umutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors nabyo byahujwe no kugabanya impfu ziterwa na Pneumonia, nubwo ibisubizo byagiye birushaho kuba bike ugereranyije n'ibyavuye mu isesengura ry'indwara ya Pneumonia".
ECA2 y'abantu (rhACE2) yizerwa ko ari uburyo bushya bwo kuvura uburwayi bw'ibihaha, kandi bwagaragaye ko bwahinduye imikorere y'amaraso y'ibihaha n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu ngurube zifite ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba bw'ibihaha.
Igihe cy'iherezo cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 kandi gutangira gukora ni nyuma y'iminota 30 nyuma y'igihe cy'amasaha 24 (igihe cy'amasaha).
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku barwayi batemera imiti ikumira indwara ya Renin-Angiotensin System (RAS) cyangwa indwara ziterwa n'umubyibuho ukabije wa angiotensin II. RhACE2 yatangijwe yagenzuwe mu igeragezwa mu buvuzi mu kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba.
