Ibisubizo bishingiye ku muyoboro bifite ubushobozi bwo kubona amakuru y'aho umuntu ari mu buryo bw'ibanze bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Ariko, ntabwo sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru zigomba kubona amakuru yerekeye ahantu umuntu ari; uburyo bwinshi bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite bwashyizweho kugirango zikoreshe seriveri nkuru gusa mu guhanahana amakuru (reba igice gikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu mu gukora isuzuma ry'abantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu imwe gusa, iyi sisitemu yakoranyije amakuru yo gukurikirana avuye ahantu hatandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'amakuru y'ibicuruzwa bya banki, maze ayashyira hamwe kugira ngo atange imiburo binyuze mu butumwa bugufi ku bantu bashobora kwandura.
Usibye gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo abimenyeshe abantu bashobora kuba bavugana, leta yashyize ahagaragara amakuru y'aho umuntu ari, ibyo bikaba byemewe kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko yo kugumana amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS muri iki gihugu.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze mu porogaramu nyinshi na website.Ibihugu birimo n'Ubudage birimo gutekereza gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite n'ubw'ibanze.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, ntabwo byari byatangajwe.
Kurikirana guhura no kubungabunga ubuzima bwite ni igitekerezo gisobanutse neza, hamwe n'ibitabo byinshi bya siyansi byasubiwemo byibuze 2013. Kuva ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda y'inzobere arenga icumi yakoreye ku bisubizo byubahiriza ubuzima bwite, hakoreshejwe Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) kugirango bandike aho umukoresha ari hafi y'ibindi bikoresho bya telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni imbaraga zo guhuza ibikubiye mu buryo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanze, ntabwo ari protocol imwe. Ibisobanuro by'ibanze birimo Decentralized privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, fka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT) n'ibindi.
Muri ayo maprotocol, amakuru y'umuntu ku giti cye atajya hanze y'igikoresho, kandi uburyo bwose bwo guhuriza hamwe bukorerwa mu gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga rya MIT Media Lab ryatangije inzira z'umutekano, urubuga rwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe cyo gukusanya no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari cyangwa aho anyura kugira ngo akurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Bishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu nyandiko y'ikoranabuhanga "Apps play dirty: maintaining personal privacy in an epidemic" yasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikindi gikorwa nk'icyo ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwa Enigma MPC, ikigo gikora ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga kandi cyashinzwe mbere na mbere muri MIT Media Lab.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bifite umutekano kugira ngo abasoresha bashobore gusangira amakuru y'aho bari n'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi, nta guhungabanya ubuzima bwite bw'ayo makuru.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, Global TCN Coalition yashinzwe n'amatsinda yunze ubumwe ku buryo bumwe kandi ahanini buhuriweho n'amategeko agenga, hagamijwe kugabanya icyuho, no gutuma porogaramu zo kugabisha no gukurikirana zishobora gukorana ku isi hose, ikintu cy'ingenzi mu kugera ku gufatwa ku buryo bwagutse.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapuru yatangaje ko BlueTrace protocol ikoreshwa na porogaramu ya leta yemewe, yabaye isoko rusange.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bigenzura imbuga za Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakoraho, aho bavugaga ko bazakomeza ubuzima bwite, bushingiye ku buryo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy no gukwirakwiza amakuru kugira ngo babungabunge ubuzima bwite.
