Gusubizaho ibiyobyabwenge (zwi no ku izina rya 'drug reproposition', 're-filing', 're-assignment' cyangwa 'therapeutic substitution') ni ugusubizaho ibiyobyabwenge byemewe mu kuvura indwara cyangwa uburwayi butandukanye n'ubwo byatangiwemo.
Ni imwe mu nzira z'ubushakashatsi bwa siyansi muri iki gihe mu gukora imiti idafite ubwandu kandi ikora neza ya COVID-19.
Mu bindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi harimo gukora amaraso ya plasma no gukingira COVID-19. SARS-CoV-2 ifite poroteyine zigera kuri 66 zishobora gukoreshwa, buri imwe ifite ahantu henshi ishobora gufatira.
Gusuzuma ibyo bice by'ingenzi bituma habaho igishushanyo mbonera cy'uburyo bwo gukora umuti wa virusi ukoreshwa cyane mu kurwanya za poroteyine za COVID-19.
Mu maporoteyine y'ingenzi SARS-CoV-2 yibasira harimo papain-like protease, RNA polymerase ishingiye kuri RNA, helicase, protein S na ADP ribophosphatease.
Hussein A. A., et al., yize imiti myinshi y'abakandida, hanyuma bayikora neza kandi bayisuzuma ku buryo ihuriyeho n'imiti yemewe isa cyane kugira ngo yihutishe iterambere ry'umuti ukomeye wa SARS-CoV-2 mu bushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwo gutanga inama ku bushakashatsi bw'imiti.
Chloroquine ni umuti urwanya malariya ukoreshwa no mu bindi bibazo by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine ifitanye isano na yo ari byo byonyine mu miti ine iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu igerageza ry'ubwisungane mu buvuzi.
Guverineri wa New York, Andrew Cuomo yatangaje ko igeragezwa rya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine muri leta ya New York rizatangira ku ya 24 Werurwe. Ku ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yemeje ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate binyuze mu Itegeko ry'Icyorezo (AUE).
Ubu buryo bwo kuvura ntabwo bwemejwe n'ikigo FDA cy'igerageza kandi bwemewe na AUE gusa nk'uburyo bwo kugerageza bwo kuvura byihutirwa ku barwayi bari mu bitaro badashobora guhabwa ubu buryo mu igerageza.
CDC yavuze ko "imikoreshereze, igipimo cyangwa igihe hydroxychloroquine ikoreshwa mu kwirinda cyangwa kuvura ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2" bitarashyirwaho.
Abaganga bavuze ko bakoresha iyo miti mu gihe "nta kundi byagenda".
Muri Istanbul, itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Turukiya barimo bakora ubushakashatsi buto ku ikoreshwa rya chloroquine hamwe na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye burakomeje muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
Ishuri ry'ubuvuzi rya NYU Langone ririmo gukora igerageza ku mutekano n'ubushobozi bwo kwirinda gukoresha hydroxychloroquine.
Ibizamini byo mu Bushinwa byabereye i Wuhan na Shenzhen byavuze ko favipiravir "ifite ubushobozi busesuye".
Muri Shenzhen, abarwayi 35 bagaragaje ko nta bwandu bafite mu minsi ine, mu gihe abarwayi 45 batabonye iyo miti bari bamaze iminsi 11.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye indwara y'ibihaha, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bavuwe favipiravir, ikindi kimwe cya kabiri bahabwa umifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi cy'Ubutaliyani cyibukije abaturage ko ibimenyetso bihari byo gushingiraho uyu muti ari bike kandi ko ari ibisanzwe.
Ku ya 2 Mata, Ubudage bwatangaje ko buzagura uwo muti mu Buyapani kugira ngo bawutunge kandi bukoresha ingabo mu kuwushyikiriza ibitaro bya kaminuza, aho uzakoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Nk'uko ikinyamakuru South China Morning Post kibivuga, Shinzo Abe yagiye ashyiraho uburyo bwo kugura uwo muti ku butegetsi bwa Trump. Uyu muti ushobora kuba udafite ingaruka nziza mu bantu barwaye cyane, igihe virusi imaze kwiyongera.
Gukoresha iyi miti bishobora kutaba byiza ku bagore batwite cyangwa bagerageza gusama.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku miti ya lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ikoreshwa mu buryo bumwe bwa lopinavir na ritonavir, bwagaragaje ko "nta nyungu zabayeho".
Ibiyobyabwenge byakozwe mu rwego rwo kubuza virusi itera SIDA kwongera kwiyongera binyuze mu guhuza na protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado barimo baragerageza guhindura imiti kugira ngo babone umuti wifatanya na protease ya SARS-CoV-2. Hariho kunenga mu muryango w'abahanga ku birebana no kwimurira umutungo ku miti yagenewe kurwanya SIDA.
OMS yashyize lopinavir/ritonavir mu isuzuma mpuzamahanga rya Solidarity.
Remdesivir yatangijwe kandi ikorwa na Gilead Sciences nk'umuti wa Ebola na Marburg virus. Gilead Sciences yaje kumenya ko remdesivir ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya virusi mu mubiri ku ndwara ya phylum, pneumonia, paramyx, na coronavirus.
Kimwe mu bibazo bivuka mu miti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni uko iyo virusi ihindutse, ishobora kwandura cyangwa igatera indwara zikomeye.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwa mbere bugaragaza ko remdesivir ishobora kugira inzitizi ikomeye mu ndwara. Hari ibizamini byinshi biri gukorwa, harimo bibiri byakozwe n'ibitaro bya Kaminuza ya Cleveland, kimwe ku barwayi barwaye indwara yoroheje, ikindi ku barwaye indwara ikomeye.
Hari ibizamini bitatu bya vitamini C mu mitsi birimo gukorwa ku bantu barwariye mu bitaro kandi barwaye cyane COVID-19: bibiri muri byo ni ibipimo bya placebo (mu Bushinwa no muri Kanada), mu gihe ikindi nta kigero cyabyo (mu Butaliyani).
Leta ya New York yatangiye gukora igerageza rya azithromycin, umuti urwanya indwara, ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'Ubuzima n'Ubuvuzi ku Isi (NCGM) cyo mu Buyapani kirateganya kugerageza Alvesco (cyclesonide) ikorwa n'ikigo Teijin, ni umuti wa corticosteroid wa asima uhumeka, ugamije kuvura abarwayi bataragaragaza ibimenyetso by'indwara ya koronavirusi.
Icyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ry'ubwoko bwa angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ririmo gukorwa ku barwayi 200, bagiye gukorerwa ubushakashatsi mu barwayi bakomeye bari mu bitaro muri Danemark, Ubudage na Autriche, kugira ngo hamenyekane niba ari bwo bufasha.
Muri iki gihe, abashakashatsi bo mu kigo cy'umutima muri Kanada barimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku ruhare rwa colchicine mu kugabanya ibibazo by'ibihaha n'imyanda ku barwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje bya COVID-19.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwitwa COLCORONA, burimo kwinjiza abantu bakuru 6000 barengeje imyaka 40, basanganywe COVID-19 kandi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje, batagombaga kujya mu bitaro.
Abagore batwite, bonsa cyangwa badakoresha uburyo bwiza bwo kuboneza urubyaro ntibari muri ibi byigwa.
Hari imiti ituma amaraso atembera mu maraso irimo kugeragezwa mu Butaliyani.
Heparin ifite ibiro bito by'imashini, iri gukoreshwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi, ibyo bikaba byaratumye ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani gishinzwe imiti gitanga amabwiriza ku mikoreshereze yayo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo bitandukanye, bugizwe n'abarwayi 300, burimo gusuzuma ikoreshwa rya enoxaparin sodium mu kwirinda indwara no mu miti ifasha indwara. Ubwo bushakashatsi bwatangajwe ku ya 14 Mata mu Butaliyani.
