Urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni urukingo rw'icyerekezo rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo rwamaze kugeragezwa mu buvuzi, hari ingamba nyinshi ziri gukorwa zo kurukora.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko rititeze ko urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi itera iyo ndwara, ruzaba rubonetse mu mezi atageze kuri 18.
Abakandida batanu b'urukingo bari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi ku budahemuka muri Mata.
COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu Kuboza 2019.
Mu 2020 habaye ikwirakwira rikomeye ry'icyorezo, bituma hashyirwaho imbaraga nyinshi mu ishoramari no gukora ubushakashatsi mu gukora urukingo.
Imiryango itandukanye irimo gukoresha genomes zasohotse mu gukora inkingo zishobora kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Umushinga wa Coalition for Innovations in Epidemic Preparedness, CEPI, watangaje muri Mata ko ibisabwa mu gukora urukingo ari umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, iterambere ryinshi no kugera ku isi hose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi bo muri CEPI batangaje ko hashyizweho ikoranabuhanga 10 mu bushakashatsi no mu iterambere mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rukora neza rwa COVID-19.
Intego z'ibigo bikomeye byateye imbere mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'umutekano zirimo:
Umuneke wa ADN cyangwa RNA (Umushinga wa mbere w'ubushakashatsi n'urukingo rw'umukandida: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
