Umuyobozi wa OMS, Tedros Adhanon Ghebreyesus, yasobanuye ko "CO" ari "corona", "VI", "virus", "D", indwara, naho "19" ari igihe iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Izina ryatowe mu kwirinda ibisobanuro by'ahantu runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu, hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga yo gushyiraho amazina kugira ngo hatagira umuntu ushyirwa mu kato. Virusi itera COVID-19 yiswe coronavirus y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
OMS ikoresha kandi "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu butumwa igera ku baturage.
Iyo ndwara na virusi byombi bikunze kwitwa "coronavirus".
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabereye i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byakunze kwitwa "coronavirus" na "coronavirus ya Wuhan".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yateye inkunga "2019-nCov" na " 2019-nCoV y'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikaze" nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara, hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu mazina y'indwara na virusi.
Amazina y'ibanze COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
Kubera ubushobozi buke mu miyoboro isanzwe y'itangwa ry'ibiribwa, bamwe mu bakora ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, nk'udupfunyika tw'umuhogo n'udupfunyika tw'imashini zo guhumeka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byari bikeneye cyane umufuka wo guhumeka, kandi ababikora bakaba batari bashoboye kubitanga ku gihe, ikigo cyo muri ako gace cyakoze imashini za rutura maze mu ijoro rimwe gusa bacapa za fatizo 100 zari zikenewe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere, ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru atari yo ku nkomoko, ingano, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi by'iyi ndwara byavutse, bikwirakwira kuri interineti mu buryo bwihuse.
Abantu basa n'aho bashobora kwanduza izindi nyamaswa.
Ubushakashatsi ntibwigeze bushobora kubona ibimenyetso by'uko virusi ikwirakwira mu ngurube, itere n'inkoko.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe mu kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burakomeje mu nzego za leta, mu matsinda y'abanyeshuri no mu bashakashatsi bo mu nganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije igerageza ryiswe "SOLIDARITY Trial" rigamije gusuzuma ingaruka z'ubuvuzi bw'imiti ine isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi ishobora kugira ingaruka nziza.
Nta rukingo ruhari, ariko inzego zitandukanye zirimo gukora cyane ku bakandida b'urukingo.
Ibikorwa byakozwe mbere kuri SARS-CoV birimo gukoreshwa kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 zikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira abantu burimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bafite intego yo gukora urukingo rufite virusi yose.
Gukoresha iyi virusi yaba idafite ubuzima cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutuma umubiri w'umuntu ubasha guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19 mu buryo bwihuse.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, inkingo z'udutsiko duto, bugamije gukora inkingo zituma umubiri ugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya udutsiko duto tw'iyo virusi.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine yo mu rufunzo ifasha virusi kwinjira mu cyuma cyakira ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni bwa vaccines za nucleic acid (incanco za DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza z'izo ngamba zose zagombaga kugeragezwa ku mutekano n'imikorere. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangiranye n'abakorerabushake bane i Seattle.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'imiterere itagira icyo itwaye yakuwe muri virusi itera iyo ndwara. Guteza imbere umubiri ushingiye ku rukingo rw'umubiri byavuzwe ko bishobora kuba imbogamizi mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, ariko ibyo biravuguruzanya.
Hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa kuva muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumye imiti yemewe ya malariya, harimo n'inyigo enye z'imiti yitwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Gucana imiti igabanya ubukana bwa virusi ni byo byiganje mu bushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa, aho raporo yo mu mpera za Mata yagaragaje ko hari ibizamini icyenda byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya gatatu cya remdesivir mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Isesengura ry'imikorere y'imiti n'urukingo bya COVID-19 byari bikomeje muri Mata 2020. Imiti itandukanye ya virusi iriho iri kugeragezwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo remdesivir, chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir na lopinavir/ritonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Hariho kugerageza kugaragaza ko remdesivir igira ingaruka nziza kuva muri Werurwe 2020.
Imibereho myiza y'abarwayi yagaragaye mu barwayi bahabwa remdesivir ku bw'impuhwe.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya gatatu birakorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ibitero bya chloroquine, byamaze gukoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, byakorewe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, bibonekamo ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, hari abasaba ko ubushakashatsi bwajya busubirwamo.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'Ubushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chloroquine.
Icyakora, Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara za virusi cya Wuhan, nubwo gitanga inama yo gufata igramu imwe ku munsi, kiraburira ko iyo umuntu afashe igramu ebyiri ari akaga kandi ko bishobora kumwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yasohoye uruhushya rw'ihungabana rwo gukoresha hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine ku bushake bw'abaganga bavura abantu barwaye COVID-19. Itegeko Nshinga rya 7 ry'Ubushinwa rinakubiyemo interféron, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir yo gukoresha kuri COVID-19.
Ibipimo by'ibanze bigaragaza ko ribavirin ikenera ibipimo byinshi kugira ngo ihagarike SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba.
Nitazoxanide yasabwe gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu buzima nyuma yo kugaragaza ko ifite ubushobozi buke bwo kubuza SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko poroteyine ya spicule ya mbere itegurwa na serine transmembrane protease 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ingenzi mu kwinjira kwa SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhura n'urwunganire rwa ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi kuri chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bufite inzitizi zikomeye zatumye abaganga batabona uburyo bwo kwivuza bwuzuye. Oseltamivir ntibuza SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba kandi nta ruhare ruzwi ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Icyorezo cya cytokine gishobora kuba ikibazo mu byiciro bya nyuma bya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya cytocin. Tocilzumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa nyuma yo gusoza isuzuma rito.
Icyiciro cya kabiri cy'igerageza ridakorewe ku bushake mu gihugu cyose cy'u Butaliyani kirimo gukorwa nyuma yo kugaragaza ko abantu barwaye cyane barwaye.
Iyo ufatanyije n'isuzuma ry'amaraso ya ferritin mu maraso kugira ngo umenye ibiza bya cytokine, byitezwe ko byamagana ibyo byorezo, bikaba byitezwe ko ari byo byahitanye bamwe mu bantu babyifitiye.
Interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yemejwe na FDA ishingiye ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma yo kuvura indwara yo kugabanya imisemburo ya sitokini ituma umuntu atafata imiti ikoreshwa na siteroyi ituma umuntu atafata imiti, CAR T cell therapy mu 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya kigaragara kandi gifatika cyerekana ko tocilzumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Gushyiraho abasirikare b'umubiri basukuye kandi bakomeye bakorewe n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bw'umuntu wakize COVID-19 mu bantu babukeneye birimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi nk'uburyo butari ubwisungane mu gukingira.
Ubwo buryo bwakozwe mu gihe cya SARS, ariko nta byavuye mu bushakashatsi.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo gukoresha imiti igabanya ubukana bw'umubiri mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari ubundi buryo bushobora kubaho, urugero nk'ubwandu bw'ingirabuzimafatizo bushingiye ku bishishwa by'umubiri n'ubundi bwitwa phagocytosis.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi b'umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha abarwayi b'umubiri b'umubiri umwe, burimo gukorwa.
Umusaruro wa sera yo gukira, ugizwe n'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi urimo abasirikare ba virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ushobore gushyirwa mu bikorwa vuba.
